var book = {
	"name": "Isaiah",
	"numChapters": 66,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The vision of Isaiah the son of Amoz concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17656A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17656A\"></sup>Judah and Jerusalem, which he saw during the reigns of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17656B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17656B\"></sup>Uzziah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17656C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17656C\"></sup>Jotham, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17656D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17656D\"></sup>Ahaz <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17656E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17656E\"></sup>Hezekiah, kings of Judah.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17657F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17657F\"></sup>Listen, O heavens, and hear, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17657G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17657G\"></sup>earth;For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> speaks,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17657H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17657H\"></sup>Sons I have reared and brought up,But they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17657I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17657I\"></sup>revolted against Me.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“An ox knows its owner,And a donkey its master’s manger,<i>But</i> Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17658J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17658J\"></sup>does not know,My people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17658K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17658K\"></sup>do not understand.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Alas, sinful nation,People weighed down with iniquity,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17659L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17659L\"></sup>Offspring of evildoers,Sons who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17659M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17659M\"></sup>act corruptly!They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17659N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17659N\"></sup>abandoned the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17659O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17659O\"></sup>despised the Holy One of Israel,They have turned away from Him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Where will you be stricken again,<i>As</i> you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17660P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17660P\"></sup>continue in <i>your</i> rebellion?The whole head is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17660Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17660Q\"></sup>sickAnd the whole heart is faint.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17661R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17661R\"></sup>From the sole of the foot even to the headThere is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17661S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17661S\"></sup>nothing sound in it,<i>Only</i> bruises, welts and raw wounds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17661T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17661T\"></sup>Not pressed out or bandaged,Nor softened with oil.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17662U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17662U\"></sup>land is desolate,Your cities are burned with fire,Your fields—strangers are devouring them in your presence;It is desolation, as overthrown by strangers.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The daughter of Zion is left like a shelter in a vineyard,Like a watchman’s hut in a cucumber field, like a besieged city.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17664V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17664V\"></sup>Unless the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hostsHad left us a few <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17664W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17664W\"></sup>survivors,We would be like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17664X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17664X\"></sup>Sodom,We would be like Gomorrah.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Hear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17665Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17665Y\"></sup>the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,You rulers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17665Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17665Z\"></sup>Sodom;Give ear to the instruction of our God,You people of Gomorrah.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17666AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17666AA\"></sup>What are your multiplied sacrifices to Me?”Says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“I have had enough of burnt offerings of ramsAnd the fat of fed cattle;And I take no pleasure in the blood of bulls, lambs or goats.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“When you come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17667AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17667AB\"></sup>to appear before Me,Who requires of you this trampling of My courts?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Bring your worthless offerings no longer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17668AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17668AC\"></sup>Incense is an abomination to Me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17668AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17668AD\"></sup>New moon and sabbath, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17668AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17668AE\"></sup>calling of assemblies—I cannot <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17668AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17668AF\"></sup>endure iniquity and the solemn assembly.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“I hate your new moon <i>festivals</i> and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17669AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17669AG\"></sup>appointed feasts,They have become a burden to Me;I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17669AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17669AH\"></sup>weary of bearing <i>them</i>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“So when you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17670AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17670AI\"></sup>spread out your hands <i>in prayer</i>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17670AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17670AJ\"></sup>I will hide My eyes from you;Yes, even though you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17670AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17670AK\"></sup>multiply prayers,I will not listen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17670AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17670AL\"></sup>Your hands are covered with blood.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17671AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17671AM\"></sup>Wash yourselves, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17671AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17671AN\"></sup>make yourselves clean;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17671AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17671AO\"></sup>Remove the evil of your deeds from My sight.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17671AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17671AP\"></sup>Cease to do evil,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Learn to do good;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17672AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17672AQ\"></sup>Seek justice,Reprove the ruthless,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17672AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17672AR\"></sup>Defend the orphan,Plead for the widow.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Come now, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17673AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17673AS\"></sup>let us reason together,”Says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17673AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17673AT\"></sup>Though your sins are as scarlet,They will be as white as snow;Though they are red like crimson,They will be like wool.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17674AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17674AU\"></sup>If you consent and obey,You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17674AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17674AV\"></sup>eat the best of the land;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“But if you refuse and rebel,You will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17675AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17675AW\"></sup>devoured by the sword.”Truly, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17675AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17675AX\"></sup>the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>How the faithful city has become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17676AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17676AY\"></sup>harlot,She <i>who</i> was full of justice!Righteousness once lodged in her,But now murderers.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Your silver has become dross,Your drink diluted with water.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17678AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17678AZ\"></sup>rulers are rebelsAnd companions of thieves;Everyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17678BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17678BA\"></sup>loves a bribeAnd chases after rewards.They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17678BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17678BB\"></sup>do not defend the orphan,Nor does the widow’s plea come before them.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17679BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17679BC\"></sup>Mighty One of Israel, declares,“Ah, I will be relieved of My adversariesAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17679BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17679BD\"></sup>avenge Myself on My foes.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“I will also turn My hand against you,And will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17680BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17680BE\"></sup>smelt away your dross as with lyeAnd will remove all your alloy.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Then I will restore your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17681BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17681BF\"></sup>judges as at the first,And your counselors as at the beginning;After that you will be called the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17681BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17681BG\"></sup>city of righteousness,A faithful city.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Zion will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17682BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17682BH\"></sup>redeemed with justiceAnd her repentant ones with righteousness.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But transgressors and sinners will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17683BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17683BI\"></sup>crushed together,And those who forsake the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will come to an end.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Surely you will be ashamed of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17684BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17684BJ\"></sup>oaks which you have desired,And you will be embarrassed at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17684BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17684BK\"></sup>gardens which you have chosen.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For you will be like an oak whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17685BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17685BL\"></sup>leaf fades awayOr as a garden that has no water.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The strong man will become tinder,His work also a spark.Thus they shall both <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17686BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17686BM\"></sup>burn togetherAnd there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17686BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17686BN\"></sup>none to quench <i>them</i>."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>The word which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17687A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17687A\"></sup>Isaiah the son of Amoz saw concerning Judah and Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now it will come about that<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17688B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17688B\"></sup>In the last daysThe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17688C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17688C\"></sup>mountain of the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>Will be established as the chief of the mountains,And will be raised above the hills;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17688D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17688D\"></sup>all the nations will stream to it.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And many peoples will come and say,“Come, let us go up to the mountain of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,To the house of the God of Jacob;That He may teach us concerning His waysAnd that we may walk in His paths.”For the law will go forth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17689E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17689E\"></sup>from ZionAnd the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from Jerusalem.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And He will judge between the nations,And will render decisions for many peoples;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17690F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17690F\"></sup>they will hammer their swords into plowshares and their spears into pruning hooks.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17690G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17690G\"></sup>Nation will not lift up sword against nation,And never again will they learn war.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Come, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17691H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17691H\"></sup>house of Jacob, and let us walk in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17691I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17691I\"></sup>light of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17692J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17692J\"></sup>abandoned Your people, the house of Jacob,Because they are filled <i>with influences</i> from the east,And <i>they are</i> soothsayers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17692K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17692K\"></sup>like the Philistines,And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17692L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17692L\"></sup>strike <i>bargains</i> with the children of foreigners.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Their land has also been filled with silver and goldAnd there is no end to their treasures;Their land has also been filled with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17693M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17693M\"></sup>horsesAnd there is no end to their chariots.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Their land has also been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17694N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17694N\"></sup>filled with idols;They worship the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17694O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17694O\"></sup>work of their hands,That which their fingers have made.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17695P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17695P\"></sup>the <i>common</i> man has been humbledAnd the man <i>of importance</i> has been abased,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17695Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17695Q\"></sup>do not forgive them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17696R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17696R\"></sup>Enter the rock and hide in the dust<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17696S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17696S\"></sup>From the terror of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and from the splendor of His majesty.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17697T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17697T\"></sup>proud look of man will be abasedAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17697U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17697U\"></sup>loftiness of man will be humbled,And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> alone will be exalted in that day.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will have a day <i>of reckoning</i>Against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17698V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17698V\"></sup>everyone who is proud and loftyAnd against everyone who is lifted up,That he may be abased.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And <i>it will be</i> against all the cedars of Lebanon that are lofty and lifted up,Against all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17699W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17699W\"></sup>oaks of Bashan,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Against all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17700X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17700X\"></sup>lofty mountains,Against all the hills that are lifted up,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Against every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17701Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17701Y\"></sup>high tower,Against every fortified wall,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Against all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17702Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17702Z\"></sup>ships of TarshishAnd against all the beautiful craft.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The pride of man will be humbledAnd the loftiness of men will be abased;And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> alone will be exalted in that day,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17704AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17704AA\"></sup>idols will completely vanish.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><i>Men</i> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17705AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17705AB\"></sup>go into caves of the rocksAnd into holes of the groundBefore the terror of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>And the splendor of His majesty,When He arises <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17705AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17705AC\"></sup>to make the earth tremble.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In that day men will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17706AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17706AD\"></sup>cast away to the moles and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17706AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17706AE\"></sup>batsTheir idols of silver and their idols of gold,Which they made for themselves to worship,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>In order to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17707AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17707AF\"></sup>go into the caverns of the rocks and the clefts of the cliffsBefore the terror of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and the splendor of His majesty,When He arises to make the earth tremble.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17708AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17708AG\"></sup>Stop regarding man, whose breath <i>of life</i> is in his nostrils;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17708AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17708AH\"></sup>why should he be esteemed?"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>For behold, the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17709A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17709A\"></sup>is going to remove from Jerusalem and JudahBoth supply and support, the whole supply of breadAnd the whole supply of water;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17710B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17710B\"></sup>The mighty man and the warrior,The judge and the prophet,The diviner and the elder,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The captain of fifty and the honorable man,The counselor and the expert artisan,And the skillful enchanter.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And I will make mere <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17712C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17712C\"></sup>lads their princes,And capricious children will rule over them,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And the people will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17713D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17713D\"></sup>oppressed,Each one by another, and each one by his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17713E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17713E\"></sup>neighbor;The youth will storm against the elderAnd the inferior against the honorable.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17714F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17714F\"></sup>lays hold of his brother in his father’s house, <i>saying</i>,“You have a cloak, you shall be our ruler,And these ruins will be under your charge,”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He will protest on that day, saying,“I will not be <i>your</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17715G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17715G\"></sup>healer,For in my house there is neither bread nor cloak;You should not appoint me ruler of the people.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17716H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17716H\"></sup>Jerusalem has stumbled and Judah has fallen,Because their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17716I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17716I\"></sup>speech and their actions are against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17716J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17716J\"></sup>rebel against His glorious presence.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The expression of their faces bears witness against them,And they display their sin like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17717K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17717K\"></sup>Sodom;They do not <i>even</i> conceal <i>it</i>.Woe to them!For they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17717L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17717L\"></sup>brought evil on themselves.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Say to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17718M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17718M\"></sup>righteous that <i>it will go</i> well <i>with them</i>,For they will eat the fruit of their actions.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Woe to the wicked! <i>It will go</i> badly <i>with him</i>,For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17719N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17719N\"></sup>what he deserves will be done to him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>O My people! Their oppressors are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17720O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17720O\"></sup>children,And women rule over them.O My people! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17720P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17720P\"></sup>Those who guide you lead <i>you</i> astrayAnd confuse the direction of your paths.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17721Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17721Q\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> arises to contend,And stands to judge the people.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17722R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17722R\"></sup>enters into judgment with the elders and princes of His people,“It is you who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17722S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17722S\"></sup>devoured the vineyard;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17722T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17722T\"></sup>plunder of the poor is in your houses.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“What do you mean by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17723U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17723U\"></sup>crushing My peopleAnd grinding the face of the poor?”Declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Moreover, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “Because the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17724V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17724V\"></sup>daughters of Zion are proudAnd walk with heads held high and seductive eyes,And go along with mincing stepsAnd tinkle the bangles on their feet,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore the Lord will afflict the scalp of the daughters of Zion with scabs,And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will make their foreheads bare.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In that day the Lord will take away the beauty of <i>their</i> anklets, headbands, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17726W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17726W\"></sup>crescent ornaments,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>dangling earrings, bracelets, veils,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17728X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17728X\"></sup>headdresses, ankle chains, sashes, perfume boxes, amulets,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>finger rings, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17729Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17729Y\"></sup>nose rings,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>festal robes, outer tunics, cloaks, money purses,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>hand mirrors, undergarments, turbans and veils.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now it will come about that instead of sweet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17732Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17732Z\"></sup>perfume there will be putrefaction;Instead of a belt, a rope;Instead of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17732AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17732AA\"></sup>well-set hair, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17732AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17732AB\"></sup>plucked-out scalp;Instead of fine clothes, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17732AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17732AC\"></sup>donning of sackcloth;And branding instead of beauty.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Your men will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17733AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17733AD\"></sup>fall by the swordAnd your mighty ones in battle.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17734AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17734AE\"></sup>gates will lament and mourn,And deserted she will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17734AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17734AF\"></sup>sit on the ground."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>For seven women will take hold of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17735A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17735A\"></sup>one man in that day, saying, “We will eat our own bread and wear our own clothes, only let us be called by your name; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17735B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17735B\"></sup>take away our reproach!”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>In that day the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17736C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17736C\"></sup>Branch of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be beautiful and glorious, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17736D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17736D\"></sup>fruit of the earth <i>will be</i> the pride and the adornment of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17736E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17736E\"></sup>survivors of Israel.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>It will come about that he who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17737F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17737F\"></sup>left in Zion and remains in Jerusalem will be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17737G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17737G\"></sup>holy—everyone who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17737H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17737H\"></sup>recorded for life in Jerusalem.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When the Lord has washed away the filth of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17738I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17738I\"></sup>daughters of Zion and purged the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17738J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17738J\"></sup>bloodshed of Jerusalem from her midst, by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17738K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17738K\"></sup>spirit of judgment and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17738L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17738L\"></sup>spirit of burning,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will create over the whole area of Mount Zion and over her assemblies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17739M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17739M\"></sup>a cloud by day, even smoke, and the brightness of a flaming fire by night; for over all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17739N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17739N\"></sup>glory will be a canopy.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>There will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17740O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17740O\"></sup>shelter to <i>give</i> shade from the heat by day, and refuge and protection from the storm and the rain."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Let me sing now for my well-belovedA song of my beloved concerning His vineyard.My well-beloved had a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17741A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17741A\"></sup>vineyard on a fertile hill.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He dug it all around, removed its stones,And planted it with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17742B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17742B\"></sup>choicest vine.And He built a tower in the middle of itAnd also hewed out a wine vat in it;Then He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17742C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17742C\"></sup>expected <i>it</i> to produce <i>good</i> grapes,But it produced <i>only</i> worthless ones.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“And now, O inhabitants of Jerusalem and men of Judah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17743D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17743D\"></sup>Judge between Me and My vineyard.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17744E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17744E\"></sup>What more was there to do for My vineyard that I have not done in it?Why, when I expected <i>it</i> to produce <i>good</i> grapes did it produce worthless ones?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“So now let Me tell you what I am going to do to My vineyard:I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17745F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17745F\"></sup>remove its hedge and it will be consumed;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17745G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17745G\"></sup>break down its wall and it will become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17745H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17745H\"></sup>trampled ground.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17746I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17746I\"></sup>lay it waste;It will not be pruned or hoed,But briars and thorns will come up.I will also charge the clouds to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17746J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17746J\"></sup>rain no rain on it.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17747K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17747K\"></sup>vineyard of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is the house of IsraelAnd the men of Judah His delightful plant.Thus He looked for justice, but behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17747L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17747L\"></sup>bloodshed;For righteousness, but behold, a cry of distress.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Woe to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17748M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17748M\"></sup>add house to house <i>and</i> join field to field,Until there is no more room,So that you have to live alone in the midst of the land!",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>In my ears the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts <i>has sworn</i>, “Surely, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17749N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17749N\"></sup>many houses shall become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17749O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17749O\"></sup>desolate,<i>Even</i> great and fine ones, without occupants.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17750P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17750P\"></sup>ten acres of vineyard will yield <i>only</i> one bath <i>of wine</i>,And a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17750Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17750Q\"></sup>homer of seed will yield <i>but</i> an ephah of grain.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Woe to those who rise early in the morning that they may pursue <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17751R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17751R\"></sup>strong drink,Who stay up late in the evening that wine may inflame them!",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Their banquets are <i>accompanied</i> by lyre and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17752S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17752S\"></sup>harp, by tambourine and flute, and by wine;But they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17752T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17752T\"></sup>do not pay attention to the deeds of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Nor do they consider the work of His hands.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore My people go into exile for their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17753U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17753U\"></sup>lack of knowledge;And their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17753V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17753V\"></sup>honorable men are famished,And their multitude is parched with thirst.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17754W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17754W\"></sup>Sheol has enlarged its throat and opened its mouth without measure;And Jerusalem’s splendor, her multitude, her din <i>of revelry</i> and the jubilant within her, descend <i>into it</i>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So the <i>common</i> man will be humbled and the man of <i>importance</i> abased,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17755X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17755X\"></sup>The eyes of the proud also will be abased.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17756Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17756Y\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17756Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17756Z\"></sup>exalted in judgment,And the holy God will show Himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17756AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17756AA\"></sup>holy in righteousness.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17757AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17757AB\"></sup>Then the lambs will graze as in their pasture,And strangers will eat in the waste places of the wealthy.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Woe to those who drag <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17758AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17758AC\"></sup>iniquity with the cords of falsehood,And sin as if with cart ropes;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17759AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17759AD\"></sup>Who say, “Let Him make speed, let Him hasten His work, that we may see <i>it</i>;And let the purpose of the Holy One of Israel draw nearAnd come to pass, that we may know <i>it</i>!”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Woe to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17760AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17760AE\"></sup>call evil good, and good evil;Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17760AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17760AF\"></sup>substitute darkness for light and light for darkness;Who substitute bitter for sweet and sweet for bitter!",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Woe to those who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17761AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17761AG\"></sup>wise in their own eyesAnd clever in their own sight!",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17762AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17762AH\"></sup>Woe to those who are heroes in drinking wineAnd valiant men in mixing strong drink,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17763AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17763AI\"></sup>Who justify the wicked for a bribe,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17763AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17763AJ\"></sup>take away the rights of the ones who are in the right!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17764AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17764AK\"></sup>as a tongue of fire consumes stubbleAnd dry grass collapses into the flame,So their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17764AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17764AL\"></sup>root will become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17764AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17764AM\"></sup>like rot and their blossom blow away as dust;For they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17764AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17764AN\"></sup>rejected the law of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hostsAnd despised the word of the Holy One of Israel.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>On this account the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17765AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17765AO\"></sup>anger of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has burned against His people,And He has stretched out His hand against them and struck them down.And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17765AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17765AP\"></sup>mountains quaked, and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17765AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17765AQ\"></sup>corpses lay like refuse in the middle of the streets.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17765AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17765AR\"></sup>For all this His anger is not spent,But His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17765AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17765AS\"></sup>hand is still stretched out.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He will also lift up a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17766AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17766AT\"></sup>standard to the distant nation,And will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17766AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17766AU\"></sup>whistle for it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17766AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17766AV\"></sup>from the ends of the earth;And behold, it will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17766AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17766AW\"></sup>come with speed swiftly.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17767AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17767AX\"></sup>No one in it is weary or stumbles,None slumbers or sleeps;Nor is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17767AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17767AY\"></sup>belt at its waist undone,Nor its sandal strap broken.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17768AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17768AZ\"></sup>Its arrows are sharp and all its bows are bent;The hoofs of its horses seem like flint and its <i>chariot</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17768BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17768BA\"></sup>wheels like a whirlwind.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17769BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17769BB\"></sup>roaring is like a lioness, and it roars like young lions;It growls as it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17769BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17769BC\"></sup>seizes the preyAnd carries <i>it</i> off with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17769BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17769BD\"></sup>no one to deliver <i>it</i>.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And it will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17770BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17770BE\"></sup>growl over it in that day like the roaring of the sea.If one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17770BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17770BF\"></sup>looks to the land, behold, there is darkness <i>and</i> distress;Even the light is darkened by its clouds."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>In the year of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17771A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17771A\"></sup>King Uzziah’s death <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17771B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17771B\"></sup>I saw the Lord sitting on a throne, lofty and exalted, with the train of His robe filling the temple.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Seraphim stood above Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17772C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17772C\"></sup>each having six wings: with two he covered his face, and with two he covered his feet, and with two he flew.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And one called out to another and said,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17773D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17773D\"></sup>Holy, Holy, Holy, is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17773E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17773E\"></sup>whole earth is full of His glory.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And the foundations of the thresholds trembled at the voice of him who called out, while the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17774F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17774F\"></sup>temple was filling with smoke.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then I said,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17775G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17775G\"></sup>Woe is me, for I am ruined!Because I am a man of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17775H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17775H\"></sup>unclean lips,And I live among a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17775I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17775I\"></sup>people of unclean lips;For my eyes have seen the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17775J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17775J\"></sup>King, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then one of the seraphim flew to me with a burning coal in his hand, which he had taken from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17776K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17776K\"></sup>altar with tongs.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17777L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17777L\"></sup>touched my mouth <i>with it</i> and said, “Behold, this has touched your lips; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17777M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17777M\"></sup>your iniquity is taken away and your sin is forgiven.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then I heard the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17778N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17778N\"></sup>voice of the Lord, saying, “Whom shall I send, and who will go for Us?” Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17778O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17778O\"></sup>I said, “Here am I. Send me!”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He said, “Go, and tell this people:‘Keep on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17779P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17779P\"></sup>listening, but do not perceive;Keep on looking, but do not understand.’",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17780Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17780Q\"></sup>Render the hearts of this people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17780R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17780R\"></sup>insensitive,Their ears dull,And their eyes dim,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17780S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17780S\"></sup>Otherwise they might see with their eyes,Hear with their ears,Understand with their hearts,And return and be healed.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I said, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17781T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17781T\"></sup>how long?” And He answered,“Until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17781U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17781U\"></sup>cities are devastated <i>and</i> without inhabitant,Houses are without peopleAnd the land is utterly desolate,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17782V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17782V\"></sup>removed men far away,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17782W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17782W\"></sup>forsaken places are many in the midst of the land.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Yet there will be a tenth portion in it,And it will again be <i>subject</i> to burning,Like a terebinth or an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17783X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17783X\"></sup>oakWhose stump remains when it is felled.The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17783Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17783Y\"></sup>holy seed is its stump.”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>Now it came about in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17784A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17784A\"></sup>Ahaz, the son of Jotham, the son of Uzziah, king of Judah, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17784B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17784B\"></sup>Rezin the king of Aram and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17784C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17784C\"></sup>Pekah the son of Remaliah, king of Israel, went up to Jerusalem to <i>wage</i> war against it, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17784D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17784D\"></sup>could not conquer it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When it was reported to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17785E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17785E\"></sup>house of David, saying, “The Arameans <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17785F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17785F\"></sup>have camped in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17785G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17785G\"></sup>Ephraim,” his heart and the hearts of his people shook as the trees of the forest shake with the wind.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Isaiah, “Go out now to meet Ahaz, you and your son Shear-jashub, at the end of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17786H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17786H\"></sup>conduit of the upper pool, on the highway to the fuller’s field,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and say to him, ‘Take care and be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17787I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17787I\"></sup>calm, have no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17787J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17787J\"></sup>fear and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17787K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17787K\"></sup>do not be fainthearted because of these two stubs of smoldering <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17787L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17787L\"></sup>firebrands, on account of the fierce anger of Rezin and Aram and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17787M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17787M\"></sup>son of Remaliah.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17788N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17788N\"></sup>Aram, <i>with</i> Ephraim and the son of Remaliah, has planned evil against you, saying,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Let us go up against Judah and terrorize it, and make for ourselves a breach in its walls and set up the son of Tabeel as king in the midst of it,”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>: “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17790O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17790O\"></sup>It shall not stand nor shall it come to pass.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For the head of Aram is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17791P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17791P\"></sup>Damascus and the head of Damascus is Rezin (now within another 65 years Ephraim will be shattered, <i>so that it is</i> no longer a people),",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and the head of Ephraim is Samaria and the head of Samaria is the son of Remaliah. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17792Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17792Q\"></sup>If you will not believe, you surely shall not last.”’”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke again to Ahaz, saying,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Ask a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17794R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17794R\"></sup>sign for yourself from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God; make <i>it</i> deep as Sheol or high as heaven.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But Ahaz said, “I will not ask, nor will I test the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then he said, “Listen now, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17796S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17796S\"></sup>house of David! Is it too slight a thing for you to try the patience of men, that you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17796T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17796T\"></sup>try the patience of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17796U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17796U\"></sup>my God as well?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore the Lord Himself will give you a sign: Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17797V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17797V\"></sup>a virgin will be with child and bear a son, and she will call His name <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17797W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17797W\"></sup>Immanuel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He will eat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17798X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17798X\"></sup>curds and honey at the time He knows <i>enough</i> to refuse evil and choose good.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17799Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17799Y\"></sup>For before the boy will know <i>enough</i> to refuse evil and choose good, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17799Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17799Z\"></sup>the land whose two kings you dread will be forsaken.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will bring on you, on your people, and on your father’s house such days as have never come since the day that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17800AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17800AA\"></sup>Ephraim separated from Judah, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17800AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17800AB\"></sup>king of Assyria.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In that day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17801AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17801AC\"></sup>whistle for the fly that is in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17801AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17801AD\"></sup>remotest part of the rivers of Egypt and for the bee that is in the land of Assyria.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They will all come and settle on the steep ravines, on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17802AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17802AE\"></sup>ledges of the cliffs, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17802AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17802AF\"></sup>on all the thorn bushes and on all the watering places.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>In that day the Lord will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17803AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17803AG\"></sup>shave with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17803AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17803AH\"></sup>razor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17803AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17803AI\"></sup>hired from regions beyond <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17803AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17803AJ\"></sup>the Euphrates (<i>that is</i>, with the king of Assyria), the head and the hair of the legs; and it will also remove the beard.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Now in that day a man may keep alive a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17804AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17804AK\"></sup>heifer and a pair of sheep;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and because of the abundance of the milk produced he will eat curds, for everyone that is left within the land will eat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17805AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17805AL\"></sup>curds and honey.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And it will come about in that day, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17806AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17806AM\"></sup>that every place where there used to be a thousand vines, <i>valued</i> at a thousand <i>shekels</i> of silver, will become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17806AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17806AN\"></sup>briars and thorns.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup><i>People</i> will come there with bows and arrows because all the land will be briars and thorns.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>As for all the hills which used to be cultivated with the hoe, you will not go there for fear of briars and thorns; but they will become a place for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17808AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17808AO\"></sup>pasturing oxen and for sheep to trample."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Take for yourself a large tablet and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17809A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17809A\"></sup>write on it in ordinary letters: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17809B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17809B\"></sup>Swift is the booty, speedy is the prey.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I will take to Myself faithful witnesses for testimony, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17810C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17810C\"></sup>Uriah the priest and Zechariah the son of Jeberechiah.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So I approached the prophetess, and she conceived and gave birth to a son. Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Name him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17811D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17811D\"></sup>Maher-shalal-hash-baz;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17812E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17812E\"></sup>before the boy knows how to cry out ‘My father’ or ‘My mother,’ the wealth of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17812F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17812F\"></sup>Damascus and the spoil of Samaria will be carried away before the king of Assyria.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Again the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke to me further, saying,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Inasmuch as these people have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17814G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17814G\"></sup>rejected the gently flowing waters of ShiloahAnd rejoice in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17814H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17814H\"></sup>Rezin and the son of Remaliah;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Now therefore, behold, the Lord is about to bring on them the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17815I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17815I\"></sup>strong and abundant waters of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17815J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17815J\"></sup>Euphrates,<i>Even</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17815K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17815K\"></sup>king of Assyria and all his glory;And it will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17815L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17815L\"></sup>rise up over all its channels and go over all its banks.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17816M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17816M\"></sup>it will sweep on into Judah, it will overflow and pass through,It will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17816N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17816N\"></sup>reach even to the neck;And the spread of its wings will fill the breadth of your land, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17816O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17816O\"></sup>Immanuel.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17817P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17817P\"></sup>Be broken, O peoples, and be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17817Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17817Q\"></sup>shattered;And give ear, all remote places of the earth.Gird yourselves, yet be shattered;Gird yourselves, yet be shattered.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17818R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17818R\"></sup>Devise a plan, but it will be thwarted;State a proposal, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17818S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17818S\"></sup>it will not stand,For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17818T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17818T\"></sup>God is with us.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For thus the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke to me with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17819U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17819U\"></sup>mighty power and instructed me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17819V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17819V\"></sup>not to walk in the way of this people, saying,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“You are not to say, ‘<i>It is</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17820W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17820W\"></sup>conspiracy!’In regard to all that this people call a conspiracy,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17820X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17820X\"></sup>you are not to fear what they fear or be in dread of <i>it</i>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“It is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17821Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17821Y\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17821Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17821Z\"></sup>whom you should regard as holy.And He shall be your fear,And He shall be your dread.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Then He shall become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17822AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17822AA\"></sup>sanctuary;But to both the houses of Israel, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17822AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17822AB\"></sup>stone to strike and a rock to stumble over,<i>And</i> a snare and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17822AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17822AC\"></sup>trap for the inhabitants of Jerusalem.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17823AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17823AD\"></sup>will stumble over them,Then they will fall and be broken;They will even be snared and caught.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17824AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17824AE\"></sup>Bind up the testimony, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17824AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17824AF\"></sup>seal the law among <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17824AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17824AG\"></sup>my disciples.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17825AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17825AH\"></sup>wait for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17825AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17825AI\"></sup>who is hiding His face from the house of Jacob; I will even look eagerly for Him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17826AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17826AJ\"></sup>Behold, I and the children whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has given me are for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17826AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17826AK\"></sup>signs and wonders in Israel from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17826AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17826AL\"></sup>dwells on Mount Zion.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When they say to you, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17827AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17827AM\"></sup>Consult the mediums and the spiritists who whisper and mutter,” should not a people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17827AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17827AN\"></sup>consult their God? <i>Should they</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17827AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17827AO\"></sup><i>consult</i> the dead on behalf of the living?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>To the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17828AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17828AP\"></sup>law and to the testimony! If they do not speak according to this word, it is because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17828AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17828AQ\"></sup>they have no dawn.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They will pass through the land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17829AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17829AR\"></sup>hard-pressed and famished, and it will turn out that when they are hungry, they will be enraged and curse their king and their God as they face upward.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17830AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17830AS\"></sup>look to the earth, and behold, distress and darkness, the gloom of anguish; and <i>they will be</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17830AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17830AT\"></sup>driven away into darkness."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>But there will be no <i>more</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17831A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17831A\"></sup>gloom for her who was in anguish; in earlier times He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17831B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17831B\"></sup>treated the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17831C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17831C\"></sup>land of Zebulun and the land of Naphtali with contempt, but later on He shall make <i>it</i> glorious, by the way of the sea, on the other side of Jordan, Galilee of the Gentiles.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17832D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17832D\"></sup>The people who walk in darknessWill see a great light;Those who live in a dark land,The light will shine on them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17833E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17833E\"></sup>You shall multiply the nation,You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17833F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17833F\"></sup>shall increase their gladness;They will be glad in Your presenceAs with the gladness of harvest,As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17833G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17833G\"></sup>men rejoice when they divide the spoil.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17834H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17834H\"></sup>You shall break the yoke of their burden and the staff on their shoulders,The rod of their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17834I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17834I\"></sup>oppressor, as at the battle of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17834J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17834J\"></sup>Midian.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For every boot of the booted warrior in the <i>battle</i> tumult,And cloak rolled in blood, will be for burning, fuel for the fire.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17836K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17836K\"></sup>child will be born to us, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17836L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17836L\"></sup>son will be given to us;And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17836M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17836M\"></sup>government will rest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17836N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17836N\"></sup>on His shoulders;And His name will be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17836O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17836O\"></sup>Wonderful Counselor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17836P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17836P\"></sup>Mighty God,Eternal <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17836Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17836Q\"></sup>Father, Prince of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17836R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17836R\"></sup>Peace.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>There will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17837S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17837S\"></sup>no end to the increase of <i>His</i> government or of peace,On the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17837T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17837T\"></sup>throne of David and over his kingdom,To establish it and to uphold it with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17837U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17837U\"></sup>justice and righteousnessFrom then on and forevermore.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17837V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17837V\"></sup>The zeal of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will accomplish this.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Lord sends a message against Jacob,And it falls on Israel.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And all the people know <i>it</i>,<i>That is</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17839W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17839W\"></sup>Ephraim and the inhabitants of Samaria,Asserting in pride and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17839X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17839X\"></sup>arrogance of heart:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“The bricks have fallen down,But we will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17840Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17840Y\"></sup>rebuild with smooth stones;The sycamores have been cut down,But we will replace <i>them</i> with cedars.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> raises against them adversaries from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17841Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17841Z\"></sup>RezinAnd spurs their enemies on,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The Arameans on the east and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17842AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17842AA\"></sup>Philistines on the west;And they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17842AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17842AB\"></sup>devour Israel with gaping jaws.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17842AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17842AC\"></sup>In <i>spite of</i> all this, His anger does not turn awayAnd His hand is still stretched out.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Yet the people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17843AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17843AD\"></sup>do not turn back to Him who struck them,Nor do they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17843AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17843AE\"></sup>seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> cuts off <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17844AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17844AF\"></sup>head and tail from Israel,<i>Both</i> palm branch and bulrush <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17844AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17844AG\"></sup>in a single day.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The head is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17845AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17845AH\"></sup>the elder and honorable man,And the prophet who teaches <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17845AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17845AI\"></sup>falsehood is the tail.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17846AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17846AJ\"></sup>For those who guide this people are leading <i>them</i> astray;And those who are guided by them are brought to confusion.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Therefore the Lord does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17847AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17847AK\"></sup>not take pleasure in their young men,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17847AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17847AL\"></sup>Nor does He have pity on their orphans or their widows;For every one of them is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17847AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17847AM\"></sup>godless and an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17847AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17847AN\"></sup>evildoer,And every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17847AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17847AO\"></sup>mouth is speaking foolishness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17847AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17847AP\"></sup>In <i>spite of</i> all this, His anger does not turn awayAnd His hand is still stretched out.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17848AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17848AQ\"></sup>For wickedness burns like a fire;It consumes briars and thorns;It even sets the thickets of the forest aflameAnd they roll upward in a column of smoke.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>By the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17849AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17849AR\"></sup>fury of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17849AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17849AS\"></sup>land is burned up,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17849AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17849AT\"></sup>people are like fuel for the fire;No <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17849AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17849AU\"></sup>man spares his brother.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>They slice off <i>what is</i> on the right hand but <i>still</i> are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17850AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17850AV\"></sup>hungry,And they eat <i>what is</i> on the left hand but they are not satisfied;Each of them eats the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17850AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17850AW\"></sup>flesh of his own arm.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Manasseh <i>devours</i> Ephraim, and Ephraim Manasseh,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17851AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17851AX\"></sup><i>And</i> together they are against Judah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17851AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17851AY\"></sup>In <i>spite of</i> all this, His anger does not turn awayAnd His hand is still stretched out."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Woe to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17852A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17852A\"></sup>enact evil statutesAnd to those who constantly record unjust decisions,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17853B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17853B\"></sup>to deprive the needy of justiceAnd rob the poor of My people of <i>their</i> rights,So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17853C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17853C\"></sup>that widows may be their spoilAnd that they may plunder the orphans.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17854D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17854D\"></sup>what will you do in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17854E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17854E\"></sup>day of punishment,And in the devastation which will come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17854F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17854F\"></sup>from afar?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17854G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17854G\"></sup>To whom will you flee for help?And where will you leave your wealth?",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Nothing <i>remains</i> but to crouch among the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17855H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17855H\"></sup>captivesOr fall among the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17855I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17855I\"></sup>slain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17855J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17855J\"></sup>In <i>spite of</i> all this, His anger does not turn awayAnd His hand is still stretched out.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Woe to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17856K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17856K\"></sup>Assyria, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17856L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17856L\"></sup>rod of My angerAnd the staff in whose hands is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17856M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17856M\"></sup>My indignation,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I send it against a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17857N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17857N\"></sup>godless nationAnd commission it against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17857O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17857O\"></sup>people of My furyTo capture booty and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17857P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17857P\"></sup>to seize plunder,And to trample them down like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17857Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17857Q\"></sup>mud in the streets.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Yet it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17858R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17858R\"></sup>does not so intend,Nor does it plan so in its heart,But rather it is its purpose to destroyAnd to cut off many nations.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For it says, “Are not my princes all kings?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17860S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17860S\"></sup>Calno like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17860T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17860T\"></sup>Carchemish,Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17860U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17860U\"></sup>Hamath like Arpad,Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17860V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17860V\"></sup>Samaria like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17860W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17860W\"></sup>Damascus?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“As my hand has reached to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17861X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17861X\"></sup>kingdoms of the idols,Whose graven images <i>were</i> greater than those of Jerusalem and Samaria,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Shall I not do to Jerusalem and her imagesJust as I have done to Samaria and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17862Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17862Y\"></sup>her idols?”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So it will be that when the Lord has completed all His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17863Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17863Z\"></sup>work on Mount Zion and on Jerusalem, <i>He will say</i>, “I will punish the fruit of the arrogant heart of the king of Assyria and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17863AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17863AA\"></sup>the pomp of his haughtiness.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17864AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17864AB\"></sup>he has said,“By the power of my hand and by my wisdom I did <i>this</i>,For I have understanding;And I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17864AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17864AC\"></sup>removed the boundaries of the peoplesAnd plundered their treasures,And like a mighty man I brought down <i>their</i> inhabitants,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And my hand reached to the riches of the peoples like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17865AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17865AD\"></sup>nest,And as one gathers abandoned eggs, I gathered all the earth;And there was not one that flapped its wing or opened <i>its</i> beak or chirped.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17866AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17866AE\"></sup>axe to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17866AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17866AF\"></sup>boast itself over the one who chops with it?Is the saw to exalt itself over the one who wields it?<i>That would be</i> like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17866AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17866AG\"></sup>a club wielding those who lift it,<i>Or</i> like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17866AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17866AH\"></sup>a rod lifting <i>him who</i> is not wood.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts, will send a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17867AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17867AI\"></sup>wasting disease among his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17867AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17867AJ\"></sup>stout warriors;And under his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17867AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17867AK\"></sup>glory a fire will be kindled like a burning flame.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17868AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17868AL\"></sup>light of Israel will become a fire and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17868AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17868AM\"></sup>Holy One a flame,And it will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17868AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17868AN\"></sup>burn and devour his thorns and his briars in a single day.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17869AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17869AO\"></sup>destroy the glory of his forest and of his fruitful garden, both soul and body,And it will be as when a sick man wastes away.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17870AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17870AP\"></sup>rest of the trees of his forest will be so small in numberThat a child could write them down.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now in that day the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17871AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17871AQ\"></sup>remnant of Israel, and those of the house of Jacob <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17871AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17871AR\"></sup>who have escaped, will never again rely on the one who struck them, but will truly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17871AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17871AS\"></sup>rely on the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the Holy One of Israel.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17872AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17872AT\"></sup>remnant will return, the remnant of Jacob, to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17872AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17872AU\"></sup>mighty God.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17873AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17873AV\"></sup>though your people, O Israel, may be like the sand of the sea,<i>Only</i> a remnant within them will return;A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17873AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17873AW\"></sup>destruction is determined, overflowing with righteousness.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For a complete destruction, one that is decreed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17874AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17874AX\"></sup>the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts will execute in the midst of the whole land.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts, “O My people who dwell in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17875AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17875AY\"></sup>Zion, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17875AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17875AZ\"></sup>do not fear the Assyrian who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17875BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17875BA\"></sup>strikes you with the rod and lifts up his staff against you, the way Egypt <i>did</i>.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For in a very <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17876BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17876BB\"></sup>little while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17876BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17876BC\"></sup>My indignation <i>against you</i> will be spent and My anger <i>will be directed</i> to their destruction.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17877BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17877BD\"></sup>arouse a scourge against him like the slaughter of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17877BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17877BE\"></sup>Midian at the rock of Oreb; and His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17877BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17877BF\"></sup>staff will be over the sea and He will lift it up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17877BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17877BG\"></sup>the way <i>He did</i> in Egypt.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>So it will be in that day, that his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17878BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17878BH\"></sup>burden will be removed from your shoulders and his yoke from your neck, and the yoke will be broken because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17878BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17878BI\"></sup>of fatness.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>He has come against Aiath,He has passed through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17879BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17879BJ\"></sup>Migron;At <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17879BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17879BK\"></sup>Michmash he deposited his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17879BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17879BL\"></sup>baggage.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>They have gone through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17880BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17880BM\"></sup>the pass, <i>saying</i>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17880BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17880BN\"></sup>Geba will be our lodging place.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17880BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17880BO\"></sup>Ramah is terrified, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17880BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17880BP\"></sup>Gibeah of Saul has fled away.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Cry aloud with your voice, O daughter of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17881BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17881BQ\"></sup>Gallim!Pay attention, Laishah <i>and</i> wretched <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17881BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17881BR\"></sup>Anathoth!",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Madmenah has fled.The inhabitants of Gebim have sought refuge.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Yet today he will halt at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17883BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17883BS\"></sup>Nob;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17883BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17883BT\"></sup>shakes his fist at the mountain of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17883BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17883BU\"></sup>daughter of Zion, the hill of Jerusalem.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Behold, the Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts, will lop off the boughs with a terrible crash;Those also who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17884BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17884BV\"></sup>tall in stature will be cut downAnd those who are lofty will be abased.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>He will cut down the thickets of the forest with an iron <i>axe</i>,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17885BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17885BW\"></sup>Lebanon will fall by the Mighty One."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Then a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17886A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17886A\"></sup>shoot will spring from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17886B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17886B\"></sup>stem of Jesse,And a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17886C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17886C\"></sup>branch from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17886D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17886D\"></sup>his roots will bear fruit.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17887E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17887E\"></sup>Spirit of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will rest on Him,The spirit of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17887F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17887F\"></sup>wisdom and understanding,The spirit of counsel and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17887G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17887G\"></sup>strength,The spirit of knowledge and the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And He will delight in the fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And He will not judge by what His eyes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17888H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17888H\"></sup>see,Nor make a decision by what His ears hear;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17889I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17889I\"></sup>righteousness He will judge the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17889J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17889J\"></sup>poor,And decide with fairness for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17889K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17889K\"></sup>afflicted of the earth;And He will strike the earth with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17889L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17889L\"></sup>rod of His mouth,And with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17889M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17889M\"></sup>breath of His lips He will slay the wicked.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17890N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17890N\"></sup>righteousness will be the belt about His loins,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17890O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17890O\"></sup>faithfulness the belt about His waist.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17891P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17891P\"></sup>wolf will dwell with the lamb,And the leopard will lie down with the young goat,And the calf and the young lion and the fatling together;And a little boy will lead them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Also the cow and the bear will graze,Their young will lie down together,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17892Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17892Q\"></sup>lion will eat straw like the ox.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The nursing child will play by the hole of the cobra,And the weaned child will put his hand on the viper’s den.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17894R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17894R\"></sup>not hurt or destroy in all My holy mountain,For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17894S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17894S\"></sup>earth will be full of the knowledge of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>As the waters cover the sea.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then in that dayThe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17895T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17895T\"></sup>nations will resort to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17895U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17895U\"></sup>root of Jesse,Who will stand as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17895V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17895V\"></sup>signal for the peoples;And His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17895W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17895W\"></sup>resting place will be glorious.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then it will happen on that day that the LordWill again recover the second time with His handThe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17896X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17896X\"></sup>remnant of His people, who will remain,From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17896Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17896Y\"></sup>Assyria, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17896Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17896Z\"></sup>Egypt, Pathros, Cush, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17896AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17896AA\"></sup>Elam, Shinar, Hamath,And from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17896AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17896AB\"></sup>islands of the sea.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And He will lift up a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17897AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17897AC\"></sup>standard for the nationsAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17897AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17897AD\"></sup>assemble the banished ones of Israel,And will gather the dispersed of JudahFrom the four corners of the earth.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17898AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17898AE\"></sup>jealousy of Ephraim will depart,And those who harass Judah will be cut off;Ephraim will not be jealous of Judah,And Judah will not harass Ephraim.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17899AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17899AF\"></sup>swoop down on the slopes of the Philistines on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17899AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17899AG\"></sup>west;Together they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17899AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17899AH\"></sup>plunder the sons of the east;They will possess <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17899AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17899AI\"></sup>Edom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17899AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17899AJ\"></sup>Moab,And the sons of Ammon will be subject to them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17900AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17900AK\"></sup>utterly destroyThe tongue of the Sea of Egypt;And He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17900AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17900AL\"></sup>wave His hand over the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17900AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17900AM\"></sup>RiverWith His scorching wind;And He will strike it into seven streamsAnd make <i>men</i> walk over dry-shod.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And there will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17901AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17901AN\"></sup>highway from AssyriaFor the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17901AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17901AO\"></sup>remnant of His people who will be left,Just as there was for IsraelIn <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17901AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17901AP\"></sup>the day that they came up out of the land of Egypt."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>Then you will say on that day,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17902A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17902A\"></sup>I will give thanks to You, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17902B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17902B\"></sup>although You were angry with me,Your anger is turned away,And You comfort me.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17903C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17903C\"></sup>God is my salvation,I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17903D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17903D\"></sup>trust and not be afraid;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17903E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17903E\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord God</span> is my strength and song,And He has become my salvation.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore you will joyously <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17904F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17904F\"></sup>draw waterFrom the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17904G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17904G\"></sup>springs of salvation.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And in that day you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17905H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17905H\"></sup>say,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17905I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17905I\"></sup>Give thanks to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, call on His name.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17905J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17905J\"></sup>Make known His deeds among the peoples;Make <i>them</i> remember that His name is exalted.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17906K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17906K\"></sup>Praise the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in song, for He has done excellent things;Let this be known throughout the earth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17907L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17907L\"></sup>Cry aloud and shout for joy, O inhabitant of Zion,For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17907M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17907M\"></sup>great in your midst is the Holy One of Israel."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17908A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17908A\"></sup>oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17908B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17908B\"></sup>Babylon which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17908C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17908C\"></sup>Isaiah the son of Amoz saw.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17909D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17909D\"></sup>Lift up a standard on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17909E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17909E\"></sup>bare hill,Raise your voice to them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17909F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17909F\"></sup>Wave the hand that they may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17909G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17909G\"></sup>enter the doors of the nobles.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I have commanded My consecrated ones,I have even called My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17910H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17910H\"></sup>mighty warriors,My proudly exulting ones,To <i>execute</i> My anger.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17911I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17911I\"></sup>sound of tumult on the mountains,Like that of many people!A sound of the uproar of kingdoms,Of nations gathered together!The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is mustering the army for battle.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They are coming from a far country,From the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17912J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17912J\"></sup>farthest horizons,The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and His instruments of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17912K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17912K\"></sup>indignation,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17912L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17912L\"></sup>destroy the whole land.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Wail, for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17913M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17913M\"></sup>day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is near!It will come as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17913N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17913N\"></sup>destruction from the Almighty.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17914O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17914O\"></sup>all hands will fall limp,And every man’s <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17914P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17914P\"></sup>heart will melt.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17915Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17915Q\"></sup>terrified,Pains and anguish will take hold of <i>them</i>;They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17915R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17915R\"></sup>writhe like a woman in labor,They will look at one another in astonishment,Their faces aflame.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17916S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17916S\"></sup>the day of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is coming,Cruel, with fury and burning anger,To make the land a desolation;And He will exterminate its sinners from it.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17917T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17917T\"></sup>stars of heaven and their constellationsWill not flash forth their light;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17917U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17917U\"></sup>sun will be dark when it risesAnd the moon will not shed its light.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Thus I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17918V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17918V\"></sup>punish the world for its evilAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17918W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17918W\"></sup>wicked for their iniquity;I will also put an end to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17918X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17918X\"></sup>arrogance of the proudAnd abase the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17918Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17918Y\"></sup>haughtiness of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17918Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17918Z\"></sup>ruthless.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will make mortal man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17919AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17919AA\"></sup>scarcer than pure goldAnd mankind than the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17919AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17919AB\"></sup>gold of Ophir.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore I will make the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17920AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17920AC\"></sup>heavens tremble,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17920AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17920AD\"></sup>the earth will be shaken from its placeAt the fury of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hostsIn <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17920AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17920AE\"></sup>the day of His burning anger.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And it will be that like a hunted gazelle,Or like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17921AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17921AF\"></sup>sheep with none to gather <i>them</i>,They will each turn to his own people,And each one flee to his own land.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Anyone who is found will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17922AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17922AG\"></sup>thrust through,And anyone who is captured will fall by the sword.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17923AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17923AH\"></sup>little ones also will be dashed to piecesBefore their eyes;Their houses will be plunderedAnd their wives ravished.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Behold, I am going to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17924AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17924AI\"></sup>stir up the Medes against them,Who will not value silver or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17924AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17924AJ\"></sup>take pleasure in gold.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And <i>their</i> bows will mow down the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17925AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17925AK\"></sup>young men,They will not even have compassion on the fruit of the womb,<i>Nor</i> will their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17925AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17925AL\"></sup>eye pity children.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17926AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17926AM\"></sup>Babylon, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17926AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17926AN\"></sup>beauty of kingdoms, the glory of the Chaldeans’ pride,Will be as when God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17926AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17926AO\"></sup>overthrew Sodom and Gomorrah.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>It will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17927AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17927AP\"></sup>never be inhabited or lived in from generation to generation;Nor will the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17927AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17927AQ\"></sup>Arab pitch <i>his</i> tent there,Nor will shepherds make <i>their flocks</i> lie down there.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17928AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17928AR\"></sup>desert creatures will lie down there,And their houses will be full of owls;Ostriches also will live there, and shaggy goats will frolic there.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Hyenas will howl in their fortified towersAnd jackals in their luxurious <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17929AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17929AS\"></sup>palaces.Her <i>fateful</i> time also will soon comeAnd her days will not be prolonged."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17930A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17930A\"></sup>have compassion on Jacob and again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17930B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17930B\"></sup>choose Israel, and settle them in their own land, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17930C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17930C\"></sup>strangers will join them and attach themselves to the house of Jacob.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The peoples will take them along and bring them to their place, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17931D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17931D\"></sup>house of Israel will possess them as an inheritance in the land of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17931E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17931E\"></sup>as male servants and female servants; and they will take their captors captive and will rule over their oppressors.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And it will be in the day when the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gives you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17932F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17932F\"></sup>rest from your pain and turmoil and harsh service in which you have been enslaved,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>that you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17933G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17933G\"></sup>take up this taunt against the king of Babylon, and say,“How <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17933H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17933H\"></sup>the oppressor has ceased,<i>And how</i> fury has ceased!",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has broken the staff of the wicked,The scepter of rulers",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17935I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17935I\"></sup>Which used to strike the peoples in fury with unceasing strokes,Which subdued the nations in anger with unrestrained persecution.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“The whole earth is at rest <i>and</i> is quiet;They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17936J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17936J\"></sup>break forth into shouts of joy.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Even the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17937K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17937K\"></sup>cypress trees rejoice over you, <i>and</i> the cedars of Lebanon, <i>saying</i>,‘Since you were laid low, no <i>tree</i> cutter comes up against us.’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17938L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17938L\"></sup>Sheol from beneath is excited over you to meet you when you come;It arouses for you the spirits of the dead, all the leaders of the earth;It raises all the kings of the nations from their thrones.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17939M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17939M\"></sup>They will all respond and say to you,‘Even you have been made weak as we,You have become like us.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>‘Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17940N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17940N\"></sup>pomp <i>and</i> the music of your harpsHave been brought down to Sheol;Maggots are spread out <i>as your bed</i> beneath youAnd worms are your covering.’",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“How you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17941O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17941O\"></sup>fallen from heaven,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17941P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17941P\"></sup>star of the morning, son of the dawn!You have been cut down to the earth,You who have weakened the nations!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“But you said in your heart,‘I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17942Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17942Q\"></sup>ascend to heaven;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17942R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17942R\"></sup>raise my throne above the stars of God,And I will sit on the mount of assemblyIn the recesses of the north.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>‘I will ascend above the heights of the clouds;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17943S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17943S\"></sup>I will make myself like the Most High.’",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Nevertheless you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17944T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17944T\"></sup>will be thrust down to Sheol,To the recesses of the pit.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Those who see you will gaze at you,They will ponder over you, <i>saying</i>,‘Is this the man who made the earth tremble,Who shook kingdoms,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Who made the world like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17946U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17946U\"></sup>wildernessAnd overthrew its cities,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17946V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17946V\"></sup>did not allow his prisoners to <i>go</i> home?’",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“All the kings of the nations lie in glory,Each in his own tomb.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“But you have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17948W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17948W\"></sup>cast out of your tombLike a rejected branch,Clothed with the slain who are pierced with a sword,Who go down to the stones of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17948X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17948X\"></sup>pitLike a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17948Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17948Y\"></sup>trampled corpse.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“You will not be united with them in burial,Because you have ruined your country,You have slain your people.May the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17949Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17949Z\"></sup>offspring of evildoers not be mentioned forever.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Prepare for his sons a place of slaughterBecause of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17950AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17950AA\"></sup>iniquity of their fathers.They must not arise and take possession of the earthAnd fill the face of the world with cities.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“I will rise up against them,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “and will cut off from Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17951AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17951AB\"></sup>name and survivors, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17951AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17951AC\"></sup>offspring and posterity,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“I will also make it a possession for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17952AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17952AD\"></sup>hedgehog and swamps of water, and I will sweep it with the broom of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17952AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17952AE\"></sup>destruction,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has sworn saying, “Surely, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17953AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17953AF\"></sup>just as I have intended so it has happened, and just as I have planned so it will stand,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17954AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17954AG\"></sup>break Assyria in My land, and I will trample him on My mountains. Then his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17954AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17954AH\"></sup>yoke will be removed from them and his burden removed from their shoulder.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>This is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17955AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17955AI\"></sup>plan devised against the whole earth; and this is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17955AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17955AJ\"></sup>hand that is stretched out against all the nations.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17956AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17956AK\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has planned, and who can frustrate <i>it</i>? And as for His stretched-out hand, who can turn it back?”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17957AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17957AL\"></sup>year that King Ahaz died this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17957AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17957AM\"></sup>oracle came:",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Do not rejoice, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17958AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17958AN\"></sup>Philistia, all of you,Because the rod that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17958AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17958AO\"></sup>struck you is broken;For from the serpent’s root a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17958AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17958AP\"></sup>viper will come out,And its fruit will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17958AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17958AQ\"></sup>flying serpent.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Those who are most <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17959AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17959AR\"></sup>helpless will eat,And the needy will lie down in security;I will destroy your root with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17959AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17959AS\"></sup>famine,And it will kill off your survivors.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“Wail, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17960AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17960AT\"></sup>gate; cry, O city;Melt away, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17960AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17960AU\"></sup>Philistia, all of you;For smoke comes from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17960AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17960AV\"></sup>north,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17960AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17960AW\"></sup>there is no straggler in his ranks.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“How then will one answer the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17961AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17961AX\"></sup>messengers of the nation?That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17961AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17961AY\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has founded Zion,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17961AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17961AZ\"></sup>the afflicted of His people will seek refuge in it.”"
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>The oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17962A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17962A\"></sup>Moab.Surely in a night <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17962B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17962B\"></sup>Ar of Moab is devastated <i>and</i> ruined;Surely in a night Kir of Moab is devastated <i>and</i> ruined.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>They have gone up to the temple and <i>to</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17963C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17963C\"></sup>Dibon, <i>even</i> to the high places to weep.Moab wails over Nebo and Medeba;Everyone’s head is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17963D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17963D\"></sup>bald <i>and</i> every beard is cut off.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>In their streets they have girded themselves with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17964E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17964E\"></sup>sackcloth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17964F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17964F\"></sup>On their housetops and in their squaresEveryone is wailing, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17964G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17964G\"></sup>dissolved in tears.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17965H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17965H\"></sup>Heshbon and Elealeh also cry out,Their voice is heard all the way to Jahaz;Therefore the armed men of Moab cry aloud;His soul trembles within him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>My heart cries out for Moab;His fugitives are as far as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17966I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17966I\"></sup>Zoar <i>and</i> Eglath-shelishiyah,For they go up the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17966J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17966J\"></sup>ascent of Luhith weeping;Surely on the road to Horonaim they raise a cry of distress <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17966K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17966K\"></sup>over <i>their</i> ruin.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17967L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17967L\"></sup>waters of Nimrim are desolate.Surely the grass is withered, the tender grass died out,There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17967M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17967M\"></sup>no green thing.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17968N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17968N\"></sup>abundance <i>which</i> they have acquired and stored upThey carry off over the brook of Arabim.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For the cry of distress has gone around the territory of Moab,Its wail <i>goes</i> as far as Eglaim and its wailing even to Beer-elim.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For the waters of Dimon are full of blood;Surely I will bring added <i>woes</i> upon Dimon,A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17970O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17970O\"></sup>lion upon the fugitives of Moab and upon the remnant of the land."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17971A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17971A\"></sup>Send the <i>tribute</i> lamb to the ruler of the land,From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17971B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17971B\"></sup>Sela by way of the wilderness to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17971C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17971C\"></sup>mountain of the daughter of Zion.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then, like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17972D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17972D\"></sup>fleeing birds <i>or</i> scattered nestlings,The daughters of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17972E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17972E\"></sup>Moab will be at the fords of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17972F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17972F\"></sup>Arnon.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Give <i>us</i> advice, make a decision;Cast your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17973G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17973G\"></sup>shadow like night at high noon;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17973H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17973H\"></sup>Hide the outcasts, do not betray the fugitive.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Let the outcasts of Moab stay with you;Be a hiding place to them from the destroyer.”For the extortioner has come to an end, destruction has ceased,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17974I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17974I\"></sup>Oppressors have completely <i>disappeared</i> from the land.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17975J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17975J\"></sup>throne will even be established in lovingkindness,And a judge will sit on it in faithfulness in the tent of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17975K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17975K\"></sup>David;Moreover, he will seek justiceAnd be prompt in righteousness.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17976L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17976L\"></sup>We have heard of the pride of Moab, an excessive pride;<i>Even</i> of his arrogance, pride, and fury;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17976M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17976M\"></sup>His idle boasts are false.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore Moab will wail; everyone of Moab will wail.You will moan for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17977N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17977N\"></sup>raisin cakes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17977O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17977O\"></sup>Kir-haresethAs those who are utterly stricken.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For the fields of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17978P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17978P\"></sup>Heshbon have withered, the vines of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17978Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17978Q\"></sup>Sibmah <i>as well</i>;The lords of the nations have trampled down its choice clustersWhich reached as far as Jazer <i>and</i> wandered to the deserts;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17978R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17978R\"></sup>Its tendrils spread themselves out <i>and</i> passed over the sea.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Therefore I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17979S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17979S\"></sup>weep bitterly for Jazer, for the vine of Sibmah;I will drench you with my tears, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17979T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17979T\"></sup>Heshbon and Elealeh;For the shouting over your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17979U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17979U\"></sup>summer fruits and your harvest has fallen away.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17980V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17980V\"></sup>Gladness and joy are taken away from the fruitful field;In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17980W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17980W\"></sup>vineyards also there will be no cries of joy or jubilant shouting,No <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17980X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17980X\"></sup>treader treads out wine in the presses,<i>For</i> I have made the shouting to cease.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17981Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17981Y\"></sup>heart intones like a harp for MoabAnd my inward feelings for Kir-hareseth.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>So it will come about when Moab <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17982Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17982Z\"></sup>presents himself,When he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17982AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17982AA\"></sup>wearies himself upon <i>his</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17982AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17982AB\"></sup>high placeAnd comes to his sanctuary to pray,That he will not prevail.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>This is the word which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke earlier concerning Moab.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But now the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> speaks, saying, “Within three years, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17984AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17984AC\"></sup>a hired man would count them, the glory of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17984AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17984AD\"></sup>Moab will be degraded along with all <i>his</i> great population, and <i>his</i> remnant will be very small <i>and</i> impotent.”"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17985A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17985A\"></sup>oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17985B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17985B\"></sup>Damascus.“Behold, Damascus is about to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17985C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17985C\"></sup>removed from being a cityAnd will become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17985D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17985D\"></sup>fallen ruin.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“The cities of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17986E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17986E\"></sup>Aroer are forsaken;They will be for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17986F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17986F\"></sup>flocks to lie down in,And there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17986G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17986G\"></sup>no one to frighten <i>them</i>.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17987H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17987H\"></sup>fortified city will disappear from Ephraim,And sovereignty from DamascusAnd the remnant of Aram;They will be like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17987I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17987I\"></sup>glory of the sons of Israel,”Declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now in that day the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17988J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17988J\"></sup>glory of Jacob will fade,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17988K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17988K\"></sup>the fatness of his flesh will become lean.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>It will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17989L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17989L\"></sup>even like the reaper gathering the standing grain,As his arm harvests the ears,Or it will be like one gleaning ears of grainIn the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17989M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17989M\"></sup>valley of Rephaim.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17990N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17990N\"></sup>gleanings will be left in it like the shaking of an olive tree,Two <i>or</i> three olives on the topmost bough,Four <i>or</i> five on the branches of a fruitful tree,Declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>In that day man will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17991O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17991O\"></sup>have regard for his MakerAnd his eyes will look to the Holy One of Israel.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He will not have regard for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17992P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17992P\"></sup>altars, the work of his hands,Nor will he look to that which his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17992Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17992Q\"></sup>fingers have made,Even the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17992R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17992R\"></sup>Asherim and incense stands.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>In that day their strong cities will be like forsaken places in the forest,Or like branches which they abandoned before the sons of Israel;And the land will be a desolation.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17994S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17994S\"></sup>you have forgotten the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17994T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17994T\"></sup>God of your salvationAnd have not remembered the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17994U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17994U\"></sup>rock of your refuge.Therefore you plant delightful plantsAnd set them with vine slips of a strange <i>god</i>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>In the day that you plant <i>it</i> you carefully fence <i>it</i> in,And in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17995V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17995V\"></sup>morning you bring your seed to blossom;<i>But</i> the harvest will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17995W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17995W\"></sup><i>be</i> a heapIn a day of sickliness and incurable pain.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Alas, the uproar of many peoples<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17996X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17996X\"></sup>Who roar like the roaring of the seas,And the rumbling of nationsWho rush on like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17996Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17996Y\"></sup>rumbling of mighty waters!",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17997Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17997Z\"></sup>nations rumble on like the rumbling of many waters,But He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17997AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17997AA\"></sup>rebuke them and they will flee far away,And be chased <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17997AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17997AB\"></sup>like chaff in the mountains before the wind,Or like whirling dust before a gale.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>At evening time, behold, <i>there is</i> terror!Before morning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17998AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17998AC\"></sup>they are no more.Such <i>will be</i> the portion of those who plunder usAnd the lot of those who pillage us."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>Alas, oh land of whirring wingsWhich lies beyond the rivers of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-17999A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-17999A\"></sup>Cush,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Which sends envoys by the sea,Even in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18000B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18000B\"></sup>papyrus vessels on the surface of the waters.Go, swift messengers, to a nation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18000C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18000C\"></sup>tall and smooth,To a people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18000D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18000D\"></sup>feared far and wide,A powerful and oppressive nationWhose land the rivers divide.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18001E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18001E\"></sup>All you inhabitants of the world and dwellers on earth,As soon as a standard is raised on the mountains, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18001F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18001F\"></sup>you will see <i>it</i>,And as soon as the trumpet is blown, you will hear <i>it</i>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For thus the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has told me,“I will look from My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18002G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18002G\"></sup>dwelling place quietlyLike dazzling heat in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18002H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18002H\"></sup>sunshine,Like a cloud of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18002I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18002I\"></sup>dew in the heat of harvest.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18003J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18003J\"></sup>before the harvest, as soon as the bud blossomsAnd the flower becomes a ripening grape,Then He will cut off the sprigs with pruning knivesAnd remove <i>and</i> cut away the spreading branches.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They will be left together for mountain birds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18004K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18004K\"></sup>of prey,And for the beasts of the earth;And the birds of prey will spend the summer <i>feeding</i> on them,And all the beasts of the earth will spend harvest time on them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>At that time a gift of homage will be brought to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hostsFrom a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18005L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18005L\"></sup>people tall and smooth,Even from a people feared far and wide,A powerful and oppressive nation,Whose land the rivers divide—To the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18005M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18005M\"></sup>place of the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, <i>even</i> Mount Zion."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18006A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18006A\"></sup>oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18006B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18006B\"></sup>Egypt.Behold, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18006C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18006C\"></sup>riding on a swift cloud and is about to come to Egypt;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18006D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18006D\"></sup>idols of Egypt will tremble at His presence,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18006E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18006E\"></sup>heart of the Egyptians will melt within them.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“So I will incite Egyptians against Egyptians;And they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18007F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18007F\"></sup>each fight against his brother and each against his neighbor,City against city <i>and</i> kingdom against kingdom.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Then the spirit of the Egyptians will be demoralized within them;And I will confound their strategy,So that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18008G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18008G\"></sup>they will resort to idols and ghosts of the deadAnd to mediums and spiritists.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Moreover, I will deliver the Egyptians into the hand of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18009H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18009H\"></sup>cruel master,And a mighty king will rule over them,” declares the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18010I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18010I\"></sup>The waters from the sea will dry up,And the river will be parched and dry.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18011J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18011J\"></sup>canals will emit a stench,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18011K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18011K\"></sup>streams of Egypt will thin out and dry up;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18011L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18011L\"></sup>The reeds and rushes will rot away.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The bulrushes by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18012M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18012M\"></sup>Nile, by the edge of the NileAnd all the sown fields by the NileWill become dry, be driven away, and be no more.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18013N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18013N\"></sup>fishermen will lament,And all those who cast a line into the Nile will mourn,And those who spread nets on the waters will pine away.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Moreover, the manufacturers of linen made from combed flaxAnd the weavers of white <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18014O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18014O\"></sup>cloth will be utterly dejected.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18015P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18015P\"></sup>pillars <i>of Egypt</i> will be crushed;All the hired laborers will be grieved in soul.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The princes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18016Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18016Q\"></sup>Zoan are mere fools;The advice of Pharaoh’s wisest advisers has become stupid.How can you <i>men</i> say to Pharaoh,“I am a son of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18016R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18016R\"></sup>wise, a son of ancient kings”?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Well then, where are your wise men?Please let them tell you,And let them understand what the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hostsHas <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18017S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18017S\"></sup>purposed against Egypt.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The princes of Zoan have acted foolishly,The princes of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18018T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18018T\"></sup>Memphis are deluded;<i>Those who are</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18018U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18018U\"></sup>cornerstone of her tribesHave led Egypt astray.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has mixed within her a spirit of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18019V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18019V\"></sup>distortion;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18019W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18019W\"></sup>They have led Egypt astray in all that it does,As a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18019X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18019X\"></sup>drunken man staggers in his vomit.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>There will be no work for Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18020Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18020Y\"></sup>Which <i>its</i> head or tail, <i>its</i> palm branch or bulrush, may do.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>In that day the Egyptians will become like women, and they will tremble and be in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18021Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18021Z\"></sup>dread because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18021AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18021AA\"></sup>waving of the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, which He is going to wave over them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The land of Judah will become a terror to Egypt; everyone to whom it is mentioned will be in dread of it, because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18022AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18022AB\"></sup>purpose of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts which He is purposing against them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In that day five cities in the land of Egypt will be speaking the language of Canaan and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18023AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18023AC\"></sup>swearing <i>allegiance</i> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts; one will be called the City of Destruction.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>In that day there will be an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18024AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18024AD\"></sup>altar to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the midst of the land of Egypt, and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18024AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18024AE\"></sup>pillar to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> near its border.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>It will become a sign and a witness to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts in the land of Egypt; for they will cry to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> because of oppressors, and He will send them a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18025AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18025AF\"></sup>Savior and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18025AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18025AG\"></sup>Champion, and He will deliver them.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Thus the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will make Himself known to Egypt, and the Egyptians will know the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in that day. They will even worship with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18026AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18026AH\"></sup>sacrifice and offering, and will make a vow to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and perform it.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will strike Egypt, striking but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18027AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18027AI\"></sup>healing; so they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18027AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18027AJ\"></sup>return to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and He will respond to them and will heal them.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>In that day there will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18028AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18028AK\"></sup>highway from Egypt to Assyria, and the Assyrians will come into Egypt and the Egyptians into Assyria, and the Egyptians will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18028AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18028AL\"></sup>worship with the Assyrians.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>In that day Israel will be the third <i>party</i> with Egypt and Assyria, a blessing in the midst of the earth,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>whom the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has blessed, saying, “Blessed is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18030AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18030AM\"></sup>Egypt My people, and Assyria <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18030AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18030AN\"></sup>the work of My hands, and Israel My inheritance.”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>In the year that the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18031A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18031A\"></sup>commander came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18031B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18031B\"></sup>Ashdod, when Sargon the king of Assyria sent him and he fought against Ashdod and captured it,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>at that time the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> spoke through <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18032C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18032C\"></sup>Isaiah the son of Amoz, saying, “Go and loosen the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18032D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18032D\"></sup>sackcloth from your hips and take your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18032E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18032E\"></sup>shoes off your feet.” And he did so, going <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18032F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18032F\"></sup>naked and barefoot.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “Even as My servant Isaiah has gone naked and barefoot three years as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18033G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18033G\"></sup>sign and token against Egypt and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18033H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18033H\"></sup>Cush,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>so the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18034I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18034I\"></sup>king of Assyria will lead away the captives of Egypt and the exiles of Cush, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18034J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18034J\"></sup>young and old, naked and barefoot with buttocks uncovered, to the shame of Egypt.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18035K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18035K\"></sup>dismayed and ashamed because of Cush their hope and Egypt their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18035L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18035L\"></sup>boast.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So the inhabitants of this coastland will say in that day, ‘Behold, such is our hope, where we fled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18036M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18036M\"></sup>for help to be delivered from the king of Assyria; and we, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18036N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18036N\"></sup>how shall we escape?’”"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18037A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18037A\"></sup>oracle concerning the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18037B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18037B\"></sup>wilderness of the sea.As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18037C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18037C\"></sup>windstorms in the Negev sweep on,It comes from the wilderness, from a terrifying land.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18038D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18038D\"></sup>harsh vision has been shown to me;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18038E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18038E\"></sup>treacherous one <i>still</i> deals treacherously, and the destroyer <i>still</i> destroys.Go up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18038F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18038F\"></sup>Elam, lay siege, Media;I have made an end of all the groaning she has caused.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For this reason my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18039G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18039G\"></sup>loins are full of anguish;Pains have seized me like the pains of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18039H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18039H\"></sup>woman in labor.I am so bewildered I cannot hear, so terrified I cannot see.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>My mind reels, horror overwhelms me;The twilight I longed for has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18040I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18040I\"></sup>turned for me into trembling.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18041J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18041J\"></sup>set the table, they spread out the cloth, they eat, they drink;“Rise up, captains, oil the shields,”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For thus the Lord says to me,“Go, station the lookout, let him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18042K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18042K\"></sup>report what he sees.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“When he sees <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18043L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18043L\"></sup>riders, horsemen in pairs,A train of donkeys, a train of camels,Let him pay close attention, very close attention.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the lookout called,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18044M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18044M\"></sup>O Lord, I stand continually by day on the watchtower,And I am stationed every night at my guard post.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Now behold, here comes a troop of riders, horsemen in pairs.”And one said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18045N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18045N\"></sup>Fallen, fallen is Babylon;And all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18045O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18045O\"></sup>images of her gods are shattered on the ground.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>O my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18046P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18046P\"></sup>threshed <i>people</i>, and my afflicted of the threshing floor!What I have heard from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,The God of Israel, I make known to you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18047Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18047Q\"></sup>Edom.One keeps calling to me from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18047R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18047R\"></sup>Seir,“Watchman, how far gone is the night?Watchman, how far gone is the night?”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The watchman says,“Morning comes but also night.If you would inquire, inquire;Come back again.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The oracle about <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18049S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18049S\"></sup>Arabia.In the thickets of Arabia you must spend the night,O caravans of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18049T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18049T\"></sup>Dedanites.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Bring water for the thirsty,O inhabitants of the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18050U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18050U\"></sup>Tema,Meet the fugitive with bread.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18051V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18051V\"></sup>fled from the swords,From the drawn sword, and from the bent bowAnd from the press of battle.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For thus the Lord said to me, “In a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18052W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18052W\"></sup>year, as a hired man would count it, all the splendor of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18052X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18052X\"></sup>Kedar will terminate;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18053Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18053Y\"></sup>remainder of the number of bowmen, the mighty men of the sons of Kedar, will be few; for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God of Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18053Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18053Z\"></sup>has spoken.”"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>The oracle concerning the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18054A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18054A\"></sup>valley of vision.What is the matter with you now, that you have all gone up to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18054B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18054B\"></sup>housetops?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>You who were full of noise,You boisterous town, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18055C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18055C\"></sup>exultant city;Your slain were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18055D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18055D\"></sup>not slain with the sword,Nor did they die in battle.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18056E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18056E\"></sup>All your rulers have fled together,<i>And</i> have been captured without the bow;All of you who were found were taken captive together,Though they had fled far away.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Therefore I say, “Turn your eyes away from me,Let me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18057F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18057F\"></sup>weep bitterly,Do not try to comfort me concerning the destruction of the daughter of my people.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18058G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18058G\"></sup>For the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts has a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18058H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18058H\"></sup>day of panic, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18058I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18058I\"></sup>subjugation and confusion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18058J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18058J\"></sup>In the valley of vision,A breaking down of wallsAnd a crying to the mountain.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18059K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18059K\"></sup>Elam took up the quiverWith the chariots, infantry <i>and</i> horsemen;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18059L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18059L\"></sup>Kir uncovered the shield.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then your choicest valleys were full of chariots,And the horsemen took up fixed positions at the gate.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And He removed the defense of Judah.In that day you depended on the weapons of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18061M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18061M\"></sup>house of the forest,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And you saw that the breachesIn the <i>wall</i> of the city of David were many;And you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18062N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18062N\"></sup>collected the waters of the lower pool.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then you counted the houses of JerusalemAnd tore down houses to fortify the wall.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And you made a reservoir <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18064O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18064O\"></sup>between the two wallsFor the waters of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18064P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18064P\"></sup>old pool.But you did not depend on Him who made it,Nor did you take into consideration Him who planned it long ago.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore in that day the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts called <i>you</i> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18065Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18065Q\"></sup>weeping, to wailing,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18065R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18065R\"></sup>shaving the head and to wearing sackcloth.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Instead, there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18066S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18066S\"></sup>gaiety and gladness,Killing of cattle and slaughtering of sheep,Eating of meat and drinking of wine:“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18066T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18066T\"></sup>Let us eat and drink, for tomorrow we may die.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts revealed Himself to me,“Surely this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18067U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18067U\"></sup>iniquity <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18067V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18067V\"></sup>shall not be forgiven you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18067W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18067W\"></sup>Until you die,” says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hosts,“Come, go to this steward,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18068X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18068X\"></sup>Shebna, who is in charge of the <i>royal</i> household,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>‘What right do you have here,And whom do you have here,That you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18069Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18069Y\"></sup>hewn a tomb for yourself here,You who hew a tomb on the height,You who carve a resting place for yourself in the rock?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>‘Behold, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is about to hurl you headlong, O man.And He is about to grasp you firmly",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><i>And</i> roll you tightly like a ball,<i>To be</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18071Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18071Z\"></sup><i>cast</i> into a vast country;There you will dieAnd there your splendid chariots will be,You shame of your master’s house.’",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18072AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18072AA\"></sup>depose you from your office,And I will pull you down from your station.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Then it will come about in that day,That I will summon My servant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18073AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18073AB\"></sup>Eliakim the son of Hilkiah,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And I will clothe him with your tunicAnd tie your sash securely about him.I will entrust him with your authority,And he will become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18074AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18074AC\"></sup>father to the inhabitants of Jerusalem and to the house of Judah.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Then I will set <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18075AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18075AD\"></sup>the key of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18075AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18075AE\"></sup>house of David on his shoulder,When he opens no one will shut,When he shuts no one will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18075AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18075AF\"></sup>open.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“I will drive him <i>like</i> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18076AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18076AG\"></sup>peg in a firm place,And he will become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18076AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18076AH\"></sup>throne of glory to his father’s house.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>So they will hang on him all the glory of his father’s house, offspring and issue, all the least of vessels, from bowls to all the jars.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>In that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, “the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18078AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18078AI\"></sup>peg driven in a firm place will give way; it will even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18078AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18078AJ\"></sup>break off and fall, and the load hanging on it will be cut off, for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18078AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18078AK\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span>The oracle concerning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18079A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18079A\"></sup>Tyre.Wail, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18079B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18079B\"></sup>ships of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18079C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18079C\"></sup>Tarshish,For <i>Tyre</i> is destroyed, without house <i>or</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18079D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18079D\"></sup>harbor;It is reported to them from the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18079E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18079E\"></sup>Cyprus.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18080F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18080F\"></sup>Be silent, you inhabitants of the coastland,You merchants of Sidon;Your messengers crossed the sea",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And <i>were</i> on many waters.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18081G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18081G\"></sup>The grain of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18081H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18081H\"></sup>Nile, the harvest of the River was her revenue;And she was the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18081I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18081I\"></sup>market of nations.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Be ashamed, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18082J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18082J\"></sup>Sidon;For the sea speaks, the stronghold of the sea, saying,“I have neither travailed nor given birth,I have neither brought up young men <i>nor</i> reared virgins.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When the report <i>reaches</i> Egypt,They will be in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18083K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18083K\"></sup>anguish at the report of Tyre.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Pass over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18084L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18084L\"></sup>Tarshish;Wail, O inhabitants of the coastland.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Is this your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18085M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18085M\"></sup>jubilant <i>city</i>,Whose origin is from antiquity,Whose feet used to carry her to colonize distant places?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Who has planned this against Tyre, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18086N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18086N\"></sup>the bestower of crowns,Whose merchants were princes, whose traders were the honored of the earth?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18087O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18087O\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts has planned it, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18087P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18087P\"></sup>defile the pride of all beauty,To despise all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18087Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18087Q\"></sup>honored of the earth.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Overflow your land like the Nile, O daughter of Tarshish,There is no more restraint.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18089R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18089R\"></sup>stretched His hand out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18089S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18089S\"></sup>over the sea,He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18089T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18089T\"></sup>made the kingdoms tremble;The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has given a command concerning Canaan to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18089U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18089U\"></sup>demolish its strongholds.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He has said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18090V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18090V\"></sup>You shall exult no more, O crushed virgin daughter of Sidon.Arise, pass over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18090W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18090W\"></sup>Cyprus; even there you will find no rest.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Behold, the land of the Chaldeans—this is the people <i>which</i> was not; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18091X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18091X\"></sup>Assyria appointed it for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18091Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18091Y\"></sup>desert creatures—they erected their siege towers, they stripped its palaces, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18091Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18091Z\"></sup>they made it a ruin.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Wail, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18092AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18092AA\"></sup>ships of Tarshish,For your stronghold is destroyed.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Now in that day Tyre will be forgotten for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18093AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18093AB\"></sup>seventy years like the days of one king. At the end of seventy years it will happen to Tyre as <i>in</i> the song of the harlot:",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Take <i>your</i> harp, walk about the city,O forgotten harlot;Pluck the strings skillfully, sing many songs,That you may be remembered.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>It will come about at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18095AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18095AC\"></sup>the end of seventy years that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will visit Tyre. Then she will go back to her harlot’s wages and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18095AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18095AD\"></sup>play the harlot with all the kingdoms on the face of the earth.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18096AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18096AE\"></sup>gain and her harlot’s wages will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18096AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18096AF\"></sup>set apart to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>; it will not be stored up or hoarded, but her gain will become sufficient food and choice attire for those who dwell in the presence of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span>Behold, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18097A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18097A\"></sup>lays the earth waste, devastates it, distorts its surface and scatters its inhabitants.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the people will be like the priest, the servant like his master, the maid like her mistress, the buyer like the seller, the lender like the borrower, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18098B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18098B\"></sup>creditor like the debtor.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The earth will be completely laid waste and completely despoiled, for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken this word.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18100C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18100C\"></sup>earth mourns <i>and</i> withers, the world fades <i>and</i> withers, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18100D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18100D\"></sup>exalted of the people of the earth fade away.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The earth is also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18101E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18101E\"></sup>polluted by its inhabitants, for they transgressed laws, violated statutes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18101F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18101F\"></sup>broke the everlasting covenant.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18102G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18102G\"></sup>curse devours the earth, and those who live in it are held guilty. Therefore, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18102H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18102H\"></sup>inhabitants of the earth are burned, and few men are left.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18103I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18103I\"></sup>new wine mourns,The vine decays,All the merry-hearted sigh.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18104J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18104J\"></sup>gaiety of tambourines ceases,The noise of revelers stops,The gaiety of the harp ceases.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They do not drink wine with song;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18105K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18105K\"></sup>Strong drink is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18105L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18105L\"></sup>bitter to those who drink it.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18106M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18106M\"></sup>city of chaos is broken down;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18106N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18106N\"></sup>Every house is shut up so that none may enter.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>There is an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18107O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18107O\"></sup>outcry in the streets concerning the wine;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18107P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18107P\"></sup>All joy turns to gloom.The gaiety of the earth is banished.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Desolation is left in the cityAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18108Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18108Q\"></sup>gate is battered to ruins.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18109R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18109R\"></sup>thus it will be in the midst of the earth among the peoples,As the shaking of an olive tree,As the gleanings when the grape harvest is over.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18110S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18110S\"></sup>They raise their voices, they shout for joy;They cry out from the west concerning the majesty of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18111T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18111T\"></sup>glorify the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the east,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18111U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18111U\"></sup>name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel,In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18111V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18111V\"></sup>coastlands of the sea.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>From the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18112W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18112W\"></sup>ends of the earth we hear songs, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18112X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18112X\"></sup>Glory to the Righteous One,”But I say, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18112Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18112Y\"></sup>Woe to me! Woe to me! Alas for me!The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18112Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18112Z\"></sup>treacherous deal treacherously,And the treacherous deal very treacherously.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18113AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18113AA\"></sup>Terror and pit and snareConfront you, O inhabitant of the earth.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then it will be that he who flees the report of disaster will fall into the pit,And he who climbs out of the pit will be caught in the snare;For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18114AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18114AB\"></sup>windows above are opened, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18114AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18114AC\"></sup>foundations of the earth shake.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18115AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18115AD\"></sup>The earth is broken asunder,The earth is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18115AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18115AE\"></sup>split through,The earth is shaken violently.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18116AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18116AF\"></sup>reels to and fro like a drunkardAnd it totters like a shack,For its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18116AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18116AG\"></sup>transgression is heavy upon it,And it will fall, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18116AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18116AH\"></sup>never to rise again.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So it will happen in that day,That the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18117AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18117AI\"></sup>punish the host of heaven on high,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18117AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18117AJ\"></sup>kings of the earth on earth.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>They will be gathered together<i>Like</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18118AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18118AK\"></sup>prisoners in the dungeon,And will be confined in prison;And after many days they <i>will</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18118AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18118AL\"></sup><i>be</i> punished.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18119AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18119AM\"></sup>moon will be abashed and the sun ashamed,For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18119AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18119AN\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will reign on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18119AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18119AO\"></sup>Mount Zion and in Jerusalem,And <i>His</i> glory will be before His elders."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18120A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18120A\"></sup>my God;I will exalt You, I will give thanks to Your name;For You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18120B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18120B\"></sup>worked wonders,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18120C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18120C\"></sup>Plans <i>formed</i> long ago, with perfect faithfulness.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For You have made a city into a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18121D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18121D\"></sup>heap,A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18121E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18121E\"></sup>fortified city into a ruin;A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18121F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18121F\"></sup>palace of strangers is a city no more,It will never be rebuilt.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore a strong people will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18122G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18122G\"></sup>glorify You;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18122H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18122H\"></sup>Cities of ruthless nations will revere You.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For You have been a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18123I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18123I\"></sup>defense for the helpless,A defense for the needy in his distress,A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18123J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18123J\"></sup>refuge from the storm, a shade from the heat;For the breath of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18123K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18123K\"></sup>ruthlessIs like a <i>rain</i> storm <i>against</i> a wall.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Like heat in drought, You subdue the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18124L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18124L\"></sup>uproar of aliens;<i>Like</i> heat by the shadow of a cloud, the song of the ruthless is silenced.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18125M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18125M\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will prepare a lavish banquet for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18125N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18125N\"></sup>all peoples on this mountain;A banquet of aged wine, choice pieces with marrow,<i>And</i> refined, aged wine.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And on this mountain He will swallow up the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18126O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18126O\"></sup>covering which is over all peoples,Even the veil which is stretched over all nations.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18127P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18127P\"></sup>swallow up death for all time,And the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18127Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18127Q\"></sup>wipe tears away from all faces,And He will remove the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18127R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18127R\"></sup>reproach of His people from all the earth;For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And it will be said in that day,“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18128S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18128S\"></sup>this is our God for whom we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18128T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18128T\"></sup>waited that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18128U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18128U\"></sup>He might save us.This is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> for whom we have waited;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18128V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18128V\"></sup>Let us rejoice and be glad in His salvation.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will rest on this mountain,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18129W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18129W\"></sup>Moab will be trodden down in his placeAs straw is trodden down in the water of a manure pile.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18130X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18130X\"></sup>spread out his hands in the middle of itAs a swimmer spreads out <i>his hands</i> to swim,But <i>the Lord</i> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18130Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18130Y\"></sup>lay low his pride together with the trickery of his hands.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18131Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18131Z\"></sup>unassailable fortifications of your walls He will bring down,Lay low <i>and</i> cast to the ground, even to the dust."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18132A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18132A\"></sup>In that day this song will be sung in the land of Judah:“We have a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18132B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18132B\"></sup>strong city;He sets up walls and ramparts for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18132C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18132C\"></sup>security.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Open the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18133D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18133D\"></sup>gates, that the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18133E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18133E\"></sup>righteous nation may enter,The one that remains faithful.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“The steadfast of mind You will keep in perfect <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18134F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18134F\"></sup>peace,Because he trusts in You.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18135G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18135G\"></sup>Trust in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> forever,For in <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <i>we have</i> an everlasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18135H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18135H\"></sup>Rock.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“For He has brought low those who dwell on high, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18136I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18136I\"></sup>unassailable city;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18136J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18136J\"></sup>He lays it low, He lays it low to the ground, He casts it to the dust.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18137K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18137K\"></sup>The foot will trample it,The feet of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18137L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18137L\"></sup>afflicted, the steps of the helpless.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18138M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18138M\"></sup>way of the righteous is smooth;O Upright One, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18138N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18138N\"></sup>make the path of the righteous level.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Indeed, <i>while following</i> the way of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18139O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18139O\"></sup>Your judgments, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,We have waited for You eagerly;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18139P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18139P\"></sup>Your name, even Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18139Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18139Q\"></sup>memory, is the desire of <i>our</i> souls.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18140R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18140R\"></sup>At night my soul longs for You,Indeed, my spirit within me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18140S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18140S\"></sup>seeks You diligently;For when the earth experiences Your judgmentsThe inhabitants of the world <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18140T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18140T\"></sup>learn righteousness.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><i>Though</i> the wicked is shown favor,He does not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18141U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18141U\"></sup>learn righteousness;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18141V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18141V\"></sup>deals unjustly in the land of uprightness,And does not perceive the majesty of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, Your hand is lifted up <i>yet</i> they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18142W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18142W\"></sup>do not see it.They see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18142X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18142X\"></sup><i>Your</i> zeal for the people and are put to shame;Indeed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18142Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18142Y\"></sup>fire will devour Your enemies.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, You will establish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18143Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18143Z\"></sup>peace for us,Since You have also performed for us all our works.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18144AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18144AA\"></sup>other masters besides You have ruled us;<i>But</i> through You alone we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18144AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18144AB\"></sup>confess Your name.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18145AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18145AC\"></sup>The dead will not live, the departed spirits will not rise;Therefore You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18145AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18145AD\"></sup>punished and destroyed them,And You have wiped out all remembrance of them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18146AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18146AE\"></sup>You have increased the nation, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,You have increased the nation, You are glorified;You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18146AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18146AF\"></sup>extended all the borders of the land.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, they sought You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18147AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18147AG\"></sup>in distress;They could only whisper a prayer,Your chastening was upon them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18148AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18148AH\"></sup>As the pregnant woman approaches <i>the time</i> to give birth,She writhes <i>and</i> cries out in her labor pains,Thus were we before You, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>We were pregnant, we writhed <i>in labor</i>,We <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18149AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18149AI\"></sup>gave birth, as it seems, <i>only</i> to wind.We could not accomplish deliverance for the earth,Nor were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18149AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18149AJ\"></sup>inhabitants of the world born.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18150AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18150AK\"></sup>dead will live;Their corpses will rise.You who lie in the dust, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18150AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18150AL\"></sup>awake and shout for joy,For your dew <i>is as</i> the dew of the dawn,And the earth will give birth to the departed spirits.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Come, my people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18151AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18151AM\"></sup>enter into your roomsAnd close your doors behind you;Hide for a little <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18151AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18151AN\"></sup>whileUntil <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18151AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18151AO\"></sup>indignation runs <i>its</i> course.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For behold, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is about to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18152AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18152AP\"></sup>come out from His placeTo <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18152AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18152AQ\"></sup>punish the inhabitants of the earth for their iniquity;And the earth will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18152AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18152AR\"></sup>reveal her bloodshedAnd will no longer cover her slain."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span>In that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18153A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18153A\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will punish <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18153B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18153B\"></sup>Leviathan the fleeing serpent,With His fierce and great and mighty sword,Even Leviathan the twisted serpent;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18153C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18153C\"></sup>He will kill the dragon who <i>lives</i> in the sea.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>In that day,“A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18154D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18154D\"></sup>vineyard of wine, sing of it!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, am its keeper;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18155E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18155E\"></sup>I water it every moment.So that no one will damage it,I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18155F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18155F\"></sup>guard it night and day.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I have no wrath.Should someone give Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18156G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18156G\"></sup>briars <i>and</i> thorns in battle,<i>Then</i> I would step on them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18156H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18156H\"></sup>I would burn them completely.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Or let him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18157I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18157I\"></sup>rely on My protection,Let him make peace with Me,Let him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18157J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18157J\"></sup>make peace with Me.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>In the days to come Jacob <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18158K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18158K\"></sup>will take root,Israel will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18158L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18158L\"></sup>blossom and sprout,And they will fill the whole world with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18158M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18158M\"></sup>fruit.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Like the striking of Him who has struck them, has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18159N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18159N\"></sup>He struck them?Or like the slaughter of His slain, have they been slain?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>You contended with them by banishing them, by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18160O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18160O\"></sup>driving them away.With His fierce wind He has expelled <i>them</i> on the day of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18160P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18160P\"></sup>east wind.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Therefore through this Jacob’s iniquity will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18161Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18161Q\"></sup>forgiven;And this will be the full price of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18161R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18161R\"></sup>pardoning of his sin:When he makes all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18161S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18161S\"></sup>altar stones like pulverized chalk stones;<i>When</i> Asherim and incense altars will not stand.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For the fortified city is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18162T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18162T\"></sup>isolated,A homestead forlorn and forsaken like the desert;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18162U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18162U\"></sup>There the calf will graze,And there it will lie down and feed on its branches.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18163V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18163V\"></sup>limbs are dry, they are broken off;Women come <i>and</i> make a fire with them,For they are not a people of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18163W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18163W\"></sup>discernment,Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18163X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18163X\"></sup>their Maker <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18163Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18163Y\"></sup>will not have compassion on them.And their Creator will not be gracious to them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>In that day the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18164Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18164Z\"></sup>will start <i>His</i> threshing from the flowing stream of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18164AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18164AA\"></sup>Euphrates to the brook of Egypt, and you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18164AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18164AB\"></sup>gathered up one by one, O sons of Israel.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>It will come about also in that day that a great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18165AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18165AC\"></sup>trumpet will be blown, and those who were perishing in the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18165AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18165AD\"></sup>Assyria and who were scattered in the land of Egypt will come and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18165AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18165AE\"></sup>worship the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the holy mountain at Jerusalem."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span>Woe to the proud crown of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18166A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18166A\"></sup>drunkards of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18166B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18166B\"></sup>Ephraim,And to the fading flower of its glorious beauty,Which is at the head of the fertile valleyOf those who are overcome with wine!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Behold, the Lord has a strong and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18167C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18167C\"></sup>mighty <i>agent</i>;As a storm of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18167D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18167D\"></sup>hail, a tempest of destruction,Like a storm of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18167E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18167E\"></sup>mighty overflowing waters,He has cast <i>it</i> down to the earth with <i>His</i> hand.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The proud crown of the drunkards of Ephraim is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18168F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18168F\"></sup>trodden under foot.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And the fading flower of its glorious beauty,Which is at the head of the fertile valley,Will be like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18169G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18169G\"></sup>first-ripe fig prior to summer,Which one sees,<i>And</i> as soon as it is in his hand,He swallows it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>In that day the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18170H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18170H\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will become a beautiful <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18170I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18170I\"></sup>crownAnd a glorious diadem to the remnant of His people;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18171J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18171J\"></sup>spirit of justice for him who sits in judgment,A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18171K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18171K\"></sup>strength to those who repel the onslaught at the gate.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And these also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18172L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18172L\"></sup>reel with wine and stagger from strong drink:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18172M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18172M\"></sup>The priest and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18172N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18172N\"></sup>the prophet reel with strong drink,They are confused by wine, they stagger from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18172O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18172O\"></sup>strong drink;They reel while having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18172P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18172P\"></sup>visions,They totter <i>when rendering</i> judgment.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For all the tables are full of filthy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18173Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18173Q\"></sup>vomit, without a <i>single clean</i> place.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18174R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18174R\"></sup>whom would He teach knowledge,And to whom would He interpret the message?Those <i>just</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18174S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18174S\"></sup>weaned from milk?Those <i>just</i> taken from the breast?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“For <i>He says</i>,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18175T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18175T\"></sup>Order on order, order on order,Line on line, line on line,A little here, a little there.’”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Indeed, He will speak to this peopleThrough <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18176U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18176U\"></sup>stammering lips and a foreign tongue,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>He who said to them, “Here is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18177V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18177V\"></sup>rest, give rest to the weary,”And, “Here is repose,” but they would not listen.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>So the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to them will be,“Order on order, order on order,Line on line, line on line,A little here, a little there,”That they may go and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18178W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18178W\"></sup>stumble backward, be broken, snared and taken captive.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18179X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18179X\"></sup>hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18179Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18179Y\"></sup>scoffers,Who rule this people who are in Jerusalem,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Because you have said, “We have made a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18180Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18180Z\"></sup>covenant with death,And with Sheol we have made a pact.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18180AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18180AA\"></sup>The overwhelming scourge will not reach us when it passes by,For we have made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18180AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18180AB\"></sup>falsehood our refuge and we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18180AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18180AC\"></sup>concealed ourselves with deception.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18181AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18181AD\"></sup>Behold, I am laying in Zion a stone, a tested <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18181AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18181AE\"></sup>stone,A costly cornerstone <i>for</i> the foundation, firmly placed.He who believes <i>in it</i> will not be disturbed.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“I will make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18182AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18182AF\"></sup>justice the measuring lineAnd righteousness the level;Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18182AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18182AG\"></sup>hail will sweep away the refuge of liesAnd the waters will overflow the secret place.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18183AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18183AH\"></sup>covenant with death will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18183AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18183AI\"></sup>canceled,And your pact with Sheol will not stand;When the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18183AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18183AJ\"></sup>overwhelming scourge passes through,Then you become its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18183AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18183AK\"></sup>trampling <i>place</i>.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“As <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18184AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18184AL\"></sup>often as it passes through, it will seize you;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18184AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18184AM\"></sup>morning after morning it will pass through, <i>anytime</i> during the day or night,And it will be sheer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18184AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18184AN\"></sup>terror to understand what it means.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The bed is too short on which to stretch out,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18185AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18185AO\"></sup>blanket is too small to wrap oneself in.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will rise up as <i>at</i> Mount <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18186AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18186AP\"></sup>Perazim,He will be stirred up as in the valley of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18186AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18186AQ\"></sup>Gibeon,To do His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18186AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18186AR\"></sup>task, His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18186AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18186AS\"></sup>unusual task,And to work His work, His extraordinary work.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And now do not carry on as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18187AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18187AT\"></sup>scoffers,Or your fetters will be made stronger;For I have heard from the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> of hostsOf decisive <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18187AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18187AU\"></sup>destruction on all the earth.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Give ear and hear my voice,Listen and hear my words.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Does the farmer plow continually to plant seed?Does he <i>continually</i> turn and harrow the ground?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Does he not level its surfaceAnd sow dill and scatter <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18190AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18190AV\"></sup>cumminAnd plant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18190AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18190AW\"></sup>wheat in rows,Barley in its place and rye within its area?",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For his God instructs and teaches him properly.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For dill is not threshed with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18192AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18192AX\"></sup>threshing sledge,Nor is the cartwheel driven over cummin;But dill is beaten out with a rod, and cummin with a club.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><i>Grain for</i> bread is crushed,Indeed, he does not continue to thresh it forever.Because the wheel of <i>his</i> cart and his horses <i>eventually</i> damage <i>it</i>,He does not thresh it longer.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>This also comes from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,<i>Who</i> has made <i>His</i> counsel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18194AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18194AY\"></sup>wonderful and <i>His</i> wisdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18194AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18194AZ\"></sup>great."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">29 </span>Woe, O Ariel, Ariel the city <i>where</i> David <i>once</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18195A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18195A\"></sup>camped!Add year to year, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18195B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18195B\"></sup>observe <i>your</i> feasts on schedule.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>I will bring distress to Ariel,And she will be <i>a city of</i> lamenting and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18196C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18196C\"></sup>mourning;And she will be like an Ariel to me.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18197D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18197D\"></sup>camp against you encircling <i>you</i>,And I will set siegeworks against you,And I will raise up battle towers against you.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18198E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18198E\"></sup>be brought low;From the earth you will speak,And from the dust <i>where</i> you are prostrateYour words <i>will come</i>.Your voice will also be like that of a spirit from the ground,And your speech will whisper from the dust.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But the multitude of your enemies will become like fine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18199F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18199F\"></sup>dust,And the multitude of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18199G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18199G\"></sup>ruthless ones like the chaff which blows away;And it will happen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18199H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18199H\"></sup>instantly, suddenly.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>From the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18200I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18200I\"></sup>punished with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18200J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18200J\"></sup>thunder and earthquake and loud noise,<i>With</i> whirlwind and tempest and the flame of a consuming fire.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18201K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18201K\"></sup>multitude of all the nations who wage war against Ariel,Even all who wage war against her and her stronghold, and who distress her,Will be like a dream, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18201L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18201L\"></sup>vision of the night.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>It will be as when a hungry man dreams—And behold, he is eating;But when he awakens, his hunger is not satisfied,Or as when a thirsty man dreams—And behold, he is drinking,But when he awakens, behold, he is faintAnd his thirst is not quenched.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18202M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18202M\"></sup>Thus the multitude of all the nations will beWho wage war against Mount Zion.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18203N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18203N\"></sup>Be delayed and wait,Blind yourselves and be blind;They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18203O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18203O\"></sup>become drunk, but not with wine,They stagger, but not with strong drink.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has poured over you a spirit of deep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18204P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18204P\"></sup>sleep,He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18204Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18204Q\"></sup>shut your eyes, the prophets;And He has covered your heads, the seers.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The entire vision will be to you like the words of a sealed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18205R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18205R\"></sup>book, which when they give it to the one who is literate, saying, “Please read this,” he will say, “I cannot, for it is sealed.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the book will be given to the one who is illiterate, saying, “Please read this.” And he will say, “I cannot read.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then the Lord said,“Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18207S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18207S\"></sup>this people draw near with their wordsAnd honor Me with their lip service,But they remove their hearts far from Me,And their reverence for Me consists of tradition learned <i>by rote</i>,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Therefore behold, I will once again deal <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18208T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18208T\"></sup>marvelously with this people, wondrously marvelous;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18208U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18208U\"></sup>the wisdom of their wise men will perish,And the discernment of their discerning men will be concealed.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Woe to those who deeply <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18209V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18209V\"></sup>hide their plans from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18209W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18209W\"></sup>deeds are <i>done</i> in a dark place,And they say, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18209X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18209X\"></sup>Who sees us?” or “Who knows us?”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You turn <i>things</i> around!Shall the potter be considered as equal with the clay,That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18210Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18210Y\"></sup>what is made would say to its maker, “He did not make me”;Or what is formed say to him who formed it, “He has no understanding”?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Is it not yet just a little whileBefore Lebanon will be turned into a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18211Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18211Z\"></sup>fertile field,And the fertile field will be considered as a forest?",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>On that day the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18212AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18212AA\"></sup>deaf will hear <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18212AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18212AB\"></sup>words of a book,And out of <i>their</i> gloom and darkness the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18212AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18212AC\"></sup>eyes of the blind will see.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18213AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18213AD\"></sup>afflicted also will increase their gladness in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18213AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18213AE\"></sup>needy of mankind will rejoice in the Holy One of Israel.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18214AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18214AF\"></sup>ruthless will come to an end and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18214AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18214AG\"></sup>scorner will be finished,Indeed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18214AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18214AH\"></sup>all who are intent on doing evil will be cut off;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Who cause a person to be indicted by a word,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18215AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18215AI\"></sup>ensnare him who adjudicates at the gate,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18215AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18215AJ\"></sup>defraud the one in the right with meaningless arguments.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Therefore thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who redeemed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18216AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18216AK\"></sup>Abraham, concerning the house of Jacob:“Jacob <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18216AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18216AL\"></sup>shall not now be ashamed, nor shall his face now turn pale;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But when he sees his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18217AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18217AM\"></sup>children, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18217AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18217AN\"></sup>work of My hands, in his midst,They will sanctify My name;Indeed, they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18217AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18217AO\"></sup>sanctify the Holy One of JacobAnd will stand in awe of the God of Israel.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18218AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18218AP\"></sup>err in mind will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18218AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18218AQ\"></sup>know the truth,And those who criticize will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18218AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18218AR\"></sup>accept instruction."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">30 </span>“Woe to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18219A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18219A\"></sup>rebellious children,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18219B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18219B\"></sup>execute a plan, but not Mine,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18219C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18219C\"></sup>make an alliance, but not of My Spirit,In order to add sin to sin;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18220D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18220D\"></sup>proceed down to EgyptWithout <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18220E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18220E\"></sup>consulting Me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18220F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18220F\"></sup>To take refuge in the safety of PharaohAnd to seek shelter in the shadow of Egypt!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Therefore the safety of Pharaoh will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18221G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18221G\"></sup>your shameAnd the shelter in the shadow of Egypt, your humiliation.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18222H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18222H\"></sup>their princes are at ZoanAnd their ambassadors arrive at Hanes.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Everyone will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18223I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18223I\"></sup>ashamed because of a people who cannot profit them,<i>Who are</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18223J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18223J\"></sup>not for help or profit, but for shame and also for reproach.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The oracle concerning the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18224K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18224K\"></sup>beasts of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18224L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18224L\"></sup>Negev.Through a land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18224M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18224M\"></sup>distress and anguish,From where <i>come</i> lioness and lion, viper and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18224N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18224N\"></sup>flying serpent,They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18224O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18224O\"></sup>carry their riches on the backs of young donkeysAnd their treasures on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18224P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18224P\"></sup>camels’ humps,To a people who cannot profit <i>them</i>;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Even Egypt, whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18225Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18225Q\"></sup>help is vain and empty.Therefore, I have called her“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18225R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18225R\"></sup>Rahab who has been exterminated.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18226S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18226S\"></sup>write it on a tablet before themAnd inscribe it on a scroll,That it may serve in the time to comeAs a witness forever.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For this is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18227T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18227T\"></sup>rebellious people, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18227U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18227U\"></sup>false sons,Sons who refuse to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18227V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18227V\"></sup>listenTo the instruction of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Who say to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18228W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18228W\"></sup>seers, “You must not see <i>visions</i>”;And to the prophets, “You must not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18228X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18228X\"></sup>prophesy to us what is right,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18228Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18228Y\"></sup>Speak to us pleasant words,Prophesy illusions.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Get out of the way, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18229Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18229Z\"></sup>turn aside from the path,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18229AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18229AA\"></sup>Let us hear no more about the Holy One of Israel.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore thus says the Holy One of Israel,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18230AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18230AB\"></sup>Since you have rejected this wordAnd have put your trust in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18230AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18230AC\"></sup>oppression and guile, and have relied on them,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18231AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18231AD\"></sup>iniquity will be to youLike a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18231AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18231AE\"></sup>breach about to fall,A bulge in a high wall,Whose collapse comes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18231AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18231AF\"></sup>suddenly in an instant,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Whose collapse is like the smashing of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18232AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18232AG\"></sup>potter’s jar,So ruthlessly shatteredThat a sherd will not be found among its piecesTo take fire from a hearthOr to scoop water from a cistern.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For thus the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, the Holy One of Israel, has said,“In repentance and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18233AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18233AH\"></sup>rest you will be saved,In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18233AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18233AI\"></sup>quietness and trust is your strength.”But you were not willing,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And you said, “No, for we will flee on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18234AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18234AJ\"></sup>horses,”Therefore you shall flee!“And we will ride on swift <i>horses</i>,”Therefore those who pursue you shall be swift.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18235AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18235AK\"></sup>One thousand <i>will flee</i> at the threat of one <i>man</i>;You will flee at the threat of five,Until you are left as a flag on a mountain topAnd as a signal on a hill.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Therefore the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18236AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18236AL\"></sup>longs to be gracious to you,And therefore He waits on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18236AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18236AM\"></sup>high to have compassion on you.For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18236AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18236AN\"></sup>God of justice;How blessed are all those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18236AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18236AO\"></sup>long for Him.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>O people in Zion, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18237AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18237AP\"></sup>inhabitant in Jerusalem, you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18237AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18237AQ\"></sup>weep no longer. He will surely be gracious to you at the sound of your cry; when He hears it, He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18237AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18237AR\"></sup>answer you.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Although the Lord has given you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18238AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18238AS\"></sup>bread of privation and water of oppression, <i>He</i>, your Teacher will no longer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18238AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18238AT\"></sup>hide Himself, but your eyes will behold your Teacher.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Your ears will hear a word behind you, “This is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18239AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18239AU\"></sup>way, walk in it,” whenever you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18239AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18239AV\"></sup>turn to the right or to the left.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And you will defile your graven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18240AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18240AW\"></sup>images overlaid with silver, and your molten <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18240AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18240AX\"></sup>images plated with gold. You will scatter them as an impure thing, <i>and</i> say to them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18240AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18240AY\"></sup>Be gone!”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Then He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18241AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18241AZ\"></sup>give <i>you</i> rain for the seed which you will sow in the ground, and bread <i>from</i> the yield of the ground, and it will be rich and plenteous; on that day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18241BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18241BA\"></sup>your livestock will graze in a roomy pasture.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Also the oxen and the donkeys which work the ground will eat salted fodder, which has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18242BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18242BB\"></sup>winnowed with shovel and fork.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>On every lofty mountain and on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18243BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18243BC\"></sup>every high hill there will be streams running with water on the day of the great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18243BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18243BD\"></sup>slaughter, when the towers fall.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18244BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18244BE\"></sup>The light of the moon will be as the light of the sun, and the light of the sun will be seven times <i>brighter</i>, like the light of seven days, on the day <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18244BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18244BF\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> binds up the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18244BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18244BG\"></sup>fracture of His people and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18244BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18244BH\"></sup>heals the bruise He has inflicted.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18245BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18245BI\"></sup>the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> comes from a remote place;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18245BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18245BJ\"></sup>Burning is His anger and dense is <i>His</i> smoke;His lips are filled with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18245BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18245BK\"></sup>indignationAnd His tongue is like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18245BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18245BL\"></sup>consuming fire;",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18246BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18246BM\"></sup>breath is like an overflowing torrent,Which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18246BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18246BN\"></sup>reaches to the neck,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18246BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18246BO\"></sup>shake the nations back and forth in a sieve,And to <i>put</i> in the jaws of the peoples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18246BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18246BP\"></sup>the bridle which leads to ruin.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>You will have songs as in the night when you keep the festival,And gladness of heart as when one marches to <i>the sound of</i> the flute,To go to the mountain of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, to the Rock of Israel.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will cause His voice of authority to be heard,And the descending of His arm to be seen in fierce anger,And <i>in</i> the flame of a consuming fireIn cloudburst, downpour and hailstones.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18249BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18249BQ\"></sup>at the voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18249BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18249BR\"></sup>Assyria will be terrified,<i>When</i> He strikes with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18249BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18249BS\"></sup>rod.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And every blow of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18250BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18250BT\"></sup>rod of punishment,Which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will lay on him,Will be with <i>the music of</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18250BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18250BU\"></sup>tambourines and lyres;And in battles, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18250BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18250BV\"></sup>brandishing weapons, He will fight them.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18251BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18251BW\"></sup>Topheth has long been ready,Indeed, it has been prepared for the king.He has made it deep and large,A pyre of fire with plenty of wood;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18251BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18251BX\"></sup>breath of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, like a torrent of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18251BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18251BY\"></sup>brimstone, sets it afire."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">31 </span>Woe to those who go down to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18252A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18252A\"></sup>Egypt for help<i>And</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18252B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18252B\"></sup>rely on horses,And trust in chariots because they are manyAnd in horsemen because they are very strong,But they do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18252C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18252C\"></sup>look to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18252D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18252D\"></sup>Holy One of Israel, nor seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Yet He also is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18253E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18253E\"></sup>wise and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18253F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18253F\"></sup>bring disasterAnd does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18253G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18253G\"></sup>not retract His words,But will arise against the house of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18253H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18253H\"></sup>evildoersAnd against the help of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18253I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18253I\"></sup>workers of iniquity.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Now the Egyptians are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18254J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18254J\"></sup>men and not God,And their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18254K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18254K\"></sup>horses are flesh and not spirit;So the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18254L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18254L\"></sup>stretch out His hand,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18254M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18254M\"></sup>he who helps will stumbleAnd he who is helped will fall,And all of them will come to an end together.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to me,“As the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18255N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18255N\"></sup>lion or the young lion growls over his prey,Against which a band of shepherds is called out,<i>And</i> he will not be terrified at their voice nor disturbed at their noise,So will the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts come down to wage <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18255O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18255O\"></sup>war on Mount Zion and on its hill.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Like flying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18256P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18256P\"></sup>birds so the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will protect Jerusalem.He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18256Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18256Q\"></sup>protect and deliver <i>it</i>;He will pass over and rescue <i>it</i>.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18257R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18257R\"></sup>Return to Him from whom you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18257S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18257S\"></sup>deeply defected, O sons of Israel.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For in that day every man will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18258T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18258T\"></sup>cast away his silver idols and his gold idols, which your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18258U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18258U\"></sup>sinful hands have made for you as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18258V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18258V\"></sup>a sin.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18259W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18259W\"></sup>Assyrian will fall by a sword not of man,And a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18259X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18259X\"></sup>sword not of man will devour him.So he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18259Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18259Y\"></sup>not escape the sword,And his young men will become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18259Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18259Z\"></sup>forced laborers.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18260AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18260AA\"></sup>rock will pass away because of panic,And his princes will be terrified at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18260AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18260AB\"></sup>standard,”Declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18260AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18260AC\"></sup>fire is in Zion and whose furnace is in Jerusalem."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">32 </span>Behold, a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18261A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18261A\"></sup>king will reign righteouslyAnd princes will rule justly.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Each will be like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18262B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18262B\"></sup>refuge from the windAnd a shelter from the storm,Like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18262C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18262C\"></sup>streams of water in a dry country,Like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18262D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18262D\"></sup>shade of a huge rock in a parched land.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18263E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18263E\"></sup>the eyes of those who see will not be blinded,And the ears of those who hear will listen.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The mind of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18264F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18264F\"></sup>hasty will discern the truth,And the tongue of the stammerers will hasten to speak clearly.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>No longer will the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18265G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18265G\"></sup>fool be called noble,Or the rogue be spoken of <i>as</i> generous.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For a fool speaks nonsense,And his heart <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18266H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18266H\"></sup>inclines toward wickedness:To practice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18266I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18266I\"></sup>ungodliness and to speak error against the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18266J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18266J\"></sup>keep the hungry person unsatisfiedAnd to withhold drink from the thirsty.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>As for a rogue, his weapons are evil;He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18267K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18267K\"></sup>devises wicked schemesTo <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18267L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18267L\"></sup>destroy <i>the</i> afflicted with slander,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18267M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18267M\"></sup>Even though <i>the</i> needy one speaks what is right.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18268N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18268N\"></sup>the noble man devises noble plans;And by noble plans he stands.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Rise up, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18269O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18269O\"></sup>women who are at ease,<i>And</i> hear my voice;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18269P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18269P\"></sup>Give ear to my word,You complacent daughters.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Within a year and <i>a few</i> daysYou will be troubled, O complacent <i>daughters</i>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18270Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18270Q\"></sup>For the vintage is ended,<i>And</i> the <i>fruit</i> gathering will not come.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Tremble, you <i>women</i> who are at ease;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18271R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18271R\"></sup>Be troubled, you complacent <i>daughters</i>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18271S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18271S\"></sup>Strip, undress and put <i>sackcloth</i> on <i>your</i> waist,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18272T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18272T\"></sup>Beat your breasts for the pleasant fields, for the fruitful vine,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18273U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18273U\"></sup>For the land of my people <i>in which</i> thorns <i>and</i> briars shall come up;Yea, for all the joyful houses <i>and for</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18273V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18273V\"></sup>jubilant city.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18274W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18274W\"></sup>the palace has been abandoned, the populated <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18274X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18274X\"></sup>city forsaken.Hill and watch-tower have become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18274Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18274Y\"></sup>caves forever,A delight for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18274Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18274Z\"></sup>wild donkeys, a pasture for flocks;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Until the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18275AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18275AA\"></sup>Spirit is poured out upon us from on high,And the wilderness becomes a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18275AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18275AB\"></sup>fertile field,And the fertile field is considered as a forest.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18276AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18276AC\"></sup>justice will dwell in the wildernessAnd righteousness will abide in the fertile field.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18277AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18277AD\"></sup>work of righteousness will be peace,And the service of righteousness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18277AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18277AE\"></sup>quietness and confidence forever.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Then my people will live in a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18278AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18278AF\"></sup>peaceful habitation,And in secure dwellings and in undisturbed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18278AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18278AG\"></sup>resting places;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And it will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18279AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18279AH\"></sup>hail when the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18279AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18279AI\"></sup>forest comes down,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18279AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18279AJ\"></sup>the city will be utterly laid low.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>How <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18280AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18280AK\"></sup>blessed will you be, you who sow beside all waters,Who let out freely the ox and the donkey."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">33 </span>Woe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18281A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18281A\"></sup>to you, O destroyer,While you were not destroyed;And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18281B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18281B\"></sup>who is treacherous, while <i>others</i> did not deal treacherously with him.As soon as you finish destroying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18281C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18281C\"></sup>you will be destroyed;As soon as you cease to deal treacherously, <i>others</i> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18281D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18281D\"></sup>deal treacherously with you.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18282E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18282E\"></sup>be gracious to us; we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18282F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18282F\"></sup>waited for You.Be their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18282G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18282G\"></sup>strength every morning,Our salvation also in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18282H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18282H\"></sup>time of distress.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>At the sound of the tumult <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18283I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18283I\"></sup>peoples flee;At the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18283J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18283J\"></sup>lifting up of Yourself nations disperse.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Your spoil is gathered <i>as</i> the caterpillar gathers;As locusts rushing about men rush about on it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18285K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18285K\"></sup>exalted, for He dwells on high;He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18285L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18285L\"></sup>filled Zion with justice and righteousness.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And He will be the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18286M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18286M\"></sup>stability of your times,A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18286N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18286N\"></sup>wealth of salvation, wisdom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18286O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18286O\"></sup>knowledge;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18286P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18286P\"></sup>fear of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is his treasure.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Behold, their brave men cry in the streets,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18287Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18287Q\"></sup>ambassadors of peace weep bitterly.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The highways are desolate, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18288R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18288R\"></sup>traveler has ceased,He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18288S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18288S\"></sup>broken the covenant, he has despised the cities,He has no regard for man.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18289T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18289T\"></sup>The land mourns <i>and</i> pines away,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18289U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18289U\"></sup>Lebanon is shamed <i>and</i> withers;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18289V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18289V\"></sup>Sharon is like a desert plain,And Bashan and Carmel lose <i>their foliage</i>.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18290W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18290W\"></sup>I will arise,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Now I will be exalted, now I will be lifted up.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18291X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18291X\"></sup>conceived chaff, you will give birth to stubble;My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18291Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18291Y\"></sup>breath will consume you like a fire.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“The peoples will be burned to lime,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18292Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18292Z\"></sup>Like cut thorns which are burned in the fire.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“You who are far away, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18293AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18293AA\"></sup>hear what I have done;And you who are near, acknowledge My might.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18294AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18294AB\"></sup>Sinners in Zion are terrified;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18294AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18294AC\"></sup>Trembling has seized the godless.“Who among us can live with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18294AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18294AD\"></sup>the consuming fire?Who among us can live with continual <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18294AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18294AE\"></sup>burning?”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18295AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18295AF\"></sup>walks righteously and speaks with sincerity,He who rejects unjust gainAnd shakes his hands so that they hold no bribe;He who stops his ears from hearing about bloodshedAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18295AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18295AG\"></sup>shuts his eyes from looking upon evil;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>He will dwell on the heights,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18296AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18296AH\"></sup>His refuge will be the impregnable rock;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18296AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18296AI\"></sup>His bread will be given <i>him</i>,His water will be sure.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Your eyes will see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18297AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18297AJ\"></sup>the King in His beauty;They will behold <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18297AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18297AK\"></sup>a far-distant land.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Your heart will meditate on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18298AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18298AL\"></sup>terror:“Where is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18298AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18298AM\"></sup>he who counts?Where is he who weighs?Where is he who counts the towers?”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You will no longer see a fierce people,A people of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18299AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18299AN\"></sup>unintelligible speech which no one comprehends,Of a stammering tongue which no one understands.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18300AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18300AO\"></sup>Look upon Zion, the city of our appointed feasts;Your eyes will see Jerusalem, an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18300AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18300AP\"></sup>undisturbed habitation,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18300AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18300AQ\"></sup>A tent which will not be folded;Its stakes will never be pulled up,Nor any of its cords be torn apart.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But there the majestic <i>One</i>, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, will be for usA place of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18301AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18301AR\"></sup>rivers <i>and</i> wide canalsOn which no boat with oars will go,And on which no mighty ship will pass—",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18302AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18302AS\"></sup>judge,The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18302AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18302AT\"></sup>our lawgiver,The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18302AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18302AU\"></sup>our king;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18302AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18302AV\"></sup>He will save us—",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Your tackle hangs slack;It cannot hold the base of its mast firmly,Nor spread out the sail.Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18303AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18303AW\"></sup>prey of an abundant spoil will be divided;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18303AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18303AX\"></sup>The lame will take the plunder.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And no resident will say, “I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18304AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18304AY\"></sup>sick”;The people who dwell there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18304AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18304AZ\"></sup>forgiven <i>their</i> iniquity."
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">34 </span>Draw near, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18305A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18305A\"></sup>O nations, to hear; and listen, O peoples!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18305B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18305B\"></sup>Let the earth and all it contains hear, and the world and all that springs from it.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18306C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18306C\"></sup>indignation is against all the nations,And <i>His</i> wrath against all their armies;He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18306D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18306D\"></sup>utterly destroyed them,He has given them over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18306E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18306E\"></sup>slaughter.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So their slain will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18307F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18307F\"></sup>thrown out,And their corpses will give off their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18307G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18307G\"></sup>stench,And the mountains will be drenched with their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18307H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18307H\"></sup>blood.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18308I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18308I\"></sup>all the host of heaven will wear away,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18308J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18308J\"></sup>sky will be rolled up like a scroll;All their hosts will also wither awayAs a leaf withers from the vine,Or as <i>one</i> withers from the fig tree.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18309K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18309K\"></sup>My sword is satiated in heaven,Behold it shall descend for judgment upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18309L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18309L\"></sup>EdomAnd upon the people whom I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18309M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18309M\"></sup>devoted to destruction.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The sword of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is filled with blood,It is sated with fat, with the blood of lambs and goats,With the fat of the kidneys of rams.For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a sacrifice in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18310N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18310N\"></sup>BozrahAnd a great slaughter in the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18310O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18310O\"></sup>Edom.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18311P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18311P\"></sup>Wild oxen will also fall with themAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18311Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18311Q\"></sup>young bulls with strong ones;Thus their land will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18311R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18311R\"></sup>soaked with blood,And their dust become greasy with fat.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a day of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18312S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18312S\"></sup>vengeance,A year of recompense for the cause of Zion.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Its streams will be turned into pitch,And its loose earth into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18313T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18313T\"></sup>brimstone,And its land will become burning pitch.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>It will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18314U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18314U\"></sup>not be quenched night or day;Its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18314V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18314V\"></sup>smoke will go up forever.From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18314W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18314W\"></sup>generation to generation it will be desolate;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18314X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18314X\"></sup>None will pass through it forever and ever.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18315Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18315Y\"></sup>pelican and hedgehog will possess it,And owl and raven will dwell in it;And He will stretch over it the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18315Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18315Z\"></sup>line of desolationAnd the plumb line of emptiness.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Its nobles—there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18316AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18316AA\"></sup>no one there<i>Whom</i> they may proclaim king—And all its princes will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18316AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18316AB\"></sup>nothing.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Thorns will come up in its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18317AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18317AC\"></sup>fortified towers,Nettles and thistles in its fortified cities;It will also be a haunt of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18317AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18317AD\"></sup>jackals<i>And</i> an abode of ostriches.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The desert <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18318AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18318AE\"></sup>creatures will meet with the wolves,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18318AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18318AF\"></sup>hairy goat also will cry to its kind;Yes, the night monster will settle thereAnd will find herself a resting place.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The tree snake will make its nest and lay <i>eggs</i> there,And it will hatch and gather <i>them</i> under its protection.Yes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18319AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18319AG\"></sup>the hawks will be gathered there,Every one with its kind.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Seek from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18320AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18320AH\"></sup>book of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and read:Not one of these will be missing;None will lack its mate.For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18320AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18320AI\"></sup>His mouth has commanded,And His Spirit has gathered them.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He has cast the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18321AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18321AJ\"></sup>lot for them,And His hand has divided it to them by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18321AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18321AK\"></sup>line.They shall possess it forever;From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18321AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18321AL\"></sup>generation to generation they will dwell in it."
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">35 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18322A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18322A\"></sup>wilderness and the desert will be glad,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18322B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18322B\"></sup>Arabah will rejoice and blossom;Like the crocus",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>It will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18323C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18323C\"></sup>blossom profuselyAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18323D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18323D\"></sup>rejoice with rejoicing and shout of joy.The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18323E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18323E\"></sup>glory of Lebanon will be given to it,The majesty of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18323F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18323F\"></sup>Carmel and Sharon.They will see the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18323G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18323G\"></sup>glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,The majesty of our God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18324H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18324H\"></sup>Encourage the exhausted, and strengthen the feeble.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Say to those with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18325I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18325I\"></sup>anxious heart,“Take courage, fear not.Behold, your God will come <i>with</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18325J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18325J\"></sup>vengeance;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18325K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18325K\"></sup>recompense of God will come,But He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18325L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18325L\"></sup>save you.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18326M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18326M\"></sup>eyes of the blind will be openedAnd the ears of the deaf will be unstopped.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18327N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18327N\"></sup>lame will leap like a deer,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18327O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18327O\"></sup>tongue of the mute will shout for joy.For waters will break forth in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18327P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18327P\"></sup>wildernessAnd streams in the Arabah.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The scorched land will become a poolAnd the thirsty ground <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18328Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18328Q\"></sup>springs of water;In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18328R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18328R\"></sup>haunt of jackals, its resting place,Grass <i>becomes</i> reeds and rushes.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18329S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18329S\"></sup>A highway will be there, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18329T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18329T\"></sup>a roadway,And it will be called the Highway of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18329U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18329U\"></sup>Holiness.The unclean will not travel on it,But it <i>will</i> be for him who walks <i>that</i> way,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18329V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18329V\"></sup>fools will not wander <i>on it</i>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>No <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18330W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18330W\"></sup>lion will be there,Nor will any vicious beast go up on it;These will not be found there.But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18330X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18330X\"></sup>the redeemed will walk <i>there</i>,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18331Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18331Y\"></sup>the ransomed of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will returnAnd come with joyful shouting to Zion,With everlasting joy upon their heads.They will find gladness and joy,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18331Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18331Z\"></sup>sorrow and sighing will flee away."
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">36 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18332A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18332A\"></sup>Now in the fourteenth year of King Hezekiah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18332B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18332B\"></sup>Sennacherib king of Assyria came up against all the fortified cities of Judah and seized them.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18333C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18333C\"></sup>king of Assyria sent Rabshakeh from Lachish to Jerusalem to King Hezekiah with a large army. And he stood by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18333D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18333D\"></sup>conduit of the upper pool on the highway of the fuller’s field.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18334E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18334E\"></sup>Eliakim the son of Hilkiah, who was over the household, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18334F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18334F\"></sup>Shebna the scribe, and Joah the son of Asaph, the recorder, came out to him.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18335G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18335G\"></sup>Rabshakeh said to them, “Say now to Hezekiah, ‘Thus says the great king, the king of Assyria, “What is this confidence that you have?",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I say, ‘Your counsel and strength for the war are only empty words.’ Now on whom do you rely, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18336H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18336H\"></sup>you have rebelled against me?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Behold, you rely on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18337I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18337I\"></sup>staff of this crushed reed, <i>even</i> on Egypt, on which if a man leans, it will go into his hand and pierce it. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18337J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18337J\"></sup>So is Pharaoh king of Egypt to all who rely on him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But if you say to me, ‘We trust in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God,’ is it not He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18338K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18338K\"></sup>whose high places and whose altars Hezekiah has taken away and has said to Judah and to Jerusalem, ‘You shall worship before this altar’?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Now therefore, come make a bargain with my master the king of Assyria, and I will give you two thousand horses, if you are able on your part to set riders on them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>How then can you repulse one official of the least of my master’s servants and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18340L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18340L\"></sup>rely on Egypt for chariots and for horsemen?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Have I now come up without the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> approval against this land to destroy it? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18341M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18341M\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, ‘Go up against this land and destroy it.’”’”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then Eliakim and Shebna and Joah said to Rabshakeh, “Speak now to your servants in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18342N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18342N\"></sup>Aramaic, for we understand <i>it</i>; and do not speak with us in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18342O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18342O\"></sup>Judean in the hearing of the people who are on the wall.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But Rabshakeh said, “Has my master sent me only to your master and to you to speak these words, <i>and</i> not to the men who sit on the wall, <i>doomed</i> to eat their own dung and drink their own urine with you?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then Rabshakeh stood and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18344P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18344P\"></sup>cried with a loud voice in Judean and said, “Hear the words of the great king, the king of Assyria.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Thus says the king, ‘Do not let Hezekiah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18345Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18345Q\"></sup>deceive you, for he will not be able to deliver you;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>nor let Hezekiah make you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18346R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18346R\"></sup>trust in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, saying, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will surely deliver us, this city will not be given into the hand of the king of Assyria.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Do not listen to Hezekiah,’ for thus says the king of Assyria, ‘Make your peace with me and come out to me, and eat each of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18347S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18347S\"></sup>vine and each of his fig tree and drink each of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18347T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18347T\"></sup>waters of his own cistern,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>until I come and take you away to a land like your own land, a land of grain and new wine, a land of bread and vineyards.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><i>Beware</i> that Hezekiah does not mislead you, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18349U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18349U\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will deliver us.” Has any one of the gods of the nations delivered his land from the hand of the king of Assyria?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Where are the gods of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18350V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18350V\"></sup>Hamath and Arpad? Where are the gods of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18350W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18350W\"></sup>Sepharvaim? And when have they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18350X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18350X\"></sup>delivered Samaria from my hand?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Who among all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18351Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18351Y\"></sup>gods of these lands have delivered their land from my hand, that the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18351Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18351Z\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> would deliver Jerusalem from my hand?’”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But they were silent and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18352AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18352AA\"></sup>answered him not a word; for the king’s commandment was, “Do not answer him.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18353AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18353AB\"></sup>Eliakim the son of Hilkiah, who was over the household, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18353AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18353AC\"></sup>Shebna the scribe and Joah the son of Asaph, the recorder, came to Hezekiah with their clothes torn and told him the words of Rabshakeh."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">37 </span>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18354A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18354A\"></sup>when King Hezekiah heard <i>it</i>, he tore his clothes, covered himself with sackcloth and entered the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then he sent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18355B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18355B\"></sup>Eliakim who was over the household with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18355C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18355C\"></sup>Shebna the scribe and the elders of the priests, covered with sackcloth, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18355D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18355D\"></sup>Isaiah the prophet, the son of Amoz.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They said to him, “Thus says Hezekiah, ‘This day is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18356E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18356E\"></sup>day of distress, rebuke and rejection; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18356F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18356F\"></sup>children have come to birth, and there is no strength to deliver.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Perhaps the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God will hear the words of Rabshakeh, whom his master the king of Assyria has sent to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18357G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18357G\"></sup>reproach the living God, and will rebuke the words which the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God has heard. Therefore, offer a prayer for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18357H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18357H\"></sup>the remnant that is left.’”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>So the servants of King Hezekiah came to Isaiah.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Isaiah said to them, “Thus you shall say to your master, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18359I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18359I\"></sup>Do not be afraid because of the words that you have heard, with which the servants of the king of Assyria have blasphemed Me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Behold, I will put a spirit in him so that he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18360J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18360J\"></sup>hear a rumor and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18360K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18360K\"></sup>return to his own land. And I will make him fall by the sword in his own land.”’”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then Rabshakeh returned and found the king of Assyria fighting against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18361L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18361L\"></sup>Libnah, for he had heard that the king had left <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18361M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18361M\"></sup>Lachish.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18362N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18362N\"></sup>heard <i>them</i> say concerning Tirhakah king of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18362O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18362O\"></sup>Cush, “He has come out to fight against you,” and when he heard <i>it</i> he sent messengers to Hezekiah, saying,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Thus you shall say to Hezekiah king of Judah, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18363P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18363P\"></sup>Do not let your God in whom you trust deceive you, saying, “Jerusalem will not be given into the hand of the king of Assyria.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18364Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18364Q\"></sup>Behold, you have heard what the kings of Assyria have done to all the lands, destroying them completely. So will you be spared?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Did the gods of those nations which my fathers have destroyed deliver them, <i>even</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18365R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18365R\"></sup>Gozan and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18365S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18365S\"></sup>Haran and Rezeph and the sons of Eden who <i>were</i> in Telassar?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Where is the king of Hamath, the king of Arpad, the king of the city of Sepharvaim, <i>and of</i> Hena and Ivvah?’”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then Hezekiah took the letter from the hand of the messengers and read it, and he went up to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and spread it out before the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Hezekiah prayed to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> saying,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts, the God of Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18369T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18369T\"></sup>who is enthroned <i>above</i> the cherubim, You are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18369U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18369U\"></sup>God, You alone, of all the kingdoms of the earth. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18369V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18369V\"></sup>You have made heaven and earth.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18370W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18370W\"></sup>Incline Your ear, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and hear; open Your eyes, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and see; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18370X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18370X\"></sup>listen to all the words of Sennacherib, who sent <i>them</i> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18370Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18370Y\"></sup>reproach the living God.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Truly, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18371Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18371Z\"></sup>kings of Assyria have devastated all the countries and their lands,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and have cast their gods into the fire, for they were not gods but the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18372AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18372AA\"></sup>work of men’s hands, wood and stone. So they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18372AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18372AB\"></sup>destroyed them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Now, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> our God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18373AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18373AC\"></sup>deliver us from his hand that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18373AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18373AD\"></sup>all the kingdoms of the earth may know that You alone, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, are God.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18374AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18374AE\"></sup>Isaiah the son of Amoz sent <i>word</i> to Hezekiah, saying, “Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, ‘Because you have prayed to Me about Sennacherib king of Assyria,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>this is the word that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken against him:“She has despised you and mocked you,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18375AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18375AF\"></sup>virgin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18375AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18375AG\"></sup>daughter of Zion;She has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18375AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18375AH\"></sup>shaken <i>her</i> head behind you,The daughter of Jerusalem!",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“Whom have you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18376AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18376AI\"></sup>reproached and blasphemed?And against whom have you raised <i>your</i> voiceAnd haughtily <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18376AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18376AJ\"></sup>lifted up your eyes?Against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18376AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18376AK\"></sup>Holy One of Israel!",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Through your servants you have reproached the Lord,And you have said, ‘With my many chariots I came up to the heights of the mountains,To the remotest parts of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18377AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18377AL\"></sup>Lebanon;And I cut down its tall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18377AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18377AM\"></sup>cedars <i>and</i> its choice cypresses.And I will go to its highest peak, its thickest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18377AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18377AN\"></sup>forest.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>‘I dug <i>wells</i> and drank waters,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18378AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18378AO\"></sup>with the sole of my feet I dried upAll the rivers of Egypt.’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18379AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18379AP\"></sup>Have you not heard?Long ago I did it,From ancient times I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18379AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18379AQ\"></sup>planned it.Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18379AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18379AR\"></sup>I have brought it to pass,That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18379AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18379AS\"></sup>you should turn fortified cities into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18379AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18379AT\"></sup>ruinous heaps.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Therefore their inhabitants were short of strength,They were dismayed and put to shame;They were <i>as</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18380AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18380AU\"></sup>vegetation of the field and <i>as</i> the green herb,<i>As</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18380AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18380AV\"></sup>grass on the housetops is scorched before it is grown up.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“But I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18381AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18381AW\"></sup>know your sitting downAnd your going out and your coming inAnd your raging against Me.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Because of your raging against MeAnd because your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18382AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18382AX\"></sup>arrogance has come up to My ears,Therefore I will put My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18382AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18382AY\"></sup>hook in your noseAnd My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18382AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18382AZ\"></sup>bridle in your lips,And I will turn you back <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18382BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18382BA\"></sup>by the way which you came.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>“Then this shall be the sign for you: you will eat this year what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18383BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18383BB\"></sup>grows of itself, in the second year what springs from the same, and in the third year sow, reap, plant vineyards and eat their fruit.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18384BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18384BC\"></sup>surviving <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18384BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18384BD\"></sup>remnant of the house of Judah will again <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18384BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18384BE\"></sup>take root downward and bear fruit upward.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For out of Jerusalem will go forth a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18385BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18385BF\"></sup>remnant and out of Mount Zion survivors. The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18385BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18385BG\"></sup>zeal of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts will perform this.”’",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Therefore, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> concerning the king of Assyria, ‘He will not come to this city or shoot an arrow there; and he will not come before it with a shield, or throw up a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18386BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18386BH\"></sup>siege ramp against it.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18387BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18387BI\"></sup>By the way that he came, by the same he will return, and he will not come to this city,’ declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>‘For I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18388BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18388BJ\"></sup>defend this city to save it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18388BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18388BK\"></sup>for My own sake and for My servant David’s sake.’”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18389BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18389BL\"></sup>angel of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> went out and struck 185,000 in the camp of the Assyrians; and when men arose early in the morning, behold, all of these were dead.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>So Sennacherib king of Assyria departed and returned <i>home</i> and lived at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18390BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18390BM\"></sup>Nineveh.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>It came about as he was worshiping in the house of Nisroch his god, that Adrammelech and Sharezer his sons killed him with the sword; and they escaped into the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18391BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18391BN\"></sup>Ararat. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18391BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18391BO\"></sup>Esarhaddon his son became king in his place."
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">38 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18392A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18392A\"></sup>In those days Hezekiah became mortally ill. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18392B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18392B\"></sup>Isaiah the prophet the son of Amoz came to him and said to him, “Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18392C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18392C\"></sup>Set your house in order, for you shall die and not live.’”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then Hezekiah turned his face to the wall and prayed to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18394D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18394D\"></sup>Remember now, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I beseech You, how I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18394E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18394E\"></sup>walked before You in truth and with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18394F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18394F\"></sup>whole heart, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18394G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18394G\"></sup>have done what is good in Your sight.” And Hezekiah <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18394H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18394H\"></sup>wept bitterly.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> came to Isaiah, saying,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Go and say to Hezekiah, ‘Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of your father David, “I have heard your prayer, I have seen your tears; behold, I will add <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18396I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18396I\"></sup>fifteen years to your life.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18397J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18397J\"></sup>deliver you and this city from the hand of the king of Assyria; and I will defend this city.”’",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“This shall be the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18398K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18398K\"></sup>sign to you from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will do this thing that He has spoken:",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Behold, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18399L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18399L\"></sup>cause the shadow on the stairway, which has gone down with the sun on the stairway of Ahaz, to go back ten steps.” So the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18399M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18399M\"></sup>sun’s <i>shadow</i> went back ten steps on the stairway on which it had gone down.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>A writing of Hezekiah king of Judah after his illness and recovery:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18401N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18401N\"></sup>In the middle of my lifeI am to enter the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18401O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18401O\"></sup>gates of Sheol;I am to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18401P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18401P\"></sup>deprived of the rest of my years.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I said, “I will not see the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18402Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18402Q\"></sup>in the land of the living;I will look on man no more among the inhabitants of the world.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Like a shepherd’s <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18403R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18403R\"></sup>tent my dwelling is pulled up and removed from me;As a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18403S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18403S\"></sup>weaver I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18403T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18403T\"></sup>rolled up my life.He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18403U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18403U\"></sup>cuts me off from the loom;From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18403V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18403V\"></sup>day until night You make an end of me.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“I composed <i>my soul</i> until morning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18404W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18404W\"></sup>Like a lion—so He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18404X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18404X\"></sup>breaks all my bones,From <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18404Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18404Y\"></sup>day until night You make an end of me.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18405Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18405Z\"></sup>Like a swallow, <i>like</i> a crane, so I twitter;I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18405AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18405AA\"></sup>moan like a dove;My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18405AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18405AB\"></sup>eyes look wistfully to the heights;O Lord, I am oppressed, be my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18405AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18405AC\"></sup>security.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18406AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18406AD\"></sup>What shall I say?For He has spoken to me, and He Himself has done it;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18406AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18406AE\"></sup>wander about all my years because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18406AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18406AF\"></sup>bitterness of my soul.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“O Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18407AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18407AG\"></sup>by <i>these</i> things <i>men</i> live,And in all these is the life of my spirit;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18407AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18407AH\"></sup>O restore me to health and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18407AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18407AI\"></sup>let me live!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Lo, for <i>my own</i> welfare I had great bitterness;It is You who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18408AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18408AJ\"></sup>kept my soul from the pit of nothingness,For You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18408AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18408AK\"></sup>cast all my sins behind Your back.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18409AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18409AL\"></sup>Sheol cannot thank You,Death cannot praise You;Those who go down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18409AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18409AM\"></sup>to the pit cannot hope for Your faithfulness.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“It is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18410AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18410AN\"></sup>living who give thanks to You, as I do today;A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18410AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18410AO\"></sup>father tells his sons about Your faithfulness.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will surely save me;So we will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18411AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18411AP\"></sup>play my songs on stringed instruments<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18411AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18411AQ\"></sup>All <i>the</i> days of our life <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18411AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18411AR\"></sup>at the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18412AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18412AS\"></sup>Isaiah had said, “Let them take a cake of figs and apply it to the boil, that he may recover.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Then Hezekiah had said, “What is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18413AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18413AT\"></sup>sign that I shall go up to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?”"
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">39 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18414A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18414A\"></sup>At that time Merodach-baladan son of Baladan, king of Babylon, sent letters and a present to Hezekiah, for he heard that he had been sick and had recovered.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Hezekiah was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18415B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18415B\"></sup>pleased, and showed them <i>all</i> his treasure house, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18415C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18415C\"></sup>silver and the gold and the spices and the precious oil and his whole armory and all that was found in his treasuries. There was nothing in his house nor in all his dominion that Hezekiah did not show them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then Isaiah the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18416D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18416D\"></sup>prophet came to King Hezekiah and said to him, “What did these men say, and from where have they come to you?” And Hezekiah said, “They have come to me from a far <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18416E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18416E\"></sup>country, from Babylon.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He said, “What have they seen in your house?” So Hezekiah answered, “They have seen all that is in my house; there is nothing among my treasuries that I have not shown them.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then Isaiah said to Hezekiah, “Hear the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18418F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18418F\"></sup>word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>‘Behold, the days are coming when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18419G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18419G\"></sup>all that is in your house and all that your fathers have laid up in store to this day will be carried to Babylon; nothing will be left,’ says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>‘And <i>some</i> of your sons who will issue from you, whom you will beget, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18420H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18420H\"></sup>will be taken away, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18420I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18420I\"></sup>they will become officials in the palace of the king of Babylon.’”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18421J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18421J\"></sup>Then Hezekiah said to Isaiah, “The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> which you have spoken is good.” For he thought, “For there will be peace and truth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18421K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18421K\"></sup>in my days.”"
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">40 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18422A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18422A\"></sup>Comfort, O comfort My people,” says your God.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18423B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18423B\"></sup>Speak kindly to Jerusalem;And call out to her, that her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18423C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18423C\"></sup>warfare has ended,That her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18423D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18423D\"></sup>iniquity has been removed,That she has received of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> hand<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18423E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18423E\"></sup>Double for all her sins.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18424F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18424F\"></sup>A voice is calling,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18424G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18424G\"></sup>Clear the way for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> in the wilderness;Make smooth in the desert a highway for our God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Let every valley be lifted up,And every mountain and hill be made low;And let the rough ground become a plain,And the rugged terrain a broad valley;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18426H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18426H\"></sup>glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be revealed,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18426I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18426I\"></sup>all flesh will see <i>it</i> together;For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18426J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18426J\"></sup>mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A voice says, “Call out.”Then he answered, “What shall I call out?”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18427K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18427K\"></sup>All flesh is grass, and all its loveliness is like the flower of the field.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18428L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18428L\"></sup>grass withers, the flower fades,When the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18428M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18428M\"></sup>breath of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> blows upon it;Surely the people are grass.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The grass withers, the flower fades,But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18429N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18429N\"></sup>the word of our God stands forever.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Get yourself up on a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18430O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18430O\"></sup>high mountain,O Zion, bearer of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18430P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18430P\"></sup>good news,Lift up your voice mightily,O Jerusalem, bearer of good news;Lift <i>it</i> up, do not fear.Say to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18430Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18430Q\"></sup>cities of Judah,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18430R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18430R\"></sup>Here is your God!”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Behold, the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> will come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18431S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18431S\"></sup>with might,With His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18431T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18431T\"></sup>arm ruling for Him.Behold, His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18431U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18431U\"></sup>reward is with HimAnd His recompense before Him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Like a shepherd He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18432V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18432V\"></sup>tend His flock,In His arm He will gather the lambsAnd carry <i>them</i> in His bosom;He will gently lead the nursing <i>ewes</i>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18433W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18433W\"></sup>measured the waters in the hollow of His hand,And marked off the heavens by the span,And calculated the dust of the earth by the measure,And weighed the mountains in a balanceAnd the hills in a pair of scales?",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18434X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18434X\"></sup>Who has directed the Spirit of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Or as His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18434Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18434Y\"></sup>counselor has informed Him?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18435Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18435Z\"></sup>With whom did He consult and <i>who</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18435AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18435AA\"></sup>gave Him understanding?And <i>who</i> taught Him in the path of justice and taught Him knowledgeAnd informed Him of the way of understanding?",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18436AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18436AB\"></sup>nations are like a drop from a bucket,And are regarded as a speck of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18436AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18436AC\"></sup>dust on the scales;Behold, He lifts up the islands like fine dust.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Even Lebanon is not enough to burn,Nor its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18437AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18437AD\"></sup>beasts enough for a burnt offering.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18438AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18438AE\"></sup>All the nations are as nothing before Him,They are regarded by Him as less than nothing and meaningless.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18439AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18439AF\"></sup>To whom then will you liken God?Or what likeness will you compare with Him?",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><i>As for</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18440AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18440AG\"></sup>idol, a craftsman casts it,A goldsmith <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18440AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18440AH\"></sup>plates it with gold,And a silversmith <i>fashions</i> chains of silver.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He who is too impoverished for <i>such</i> an offeringSelects a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18441AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18441AI\"></sup>tree that does not rot;He seeks out for himself a skillful craftsmanTo prepare an idol that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18441AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18441AJ\"></sup>will not totter.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18442AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18442AK\"></sup>Do you not know? Have you not heard?Has it not been declared to you from the beginning?Have you not understood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18442AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18442AL\"></sup>from the foundations of the earth?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>It is He who sits above the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18443AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18443AM\"></sup>circle of the earth,And its inhabitants are like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18443AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18443AN\"></sup>grasshoppers,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18443AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18443AO\"></sup>stretches out the heavens like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18443AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18443AP\"></sup>curtainAnd spreads them out like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18443AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18443AQ\"></sup>tent to dwell in.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He <i>it is</i> who reduces <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18444AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18444AR\"></sup>rulers to nothing,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18444AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18444AS\"></sup>makes the judges of the earth meaningless.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Scarcely have they been planted,Scarcely have they been sown,Scarcely has their stock taken root in the earth,But He merely blows on them, and they wither,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18445AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18445AT\"></sup>storm carries them away like stubble.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18446AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18446AU\"></sup>To whom then will you liken MeThat I would be <i>his</i> equal?” says the Holy One.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18447AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18447AV\"></sup>Lift up your eyes on highAnd see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18447AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18447AW\"></sup>who has created these <i>stars</i>,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18447AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18447AX\"></sup>One who leads forth their host by number,He calls them all by name;Because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18447AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18447AY\"></sup>greatness of His might and the strength of <i>His</i> power,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18447AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18447AZ\"></sup>Not one <i>of them</i> is missing.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18448BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18448BA\"></sup>Why do you say, O Jacob, and assert, O Israel,“My way is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18448BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18448BB\"></sup>hidden from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18448BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18448BC\"></sup>justice due me escapes the notice of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18448BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18448BD\"></sup>my God”?",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18449BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18449BE\"></sup>Do you not know? Have you not heard?The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18449BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18449BF\"></sup>Everlasting God, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the Creator of the ends of the earthDoes not become weary or tired.His understanding is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18449BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18449BG\"></sup>inscrutable.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>He gives strength to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18450BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18450BH\"></sup>weary,And to <i>him who</i> lacks might He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18450BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18450BI\"></sup>increases power.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18451BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18451BJ\"></sup>youths grow weary and tired,And vigorous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18451BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18451BK\"></sup>young men stumble badly,",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Yet those who wait for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>Will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18452BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18452BL\"></sup>gain new strength;They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18452BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18452BM\"></sup>mount up <i>with</i> wings like eagles,They will run and not get tired,They will walk and not become weary."
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">41 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18453A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18453A\"></sup>Coastlands, listen to Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18453B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18453B\"></sup>in silence,And let the peoples <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18453C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18453C\"></sup>gain new strength;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18453D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18453D\"></sup>Let them come forward, then let them speak;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18453E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18453E\"></sup>Let us come together for judgment.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18454F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18454F\"></sup>Who has aroused one from the eastWhom He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18454G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18454G\"></sup>calls in righteousness to His feet?He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18454H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18454H\"></sup>delivers up nations before himAnd subdues kings.He makes them like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18454I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18454I\"></sup>dust with his sword,As the wind-driven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18454J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18454J\"></sup>chaff with his bow.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“He pursues them, passing on in safety,By a way he had not been traversing with his feet.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18456K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18456K\"></sup>Who has performed and accomplished <i>it</i>,Calling forth the generations from the beginning?‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18456L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18456L\"></sup>I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, am the first, and with the last. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18456M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18456M\"></sup>I am He.’”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18457N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18457N\"></sup>coastlands have seen and are afraid;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18457O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18457O\"></sup>ends of the earth tremble;They have drawn near and have come.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Each one helps his neighborAnd says to his brother, “Be strong!”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18459P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18459P\"></sup>craftsman encourages the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18459Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18459Q\"></sup>smelter,<i>And</i> he who smooths <i>metal</i> with the hammer <i>encourages</i> him who beats the anvil,Saying of the soldering, “It is good”;And he fastens it with nails,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18459R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18459R\"></sup><i>So that</i> it will not totter.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“But you, Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18460S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18460S\"></sup>My servant,Jacob whom I have chosen,Descendant of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18460T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18460T\"></sup>Abraham My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18460U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18460U\"></sup>friend,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>You whom I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18461V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18461V\"></sup>taken from the ends of the earth,And called from its <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18461W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18461W\"></sup>remotest partsAnd said to you, ‘You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18461X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18461X\"></sup>My servant,I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18461Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18461Y\"></sup>chosen you and not rejected you.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘Do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18462Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18462Z\"></sup>fear, for I am with you;Do not anxiously look about you, for I am your God.I will strengthen you, surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18462AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18462AA\"></sup>I will help you,Surely I will uphold you with My righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18462AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18462AB\"></sup>right hand.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18463AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18463AC\"></sup>all those who are angered at you will be shamed and dishonored;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18463AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18463AD\"></sup>Those who contend with you will be as nothing and will perish.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18464AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18464AE\"></sup>You will seek those who quarrel with you, but will not find them,Those who war with you will be as nothing and non-existent.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“For I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18465AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18465AF\"></sup>who upholds your right hand,Who says to you, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18465AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18465AG\"></sup>Do not fear, I will help you.’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Do not fear, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18466AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18466AH\"></sup>worm Jacob, you men of Israel;I will help you,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18466AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18466AI\"></sup>your Redeemer is the Holy One of Israel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Behold, I have made you a new, sharp threshing sledge with double edges;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18467AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18467AJ\"></sup>You will thresh the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18467AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18467AK\"></sup>mountains and pulverize <i>them</i>,And will make the hills like chaff.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18468AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18468AL\"></sup>winnow them, and the wind will carry them away,And the storm will scatter them;But you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18468AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18468AM\"></sup>rejoice in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,You will glory in the Holy One of Israel.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“The afflicted and needy are seeking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18469AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18469AN\"></sup>water, but there is none,And their tongue is parched with thirst;I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18469AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18469AO\"></sup>will answer them Myself,<i>As</i> the God of Israel I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18469AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18469AP\"></sup>will not forsake them.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“I will open <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18470AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18470AQ\"></sup>rivers on the bare heightsAnd springs in the midst of the valleys;I will make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18470AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18470AR\"></sup>the wilderness a pool of waterAnd the dry land fountains of water.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“I will put the cedar in the wilderness,The acacia and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18471AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18471AS\"></sup>myrtle and the olive tree;I will place the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18471AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18471AT\"></sup>juniper in the desertTogether with the box tree and the cypress,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18472AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18472AU\"></sup>they may see and recognize,And consider and gain insight as well,That the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18472AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18472AV\"></sup>hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done this,And the Holy One of Israel has created it.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Present your case,” the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> says.“Bring forward your strong <i>arguments</i>,”The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18473AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18473AW\"></sup>King of Jacob says.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18474AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18474AX\"></sup>Let them bring forth and declare to us what is going to take place;As for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18474AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18474AY\"></sup>former <i>events</i>, declare what they <i>were</i>,That we may consider them and know their outcome.Or announce to us what is coming;",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18475AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18475AZ\"></sup>Declare the things that are going to come afterward,That we may know that you are gods;Indeed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18475BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18475BA\"></sup>do good or evil, that we may anxiously look about us and fear together.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18476BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18476BB\"></sup>you are of no account,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18476BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18476BC\"></sup>your work amounts to nothing;He who chooses you is an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18476BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18476BD\"></sup>abomination.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“I have aroused <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18477BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18477BE\"></sup>one from the north, and he has come;From the rising of the sun he will call on My name;And he will come upon rulers as <i>upon</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18477BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18477BF\"></sup>mortar,Even as the potter treads clay.”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18478BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18478BG\"></sup>declared <i>this</i> from the beginning, that we might know?Or from former times, that we may say, “<i>He is</i> right!”?Surely there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18478BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18478BH\"></sup>no one who declared,Surely there was no one who proclaimed,Surely there was no one who heard your words.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18479BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18479BI\"></sup>Formerly <i>I said</i> to Zion, ‘Behold, here they are.’And to Jerusalem, ‘I will give a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18479BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18479BJ\"></sup>messenger of good news.’",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18480BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18480BK\"></sup>when I look, there is no one,And there is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18480BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18480BL\"></sup>counselor among themWho, if I ask, can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18480BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18480BM\"></sup>give an answer.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“Behold, all of them are false;Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18481BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18481BN\"></sup>works are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18481BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18481BO\"></sup>worthless,Their molten images are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18481BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18481BP\"></sup>wind and emptiness."
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">42 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18482A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18482A\"></sup>Behold, My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18482B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18482B\"></sup>Servant, whom I uphold;My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18482C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18482C\"></sup>chosen one <i>in whom</i> My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18482D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18482D\"></sup>soul delights.I have put My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18482E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18482E\"></sup>Spirit upon Him;He will bring forth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18482F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18482F\"></sup>justice to the nations.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“He will not cry out or raise <i>His voice</i>,Nor make His voice heard in the street.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“A bruised reed He will not breakAnd a dimly burning wick He will not extinguish;He will faithfully bring forth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18484G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18484G\"></sup>justice.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“He will not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18485H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18485H\"></sup>disheartened or crushedUntil He has established justice in the earth;And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18485I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18485I\"></sup>coastlands will wait expectantly for His law.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Thus says God the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18486J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18486J\"></sup>created the heavens and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18486K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18486K\"></sup>stretched them out,Who spread out the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18486L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18486L\"></sup>earth and its offspring,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18486M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18486M\"></sup>gives breath to the people on itAnd spirit to those who walk in it,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18487N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18487N\"></sup>called You in righteousness,I will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18487O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18487O\"></sup>hold You by the hand and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18487P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18487P\"></sup>watch over You,And I will appoint You as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18487Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18487Q\"></sup>covenant to the people,As a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18487R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18487R\"></sup>light to the nations,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18488S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18488S\"></sup>open blind eyes,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18488T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18488T\"></sup>bring out prisoners from the dungeonAnd those who dwell in darkness from the prison.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18489U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18489U\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18489V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18489V\"></sup>My name;I will not give My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18489W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18489W\"></sup>glory to another,Nor My praise to graven images.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Behold, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18490X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18490X\"></sup>former things have come to pass,Now I declare <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18490Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18490Y\"></sup>new things;Before they spring forth I proclaim <i>them</i> to you.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Sing to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18491Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18491Z\"></sup>new song,<i>Sing</i> His praise from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18491AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18491AA\"></sup>end of the earth!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18491AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18491AB\"></sup>You who go down to the sea, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18491AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18491AC\"></sup>all that is in it.You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18491AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18491AD\"></sup>islands, and those who dwell on them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Let the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18492AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18492AE\"></sup>wilderness and its cities lift up <i>their voices</i>,The settlements where <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18492AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18492AF\"></sup>Kedar inhabits.Let the inhabitants of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18492AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18492AG\"></sup>Sela sing aloud,Let them shout for joy from the tops of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18492AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18492AH\"></sup>mountains.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Let them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18493AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18493AI\"></sup>give glory to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>And declare His praise in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18493AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18493AJ\"></sup>coastlands.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18494AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18494AK\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will go forth like a warrior,He will arouse <i>His</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18494AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18494AL\"></sup>zeal like a man of war.He will utter a shout, yes, He will raise a war cry.He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18494AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18494AM\"></sup>prevail against His enemies.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18495AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18495AN\"></sup>I have kept silent for a long time,I have kept still and restrained Myself.<i>Now</i> like a woman in labor I will groan,I will both gasp and pant.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18496AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18496AO\"></sup>lay waste the mountains and hillsAnd wither all their vegetation;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18496AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18496AP\"></sup>make the rivers into coastlandsAnd dry up the ponds.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18497AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18497AQ\"></sup>lead the blind by a way they do not know,In paths they do not know I will guide them.I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18497AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18497AR\"></sup>make darkness into light before themAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18497AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18497AS\"></sup>rugged places into plains.These are the things I will do,And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18497AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18497AT\"></sup>not leave them undone.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They will be turned back <i>and</i> be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18498AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18498AU\"></sup>utterly put to shame,Who trust in idols,Who say to molten images,“You are our gods.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18499AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18499AV\"></sup>Hear, you deaf!And look, you blind, that you may see.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Who is blind but My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18500AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18500AW\"></sup>servant,Or so deaf as My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18500AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18500AX\"></sup>messenger whom I send?Who is so blind as he that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18500AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18500AY\"></sup>at peace <i>with Me</i>,Or so blind as the servant of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18501AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18501AZ\"></sup>You have seen many things, but you do not observe <i>them</i>;<i>Your</i> ears are open, but none hears.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was pleased for His righteousness’ sakeTo make the law <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18502BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18502BA\"></sup>great and glorious.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But this is a people plundered and despoiled;All of them are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18503BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18503BB\"></sup>trapped in caves,Or are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18503BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18503BC\"></sup>hidden away in prisons;They have become a prey with none to deliver <i>them</i>,And a spoil, with none to say, “Give <i>them</i> back!”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Who among you will give ear to this?Who will give heed and listen hereafter?",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Who gave Jacob up for spoil, and Israel to plunderers?Was it not the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, against whom we have sinned,And in whose ways they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18505BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18505BD\"></sup>were not willing to walk,And whose law they did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18505BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18505BE\"></sup>obey?",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>So He poured out on him the heat of His angerAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18506BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18506BF\"></sup>fierceness of battle;And it set him aflame all around,Yet he did not recognize <i>it</i>;And it burned him, but he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18506BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18506BG\"></sup>paid no attention."
		},
		"43": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">43 </span>But now, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18507A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18507A\"></sup>Creator, O Jacob,And He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18507B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18507B\"></sup>formed you, O Israel,“Do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18507C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18507C\"></sup>fear, for I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18507D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18507D\"></sup>redeemed you;I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18507E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18507E\"></sup>called you by name; you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18507F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18507F\"></sup>Mine!",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“When you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18508G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18508G\"></sup>pass through the waters, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18508H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18508H\"></sup>I will be with you;And through the rivers, they will not overflow you.When you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18508I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18508I\"></sup>walk through the fire, you will not be scorched,Nor will the flame burn you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18509J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18509J\"></sup>I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,The Holy One of Israel, your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18509K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18509K\"></sup>Savior;I have given Egypt as your ransom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18509L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18509L\"></sup>Cush and Seba in your place.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Since you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18510M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18510M\"></sup>precious in My sight,<i>Since</i> you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18510N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18510N\"></sup>honored and I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18510O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18510O\"></sup>love you,I will give <i>other</i> men in your place and <i>other</i> peoples in exchange for your life.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Do not fear, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18511P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18511P\"></sup>I am with you;I will bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18511Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18511Q\"></sup>your offspring from the east,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18511R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18511R\"></sup>gather you from the west.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I will say to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18512S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18512S\"></sup>north, ‘Give <i>them</i> up!’And to the south, ‘Do not hold <i>them</i> back.’Bring My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18512T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18512T\"></sup>sons from afarAnd My daughters from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18512U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18512U\"></sup>ends of the earth,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Everyone who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18513V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18513V\"></sup>called by My name,And whom I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18513W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18513W\"></sup>created for My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18513X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18513X\"></sup>glory,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18513Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18513Y\"></sup>Whom I have formed, even whom I have made.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Bring out the people who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18514Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18514Z\"></sup>blind, even though they have eyes,And the deaf, even though they have ears.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>All the nations have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18515AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18515AA\"></sup>gathered togetherSo that the peoples may be assembled.Who among them can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18515AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18515AB\"></sup>declare thisAnd proclaim to us the former things?Let them present <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18515AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18515AC\"></sup>their witnesses <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18515AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18515AD\"></sup>that they may be justified,Or let them hear and say, “It is true.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18516AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18516AE\"></sup>My witnesses,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18516AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18516AF\"></sup>My servant whom I have chosen,So that you may know and believe MeAnd understand that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18516AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18516AG\"></sup>I am He.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18516AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18516AH\"></sup>Before Me there was no God formed,And there will be none after Me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I, even I, am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And there is no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18517AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18517AI\"></sup>savior <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18517AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18517AJ\"></sup>besides Me.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“It is I who have declared and saved and proclaimed,And there was no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18518AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18518AK\"></sup>strange <i>god</i> among you;So you are My witnesses,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“And I am God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18519AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18519AL\"></sup>from eternity <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18519AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18519AM\"></sup>I am He,And there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18519AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18519AN\"></sup>none who can deliver out of My hand;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18519AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18519AO\"></sup>I act and who can reverse it?”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18520AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18520AP\"></sup>Redeemer, the Holy One of Israel,“For your sake I have sent to Babylon,And will bring them all down as fugitives,Even the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18520AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18520AQ\"></sup>Chaldeans, into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18520AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18520AR\"></sup>ships in which they rejoice.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, your Holy One,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18521AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18521AS\"></sup>The Creator of Israel, your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18521AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18521AT\"></sup>King.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18522AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18522AU\"></sup>makes a way through the seaAnd a path through the mighty waters,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Who brings forth the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18523AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18523AV\"></sup>chariot and the horse,The army and the mighty man(They will lie down together <i>and</i> not rise again;They have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18523AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18523AW\"></sup>quenched <i>and</i> extinguished like a wick):",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18524AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18524AX\"></sup>Do not call to mind the former things,Or ponder things of the past.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Behold, I will do something <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18525AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18525AY\"></sup>new,Now it will spring forth;Will you not be aware of it?I will even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18525AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18525AZ\"></sup>make a roadway in the wilderness,Rivers in the desert.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“The beasts of the field will glorify Me,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18526BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18526BA\"></sup>jackals and the ostriches,Because I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18526BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18526BB\"></sup>given waters in the wildernessAnd rivers in the desert,To give drink to My chosen people.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“The people whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18527BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18527BC\"></sup>I formed for Myself<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18527BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18527BD\"></sup>Will declare My praise.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Yet you have not called on Me, O Jacob;But you have become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18528BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18528BE\"></sup>weary of Me, O Israel.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18529BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18529BF\"></sup>not brought to Me the sheep of your burnt offerings,Nor have you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18529BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18529BG\"></sup>honored Me with your sacrifices.I have not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18529BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18529BH\"></sup>burdened you with offerings,Nor wearied you with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18529BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18529BI\"></sup>incense.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“You have bought Me not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18530BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18530BJ\"></sup>sweet cane with money,Nor have you filled Me with the fat of your sacrifices;Rather you have burdened Me with your sins,You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18530BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18530BK\"></sup>wearied Me with your iniquities.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“I, even I, am the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18531BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18531BL\"></sup>wipes out your transgressions <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18531BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18531BM\"></sup>for My own sake,And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18531BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18531BN\"></sup>not remember your sins.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Put Me in remembrance, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18532BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18532BO\"></sup>let us argue our case together;State your <i>cause</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18532BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18532BP\"></sup>that you may be proved right.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18533BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18533BQ\"></sup>first forefather sinned,And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18533BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18533BR\"></sup>spokesmen have transgressed against Me.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“So I will pollute the princes of the sanctuary,And I will consign Jacob to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18534BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18534BS\"></sup>ban and Israel to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18534BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18534BT\"></sup>revilement."
		},
		"44": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">44 </span>“But now listen, O Jacob, My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18535A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18535A\"></sup>servant,And Israel, whom I have chosen:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who made youAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18536B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18536B\"></sup>formed you from the womb, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18536C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18536C\"></sup>will help you,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18536D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18536D\"></sup>Do not fear, O Jacob My servant;And you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18536E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18536E\"></sup>Jeshurun whom I have chosen.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>‘For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18537F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18537F\"></sup>I will pour out water on the thirsty <i>land</i>And streams on the dry ground;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18537G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18537G\"></sup>pour out My Spirit on your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18537H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18537H\"></sup>offspringAnd My blessing on your descendants;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And they will spring up among the grassLike <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18538I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18538I\"></sup>poplars by streams of water.’",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“This one will say, ‘I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span>’;And that one will call on the name of Jacob;And another will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18539J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18539J\"></sup>write <i>on</i> his hand, ‘Belonging to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,’And will name Israel’s name with honor.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18540K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18540K\"></sup>King of Israel and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18540L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18540L\"></sup>Redeemer, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts:‘I am the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18540M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18540M\"></sup>first and I am the last,And there is no God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18540N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18540N\"></sup>besides Me.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>‘Who is like Me? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18541O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18541O\"></sup>Let him proclaim and declare it;Yes, let him recount it to Me in order,From the time that I established the ancient nation.And let them declare to them the things that are comingAnd the events that are going to take place.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>‘Do not tremble and do not be afraid;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18542P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18542P\"></sup>Have I not long since announced <i>it</i> to you and declared <i>it</i>?And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18542Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18542Q\"></sup>you are My witnesses.Is there any God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18542R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18542R\"></sup>besides Me,Or is there any <i>other</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18542S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18542S\"></sup>Rock?I know of none.’”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Those who fashion a graven image are all of them futile, and their precious things are of no profit; even their own witnesses fail to see or know, so that they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18543T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18543T\"></sup>put to shame.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Who has fashioned a god or cast an idol to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18544U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18544U\"></sup>no profit?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Behold, all his companions will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18545V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18545V\"></sup>put to shame, for the craftsmen themselves are mere men. Let them all assemble themselves, let them stand up, let them tremble, let them together be put to shame.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18546W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18546W\"></sup>man shapes iron into a cutting tool and does his work over the coals, fashioning it with hammers and working it with his strong arm. He also gets hungry and his strength fails; he drinks no water and becomes weary.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18547X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18547X\"></sup><i>Another</i> shapes wood, he extends a measuring line; he outlines it with red chalk. He works it with planes and outlines it with a compass, and makes it like the form of a man, like the beauty of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18547Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18547Y\"></sup>man, so that it may sit in a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18547Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18547Z\"></sup>house.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Surely he cuts cedars for himself, and takes a cypress or an oak and raises <i>it</i> for himself among the trees of the forest. He plants a fir, and the rain makes it grow.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then it becomes <i>something</i> for a man to burn, so he takes one of them and warms himself; he also makes a fire to bake bread. He also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18549AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18549AA\"></sup>makes a god and worships it; he makes it a graven image and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18549AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18549AB\"></sup>falls down before it.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Half of it he burns in the fire; over <i>this</i> half he eats meat as he roasts a roast and is satisfied. He also warms himself and says, “Aha! I am warm, I have seen the fire.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But the rest of it he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18551AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18551AC\"></sup>makes into a god, his graven image. He falls down before it and worships; he also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18551AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18551AD\"></sup>prays to it and says, “Deliver me, for you are my god.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>They do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18552AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18552AE\"></sup>know, nor do they understand, for He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18552AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18552AF\"></sup>smeared over their eyes so that they cannot see and their hearts so that they cannot comprehend.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>No one recalls, nor is there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18553AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18553AG\"></sup>knowledge or understanding to say, “I have burned half of it in the fire and also have baked bread over its coals. I roast meat and eat <i>it</i>. Then I make the rest of it into an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18553AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18553AH\"></sup>abomination, I fall down before a block of wood!”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18554AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18554AI\"></sup>feeds on ashes; a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18554AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18554AJ\"></sup>deceived heart has turned him aside. And he cannot deliver himself, nor say, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18554AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18554AK\"></sup>Is there not a lie in my right hand?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18555AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18555AL\"></sup>Remember these things, O Jacob,And Israel, for you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18555AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18555AM\"></sup>My servant;I have formed you, you are My servant,O Israel, you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18555AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18555AN\"></sup>not be forgotten by Me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18556AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18556AO\"></sup>wiped out your transgressions like a thick cloudAnd your sins like a heavy mist.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18556AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18556AP\"></sup>Return to Me, for I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18556AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18556AQ\"></sup>redeemed you.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18557AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18557AR\"></sup>Shout for joy, O heavens, for the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has done <i>it</i>!Shout joyfully, you lower parts of the earth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18557AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18557AS\"></sup>Break forth into a shout of joy, you mountains,O forest, and every tree in it;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18557AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18557AT\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has redeemed JacobAnd in Israel He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18557AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18557AU\"></sup>shows forth His glory.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18558AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18558AV\"></sup>Redeemer, and the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18558AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18558AW\"></sup>formed you from the womb,“I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, am the maker of all things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18558AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18558AX\"></sup>Stretching out the heavens by MyselfAnd spreading out the earth all alone,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18559AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18559AY\"></sup>Causing the omens of boasters to fail,Making fools out of diviners,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18559AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18559AZ\"></sup>Causing wise men to draw backAnd turning their knowledge into foolishness,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18560BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18560BA\"></sup>Confirming the word of His servantAnd performing the purpose of His messengers.<i>It is I</i> who says of Jerusalem, ‘She shall be inhabited!’And of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18560BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18560BB\"></sup>cities of Judah, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18560BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18560BC\"></sup>They shall be built.’And I will raise up her ruins <i>again</i>.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“<i>It is I</i> who says to the depth of the sea, ‘Be dried up!’And I will make your rivers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18561BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18561BD\"></sup>dry.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“<i>It is I</i> who says of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18562BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18562BE\"></sup>Cyrus, ‘<i>He is</i> My shepherd!And he will perform all My desire.’And he declares of Jerusalem, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18562BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18562BF\"></sup>She will be built,’And of the temple, ‘Your foundation will be laid.’”"
		},
		"45": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">45 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18563A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18563A\"></sup>Cyrus His anointed,Whom I have taken by the right <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18563B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18563B\"></sup>hand,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18563C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18563C\"></sup>subdue nations before himAnd to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18563D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18563D\"></sup>loose the loins of kings;To open doors before him so that gates will not be shut:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“I will go before you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18564E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18564E\"></sup>make the rough places smooth;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18564F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18564F\"></sup>shatter the doors of bronze and cut through their iron <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18564G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18564G\"></sup>bars.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“I will give you the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18565H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18565H\"></sup>treasures of darknessAnd hidden wealth of secret places,So that you may know that it is I,The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the God of Israel, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18565I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18565I\"></sup>calls you by your name.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“For the sake of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18566J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18566J\"></sup>Jacob My servant,And Israel My chosen <i>one</i>,I have also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18566K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18566K\"></sup>called you by your name;I have given you a title of honorThough you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18566L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18566L\"></sup>not known Me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18567M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18567M\"></sup>there is no other;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18567N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18567N\"></sup>Besides Me there is no God.I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18567O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18567O\"></sup>gird you, though you have not known Me;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18568P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18568P\"></sup>men may know from the rising to the setting of the sunThat there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18568Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18568Q\"></sup>no one besides Me.I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and there is no other,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The One <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18569R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18569R\"></sup>forming light and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18569S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18569S\"></sup>creating darkness,Causing well-being and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18569T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18569T\"></sup>creating calamity;I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who does all these.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18570U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18570U\"></sup>Drip down, O heavens, from above,And let the clouds pour down righteousness;Let the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18570V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18570V\"></sup>earth open up and salvation bear fruit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18570W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18570W\"></sup>And righteousness spring up with it.I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, have created it.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Woe to <i>the one</i> who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18571X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18571X\"></sup>quarrels with his Maker—An earthenware vessel among the vessels of earth!Will the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18571Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18571Y\"></sup>clay say to the potter, ‘What are you doing?’Or the thing you are making <i>say</i>, ‘He has no hands’?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Woe to him who says to a father, ‘What are you begetting?’Or to a woman, ‘To what are you giving birth?’”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Thus says the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18573Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18573Z\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the Holy One of Israel, and his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18573AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18573AA\"></sup>Maker:“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18573AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18573AB\"></sup>Ask Me about the things to come concerning My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18573AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18573AC\"></sup>sons,And you shall commit to Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18573AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18573AD\"></sup>the work of My hands.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“It is I who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18574AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18574AE\"></sup>made the earth, and created man upon it.I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18574AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18574AF\"></sup>stretched out the heavens with My handsAnd I ordained <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18574AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18574AG\"></sup>all their host.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“I have aroused him in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18575AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18575AH\"></sup>righteousnessAnd I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18575AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18575AI\"></sup>make all his ways smooth;He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18575AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18575AJ\"></sup>build My city and will let My exiles go <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18575AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18575AK\"></sup>free,Without any payment or reward,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“The products of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18576AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18576AL\"></sup>Egypt and the merchandise of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18576AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18576AM\"></sup>CushAnd the Sabeans, men of stature,Will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18576AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18576AN\"></sup>come over to you and will be yours;They will walk behind you, they will come over in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18576AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18576AO\"></sup>chainsAnd will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18576AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18576AP\"></sup>bow down to you;They will make supplication to you:‘Surely, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18576AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18576AQ\"></sup>God is with you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18576AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18576AR\"></sup>there is none else,No other God.’”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Truly, You are a God who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18577AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18577AS\"></sup>hides Himself,O God of Israel, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18577AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18577AT\"></sup>Savior!",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>They will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18578AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18578AU\"></sup>put to shame and even humiliated, all of them;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18578AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18578AV\"></sup>manufacturers of idols will go away together in humiliation.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Israel has been saved by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>With an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18579AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18579AW\"></sup>everlasting salvation;You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18579AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18579AX\"></sup>will not be put to shame or humiliatedTo all eternity.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18580AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18580AY\"></sup>created the heavens (He is the God who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18580AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18580AZ\"></sup>formed the earth and made it, He established it <i>and</i> did not create it a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18580BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18580BA\"></sup>waste place, <i>but</i> formed it to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18580BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18580BB\"></sup>inhabited),“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18580BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18580BC\"></sup>there is none else.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18581BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18581BD\"></sup>I have not spoken in secret,In some dark land;I did not say to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18581BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18581BE\"></sup>offspring of Jacob,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18581BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18581BF\"></sup>Seek Me in a waste place’;I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18581BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18581BG\"></sup>speak righteousness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18581BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18581BH\"></sup>Declaring things that are upright.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18582BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18582BI\"></sup>Gather yourselves and come;Draw near together, you fugitives of the nations;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18582BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18582BJ\"></sup>They have no knowledge,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18582BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18582BK\"></sup>carry about their wooden idolAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18582BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18582BL\"></sup>pray to a god who cannot save.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18583BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18583BM\"></sup>Declare and set forth <i>your case</i>;Indeed, let them consult together.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18583BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18583BN\"></sup>Who has announced this from of old?Who has long since declared it?Is it not I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?And there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18583BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18583BO\"></sup>no other God besides Me,A righteous God and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18583BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18583BP\"></sup>Savior;There is none except Me.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18584BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18584BQ\"></sup>Turn to Me and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18584BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18584BR\"></sup>be saved, all the ends of the earth;For I am God, and there is no other.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18585BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18585BS\"></sup>I have sworn by Myself,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18585BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18585BT\"></sup>word has gone forth from My mouth in righteousnessAnd will not turn back,That to Me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18585BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18585BU\"></sup>every knee will bow, every tongue will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18585BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18585BV\"></sup>swear <i>allegiance</i>.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“They will say of Me, ‘Only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18586BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18586BW\"></sup>in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> are righteousness and strength.’Men will come to Him,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18586BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18586BX\"></sup>all who were angry at Him will be put to shame.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“In the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> all the offspring of IsraelWill be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18587BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18587BY\"></sup>justified and will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18587BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18587BZ\"></sup>glory.”"
		},
		"46": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">46 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18588A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18588A\"></sup>Bel has bowed down, Nebo stoops over;Their images are <i>consigned</i> to the beasts and the cattle.The things that you carry are burdensome,A load for the weary <i>beast</i>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>They stooped over, they have bowed down together;They could not rescue the burden,But have themselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18589B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18589B\"></sup>gone into captivity.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18590C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18590C\"></sup>Listen to Me, O house of Jacob,And all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18590D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18590D\"></sup>the remnant of the house of Israel,You who have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18590E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18590E\"></sup>borne by Me from birthAnd have been carried from the womb;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Even to <i>your</i> old age <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18591F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18591F\"></sup>I will be the same,And even to <i>your</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18591G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18591G\"></sup>graying years I will bear <i>you</i>!I have done <i>it</i>, and I will carry <i>you</i>;And I will bear <i>you</i> and I will deliver <i>you</i>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18592H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18592H\"></sup>To whom would you liken MeAnd make Me equal and compare Me,That we would be alike?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18593I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18593I\"></sup>lavish gold from the purseAnd weigh silver on the scaleHire a goldsmith, and he makes it <i>into</i> a god;They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18593J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18593J\"></sup>bow down, indeed they worship it.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18594K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18594K\"></sup>lift it upon the shoulder <i>and</i> carry it;They set it in its place and it stands <i>there</i>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18594L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18594L\"></sup>It does not move from its place.Though one may cry to it, it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18594M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18594M\"></sup>cannot answer;It <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18594N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18594N\"></sup>cannot deliver him from his distress.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18595O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18595O\"></sup>Remember this, and be assured;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18595P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18595P\"></sup>Recall it to mind, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18595Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18595Q\"></sup>transgressors.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Remember the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18596R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18596R\"></sup>former things long past,For I am God, and there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18596S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18596S\"></sup>no other;<i>I am</i> God, and there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18596T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18596T\"></sup>no one like Me,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Declaring the end from the beginning,And from ancient times things which have not been done,Saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18597U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18597U\"></sup>My purpose will be established,And I will accomplish all My good pleasure’;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Calling a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18598V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18598V\"></sup>bird of prey from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18598W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18598W\"></sup>east,The man of My purpose from a far country.Truly I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18598X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18598X\"></sup>spoken; truly I will bring it to pass.I have planned <i>it, surely</i> I will do it.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18599Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18599Y\"></sup>Listen to Me, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18599Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18599Z\"></sup>stubborn-minded,Who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18599AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18599AA\"></sup>far from righteousness.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18600AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18600AB\"></sup>bring near My righteousness, it is not far off;And My salvation will not delay.And I will grant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18600AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18600AC\"></sup>salvation in Zion,<i>And</i> My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18600AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18600AD\"></sup>glory for Israel."
		},
		"47": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">47 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18601A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18601A\"></sup>Come down and sit in the dust,O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18601B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18601B\"></sup>virgin <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18601C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18601C\"></sup>daughter of Babylon;Sit on the ground without a throne,O daughter of the Chaldeans!For you shall no longer be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18601D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18601D\"></sup>tender and delicate.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Take the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18602E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18602E\"></sup>millstones and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18602F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18602F\"></sup>grind meal.Remove your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18602G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18602G\"></sup>veil, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18602H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18602H\"></sup>strip off the skirt,Uncover the leg, cross the rivers.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18603I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18603I\"></sup>nakedness will be uncovered,Your shame also will be exposed;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18603J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18603J\"></sup>take vengeance and will not spare a man.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18604K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18604K\"></sup>Redeemer, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is His name,The Holy One of Israel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18605L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18605L\"></sup>Sit silently, and go into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18605M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18605M\"></sup>darkness,O daughter of the Chaldeans,For you will no longer be calledThe <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18605N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18605N\"></sup>queen of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18605O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18605O\"></sup>kingdoms.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I was angry with My people,I profaned My heritageAnd gave them into your hand.You did not show mercy to them,On the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18606P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18606P\"></sup>aged you made your yoke very heavy.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Yet you said, ‘I will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18607Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18607Q\"></sup>queen forever.’These things you did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18607R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18607R\"></sup>considerNor remember the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18607S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18607S\"></sup>outcome of them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Now, then, hear this, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18608T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18608T\"></sup>sensual one,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18608U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18608U\"></sup>dwells securely,Who says in your heart,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18608V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18608V\"></sup>I am, and there is no one besides me.I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18608W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18608W\"></sup>not sit as a widow,Nor know loss of children.’",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“But these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18609X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18609X\"></sup>two things will come on you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18609Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18609Y\"></sup>suddenly in one day:Loss of children and widowhood.They will come on you in full measureIn spite of your many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18609Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18609Z\"></sup>sorceries,In spite of the great power of your spells.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“You felt <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18610AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18610AA\"></sup>secure in your wickedness and said,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18610AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18610AB\"></sup>No one sees me,’Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18610AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18610AC\"></sup>wisdom and your knowledge, they have deluded you;For you have said in your heart,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18610AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18610AD\"></sup>I am, and there is no one besides me.’",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18611AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18611AE\"></sup>evil will come on youWhich you will not know how to charm away;And disaster will fall on youFor which you cannot atone;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18611AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18611AF\"></sup>destruction about which you do not knowWill come on you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18611AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18611AG\"></sup>suddenly.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Stand <i>fast</i> now in your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18612AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18612AH\"></sup>spellsAnd in your many sorceriesWith which you have labored from your youth;Perhaps you will be able to profit,Perhaps you may cause trembling.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18613AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18613AI\"></sup>wearied with your many counsels;Let now the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18613AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18613AJ\"></sup>astrologers,Those who prophesy by the stars,Those who predict by the new moons,Stand up and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18613AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18613AK\"></sup>save you from what will come upon you.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Behold, they have become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18614AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18614AL\"></sup>like stubble,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18614AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18614AM\"></sup>Fire burns them;They cannot deliver themselves from the power of the flame;There will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18614AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18614AN\"></sup>no coal to warm by<i>Nor</i> a fire to sit before!",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“So have those become to you with whom you have labored,Who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18615AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18615AO\"></sup>trafficked with you from your youth;Each has wandered in his own way;There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18615AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18615AP\"></sup>none to save you."
		},
		"48": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">48 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18616A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18616A\"></sup>Hear this, O house of Jacob, who are named IsraelAnd who came forth from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18616B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18616B\"></sup>loins of Judah,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18616C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18616C\"></sup>swear by the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>And invoke the God of Israel,<i>But</i> not in truth nor in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18616D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18616D\"></sup>righteousness.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“For they call themselves after the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18617E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18617E\"></sup>holy cityAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18617F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18617F\"></sup>lean on the God of Israel;The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is His name.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18618G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18618G\"></sup>declared the former things long agoAnd they went forth from My mouth, and I proclaimed them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18618H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18618H\"></sup>Suddenly I acted, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18618I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18618I\"></sup>came to pass.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Because I know that you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18619J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18619J\"></sup>obstinate,And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18619K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18619K\"></sup>neck is an iron sinewAnd your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18619L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18619L\"></sup>forehead bronze,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Therefore I declared <i>them</i> to you long ago,Before they took place I proclaimed <i>them</i> to you,So that you would not say, ‘My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18620M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18620M\"></sup>idol has done them,And my graven image and my molten image have commanded them.’",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“You have heard; look at all this.And you, will you not declare it?I proclaim to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18621N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18621N\"></sup>new things from this time,Even hidden things which you have not known.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“They are created now and not long ago;And before today you have not heard them,So that you will not say, ‘Behold, I knew them.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“You have not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18623O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18623O\"></sup>heard, you have not known.Even from long ago your ear has not been open,Because I knew that you would deal very treacherously;And you have been called a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18623P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18623P\"></sup>rebel from birth.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18624Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18624Q\"></sup>For the sake of My name I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18624R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18624R\"></sup>delay My wrath,And <i>for</i> My praise I restrain <i>it</i> for you,In order not to cut you off.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Behold, I have refined you, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18625S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18625S\"></sup>not as silver;I have tested you in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18625T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18625T\"></sup>furnace of affliction.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18626U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18626U\"></sup>For My own sake, for My own sake, I will act;For how can <i>My name</i> be profaned?And My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18626V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18626V\"></sup>glory I will not give to another.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Listen to Me, O Jacob, even Israel whom I called;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18627W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18627W\"></sup>I am He, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18627X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18627X\"></sup>I am the first, I am also the last.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Surely My hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18628Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18628Y\"></sup>founded the earth,And My right hand spread out the heavens;When I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18628Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18628Z\"></sup>call to them, they stand together.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18629AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18629AA\"></sup>Assemble, all of you, and listen!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18629AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18629AB\"></sup>Who among them has declared these things?The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> loves him; he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18629AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18629AC\"></sup>carry out His good pleasure on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18629AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18629AD\"></sup>Babylon,And His arm <i>will be against</i> the Chaldeans.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“I, even I, have spoken; indeed I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18630AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18630AE\"></sup>called him,I have brought him, and He will make his ways successful.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18631AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18631AF\"></sup>Come near to Me, listen to this:From the first I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18631AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18631AG\"></sup>not spoken in secret,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18631AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18631AH\"></sup>From the time it took place, I was there.And now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18631AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18631AI\"></sup>the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> has sent Me, and His Spirit.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18632AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18632AJ\"></sup>Redeemer, the Holy One of Israel,“I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, who teaches you to profit,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18632AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18632AK\"></sup>leads you in the way you should go.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“If only you had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18633AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18633AL\"></sup>paid attention to My commandments!Then your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18633AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18633AM\"></sup>well-being would have been like a river,And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18633AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18633AN\"></sup>righteousness like the waves of the sea.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18634AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18634AO\"></sup>descendants would have been like the sand,And your offspring like its grains;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18634AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18634AP\"></sup>Their name would never be cut off or destroyed from My presence.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18635AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18635AQ\"></sup>Go forth from Babylon! Flee from the Chaldeans!Declare with the sound of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18635AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18635AR\"></sup>joyful shouting, proclaim this,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18635AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18635AS\"></sup>Send it out to the end of the earth;Say, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18635AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18635AT\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has redeemed His servant Jacob.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18636AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18636AU\"></sup>thirst when He led them through the deserts.He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18636AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18636AV\"></sup>made the water flow out of the rock for them;He split the rock and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18636AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18636AW\"></sup>the water gushed forth.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18637AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18637AX\"></sup>There is no peace for the wicked,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"49": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">49 </span>Listen to Me, O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18638A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18638A\"></sup>islands,And pay attention, you peoples from afar.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18638B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18638B\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> called Me from the womb;From the body of My mother He named Me.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He has made My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18639C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18639C\"></sup>mouth like a sharp sword,In the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18639D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18639D\"></sup>shadow of His hand He has concealed Me;And He has also made Me a select <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18639E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18639E\"></sup>arrow,He has hidden Me in His quiver.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He said to Me, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18640F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18640F\"></sup>You are My Servant, Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18640G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18640G\"></sup>In Whom I will show My glory.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But I said, “I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18641H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18641H\"></sup>toiled in vain,I have spent My strength for nothing and vanity;Yet surely the justice <i>due</i> to Me is with the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18641I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18641I\"></sup>reward with My God.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And now says <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18642J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18642J\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, who formed Me from the womb to be His Servant,To bring Jacob back to Him, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18642K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18642K\"></sup>Israel might be gathered to Him(For I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18642L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18642L\"></sup>honored in the sight of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And My God is My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18642M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18642M\"></sup>strength),",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He says, “It is too small a thing that You should be My ServantTo raise up the tribes of Jacob and to restore the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18643N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18643N\"></sup>preserved ones of Israel;I will also make You a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18643O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18643O\"></sup>light of the nationsSo that My salvation may reach to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18643P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18643P\"></sup>end of the earth.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18644Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18644Q\"></sup>Redeemer of Israel <i>and</i> its Holy One,To the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18644R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18644R\"></sup>despised One,To the One abhorred by the nation,To the Servant of rulers,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18644S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18644S\"></sup>Kings will see and arise,Princes will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18644T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18644T\"></sup>bow down,Because of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who is faithful, the Holy One of Israel who has chosen You.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“In a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18645U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18645U\"></sup>favorable time I have answered You,And in a day of salvation I have helped You;And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18645V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18645V\"></sup>keep You and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18645W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18645W\"></sup>give You for a covenant of the people,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18645X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18645X\"></sup>restore the land, to make <i>them</i> inherit the desolate heritages;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Saying to those who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18646Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18646Y\"></sup>bound, ‘Go forth,’To those who are in darkness, ‘Show yourselves.’Along the roads they will feed,And their pasture <i>will be</i> on all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18646Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18646Z\"></sup>bare heights.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18647AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18647AA\"></sup>not hunger or thirst,Nor will the scorching <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18647AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18647AB\"></sup>heat or sun strike them down;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18647AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18647AC\"></sup>He who has compassion on them will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18647AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18647AD\"></sup>lead themAnd will guide them to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18647AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18647AE\"></sup>springs of water.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“I will make all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18648AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18648AF\"></sup>My mountains a road,And My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18648AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18648AG\"></sup>highways will be raised up.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Behold, these will come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18649AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18649AH\"></sup>from afar;And lo, these <i>will come</i> from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18649AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18649AI\"></sup>north and from the west,And these from the land of Sinim.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18650AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18650AJ\"></sup>Shout for joy, O heavens! And rejoice, O earth!Break forth into joyful shouting, O mountains!For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18650AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18650AK\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has comforted His peopleAnd will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18650AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18650AL\"></sup>have compassion on His afflicted.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But Zion said, “The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has forsaken me,And the Lord has forgotten me.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Can a woman forget her nursing childAnd have no compassion on the son of her womb?Even these may forget, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18652AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18652AM\"></sup>I will not forget you.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Behold, I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18653AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18653AN\"></sup>inscribed you on the palms <i>of My hands</i>;Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18653AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18653AO\"></sup>walls are continually before Me.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Your builders hurry;Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18654AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18654AP\"></sup>destroyers and devastatorsWill depart from you.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18655AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18655AQ\"></sup>Lift up your eyes and look around;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18655AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18655AR\"></sup>All of them gather together, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18655AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18655AS\"></sup>they come to you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18655AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18655AT\"></sup>As I live,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“You will surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18655AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18655AU\"></sup>put on all of them as jewels and bind them on as a bride.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18656AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18656AV\"></sup>your waste and desolate places and your destroyed land—Surely now you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18656AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18656AW\"></sup>too cramped for the inhabitants,And those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18656AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18656AX\"></sup>swallowed you will be far away.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18657AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18657AY\"></sup>children of whom you were bereaved will yet say in your ears,‘The place is too cramped for me;Make room for me that I may live <i>here</i>.’",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18658AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18658AZ\"></sup>say in your heart,‘Who has begotten these for me,Since I have been bereaved of my childrenAnd am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18658BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18658BA\"></sup>barren, an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18658BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18658BB\"></sup>exile and a wanderer?And who has reared these?Behold, I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18658BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18658BC\"></sup>left alone;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18658BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18658BD\"></sup>From where did these come?’”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“Behold, I will lift up My hand to the nationsAnd set up My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18659BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18659BE\"></sup>standard to the peoples;And they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18659BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18659BF\"></sup>bring your sons in <i>their</i> bosom,And your daughters will be carried on <i>their</i> shoulders.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18660BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18660BG\"></sup>Kings will be your guardians,And their princesses your nurses.They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18660BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18660BH\"></sup>bow down to you with their faces to the earthAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18660BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18660BI\"></sup>lick the dust of your feet;And <i>you</i> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18660BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18660BJ\"></sup>know that I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;Those who hopefully <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18660BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18660BK\"></sup>wait for Me will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18660BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18660BL\"></sup>not be put to shame.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18661BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18661BM\"></sup>Can the prey be taken from the mighty man,Or the captives of a tyrant be rescued?”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Surely, thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Even the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18662BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18662BN\"></sup>captives of the mighty man will be taken away,And the prey of the tyrant will be rescued;For I will contend with the one who contends with you,And I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18662BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18662BO\"></sup>save your sons.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“I will feed your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18663BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18663BP\"></sup>oppressors with their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18663BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18663BQ\"></sup>own flesh,And they will become drunk with their own blood as with sweet wine;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18663BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18663BR\"></sup>all flesh will know that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, am your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18663BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18663BS\"></sup>SaviorAnd your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18663BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18663BT\"></sup>Redeemer, the Mighty One of Jacob.”"
		},
		"50": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">50 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“Where is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18664A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18664A\"></sup>certificate of divorceBy which I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18664B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18664B\"></sup>sent your mother away?Or to whom of My creditors did I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18664C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18664C\"></sup>sell you?Behold, you were sold for your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18664D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18664D\"></sup>iniquities,And for your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18664E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18664E\"></sup>transgressions your mother <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18664F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18664F\"></sup>was sent away.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Why was there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18665G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18665G\"></sup>no man when I came?When I called, <i>why</i> was there none to answer?Is My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18665H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18665H\"></sup>hand so short that it cannot ransom?Or have I no power to deliver?Behold, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18665I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18665I\"></sup>dry up the sea with My rebuke,I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18665J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18665J\"></sup>make the rivers a wilderness;Their fish stink for lack of waterAnd die of thirst.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18666K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18666K\"></sup>clothe the heavens with blacknessAnd make sackcloth their covering.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> has given Me the tongue of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18667L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18667L\"></sup>disciples,That I may know how to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18667M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18667M\"></sup>sustain the weary one with a word.He awakens <i>Me</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18667N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18667N\"></sup>morning by morning,He awakens My ear to listen as a disciple.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18668O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18668O\"></sup>opened My ear;And I was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18668P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18668P\"></sup>not disobedientNor did I turn back.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18669Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18669Q\"></sup>gave My back to those who strike <i>Me</i>,And My cheeks to those who pluck out the beard;I did not cover My face from humiliation and spitting.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18670R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18670R\"></sup>helps Me,Therefore, I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18670S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18670S\"></sup>not disgraced;Therefore, I have set My face like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18670T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18670T\"></sup>flint,And I know that I will not be ashamed.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18671U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18671U\"></sup>vindicates Me is near;Who will contend with Me?Let us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18671V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18671V\"></sup>stand up to each other;Who has a case against Me?Let him draw near to Me.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18672W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18672W\"></sup>the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> helps Me;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18672X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18672X\"></sup>Who is he who condemns Me?Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18672Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18672Y\"></sup>they will all wear out like a garment;The moth will eat them.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Who is among you that fears the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,That obeys the voice of His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18673Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18673Z\"></sup>servant,That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18673AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18673AA\"></sup>walks in darkness and has no light?Let him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18673AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18673AB\"></sup>trust in the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and rely on his God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Behold, all you who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18674AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18674AC\"></sup>kindle a fire,Who encircle yourselves with firebrands,Walk in the light of your fireAnd among the brands you have set ablaze.This you will have from My hand:You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18674AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18674AD\"></sup>lie down in torment."
		},
		"51": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">51 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18675A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18675A\"></sup>Listen to me, you who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18675B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18675B\"></sup>pursue righteousness,Who seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>:Look to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18675C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18675C\"></sup>rock from which you were hewnAnd to the quarry from which you were dug.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Look to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18676D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18676D\"></sup>Abraham your fatherAnd to Sarah who gave birth to you in pain;When <i>he</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18676E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18676E\"></sup><i>was but</i> one I called him,Then I blessed him and multiplied him.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Indeed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18677F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18677F\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will comfort Zion;He will comfort all her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18677G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18677G\"></sup>waste places.And her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18677H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18677H\"></sup>wilderness He will make like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18677I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18677I\"></sup>Eden,And her desert like the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18677J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18677J\"></sup>garden of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18677K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18677K\"></sup>Joy and gladness will be found in her,Thanksgiving and sound of a melody.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18678L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18678L\"></sup>Pay attention to Me, O My people,And give ear to Me, O My nation;For a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18678M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18678M\"></sup>law will go forth from Me,And I will set My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18678N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18678N\"></sup>justice for a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18678O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18678O\"></sup>light of the peoples.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18679P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18679P\"></sup>righteousness is near, My salvation has gone forth,And My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18679Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18679Q\"></sup>arms will judge the peoples;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18679R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18679R\"></sup>coastlands will wait for Me,And for My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18679S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18679S\"></sup>arm they will wait expectantly.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18680T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18680T\"></sup>Lift up your eyes to the sky,Then look to the earth beneath;For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18680U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18680U\"></sup>sky will vanish like smoke,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18680V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18680V\"></sup>earth will wear out like a garmentAnd its inhabitants will die in like manner;But My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18680W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18680W\"></sup>salvation will be forever,And My righteousness will not wane.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18681X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18681X\"></sup>Listen to Me, you who know righteousness,A people in whose <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18681Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18681Y\"></sup>heart is My law;Do not fear the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18681Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18681Z\"></sup>reproach of man,Nor be dismayed at their revilings.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18682AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18682AA\"></sup>moth will eat them like a garment,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18682AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18682AB\"></sup>grub will eat them like wool.But My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18682AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18682AC\"></sup>righteousness will be forever,And My salvation to all generations.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18683AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18683AD\"></sup>Awake, awake, put on strength, O arm of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;Awake as in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18683AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18683AE\"></sup>days of old, the generations of long ago.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18683AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18683AF\"></sup>Was it not You who cut Rahab in pieces,Who pierced the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18683AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18683AG\"></sup>dragon?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Was it not You who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18684AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18684AH\"></sup>dried up the sea,The waters of the great deep;Who made the depths of the sea a pathwayFor the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18684AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18684AI\"></sup>redeemed to cross over?",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18685AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18685AJ\"></sup>ransomed of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will returnAnd come with joyful shouting to Zion,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18685AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18685AK\"></sup>everlasting joy <i>will be</i> on their heads.They will obtain gladness and joy,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18685AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18685AL\"></sup>sorrow and sighing will flee away.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I, even I, am He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18686AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18686AM\"></sup>comforts you.Who are you that you are afraid of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18686AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18686AN\"></sup>man who diesAnd of the son of man who is made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18686AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18686AO\"></sup>like grass,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>That you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18687AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18687AP\"></sup>forgotten the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your Maker,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18687AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18687AQ\"></sup>stretched out the heavensAnd laid the foundations of the earth,That you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18687AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18687AR\"></sup>fear continually all day long because of the fury of the oppressor,As he makes ready to destroy?But where is the fury of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18687AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18687AS\"></sup>oppressor?",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18688AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18688AT\"></sup>exile will soon be set free, and will not die in the dungeon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18688AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18688AU\"></sup>nor will his bread be lacking.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For I am the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18689AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18689AV\"></sup>stirs up the sea and its waves roar (the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts is His name).",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18690AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18690AW\"></sup>put My words in your mouth and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18690AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18690AX\"></sup>covered you with the shadow of My hand, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18690AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18690AY\"></sup>establish the heavens, to found the earth, and to say to Zion, ‘You are My people.’”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18691AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18691AZ\"></sup>Rouse yourself! Rouse yourself! Arise, O Jerusalem,You who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18691BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18691BA\"></sup>drunk from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> hand the cup of His anger;The chalice of reeling you have drained to the dregs.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18692BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18692BB\"></sup>none to guide her among all the sons she has borne,Nor is there one to take her by the hand among all the sons she has reared.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>These two things have befallen you;Who will mourn for you?The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18693BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18693BC\"></sup>devastation and destruction, famine and sword;How shall I comfort you?",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Your sons have fainted,They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18694BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18694BD\"></sup>lie <i>helpless</i> at the head of every street,Like an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18694BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18694BE\"></sup>antelope in a net,Full of the wrath of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18694BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18694BF\"></sup>rebuke of your God.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Therefore, please hear this, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18695BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18695BG\"></sup>afflicted,Who are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18695BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18695BH\"></sup>drunk, but not with wine:",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Thus says your Lord, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, even your GodWho <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18696BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18696BI\"></sup>contends for His people,“Behold, I have taken out of your hand the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18696BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18696BJ\"></sup>cup of reeling,The chalice of My anger;You will never drink it again.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18697BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18697BK\"></sup>put it into the hand of your tormentors,Who have said to you, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18697BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18697BL\"></sup>Lie down that we may walk over <i>you</i>.’You have even made your back like the groundAnd like the street for those who walk over <i>it</i>.”"
		},
		"52": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">52 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18698A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18698A\"></sup>Awake, awake,Clothe yourself in your strength, O Zion;Clothe yourself in your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18698B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18698B\"></sup>beautiful garments,O Jerusalem, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18698C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18698C\"></sup>holy city;For the uncircumcised and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18698D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18698D\"></sup>uncleanWill no longer come into you.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Shake yourself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18699E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18699E\"></sup>from the dust, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18699F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18699F\"></sup>rise up,O captive Jerusalem;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18699G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18699G\"></sup>Loose yourself from the chains around your neck,O captive daughter of Zion.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “You were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18700H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18700H\"></sup>sold for nothing and you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18700I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18700I\"></sup>redeemed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18700J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18700J\"></sup>without money.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, “My people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18701K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18701K\"></sup>went down at the first into Egypt to reside there; then the Assyrian oppressed them without cause.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now therefore, what do I have here,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “seeing that My people have been taken away without cause?” <i>Again</i> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> declares, “Those who rule over them howl, and My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18702L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18702L\"></sup>name is continually blasphemed all day long.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore My people shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18703M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18703M\"></sup>know My name; therefore in that day I am the one who is speaking, ‘Here I am.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>How lovely on the mountainsAre the feet of him who brings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18704N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18704N\"></sup>good news,Who announces peaceAnd brings good news of happiness,Who announces salvation,<i>And</i> says to Zion, “Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18704O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18704O\"></sup>God reigns!”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Listen! Your watchmen lift up <i>their</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18705P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18705P\"></sup>voices,They shout joyfully together;For they will see with their own eyesWhen the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> restores Zion.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18706Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18706Q\"></sup>Break forth, shout joyfully together,You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18706R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18706R\"></sup>waste places of Jerusalem;For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has comforted His people,He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18706S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18706S\"></sup>redeemed Jerusalem.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has bared His holy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18707T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18707T\"></sup>armIn the sight of all the nations,That <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18707U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18707U\"></sup>all the ends of the earth may seeThe salvation of our God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18708V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18708V\"></sup>Depart, depart, go out from there,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18708W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18708W\"></sup>Touch nothing unclean;Go out of the midst of her, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18708X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18708X\"></sup>purify yourselves,You who carry the vessels of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But you will not go out in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18709Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18709Y\"></sup>haste,Nor will you go as fugitives;For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18709Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18709Z\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will go before you,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18709AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18709AA\"></sup>the God of Israel <i>will be</i> your rear guard.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Behold, My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18710AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18710AB\"></sup>servant will prosper,He will be high and lifted up and greatly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18710AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18710AC\"></sup>exalted.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Just as many were astonished at you, <i>My people</i>,So His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18711AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18711AD\"></sup>appearance was marred more than any manAnd His form more than the sons of men.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Thus He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18712AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18712AE\"></sup>sprinkle many nations,Kings will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18712AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18712AF\"></sup>shut their mouths on account of Him;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18712AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18712AG\"></sup>what had not been told them they will see,And what they had not heard they will understand."
		},
		"53": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">53 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18713A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18713A\"></sup>Who has believed our message?And to whom has the arm of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> been revealed?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For He grew up before Him like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18714B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18714B\"></sup>tender shoot,And like a root out of parched ground;He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18714C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18714C\"></sup>no <i>stately</i> form or majestyThat we should look upon Him,Nor appearance that we should be attracted to Him.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>He was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18715D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18715D\"></sup>despised and forsaken of men,A man of sorrows and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18715E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18715E\"></sup>acquainted with grief;And like one from whom men hide their faceHe was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18715F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18715F\"></sup>despised, and we did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18715G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18715G\"></sup>esteem Him.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Surely our griefs He Himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18716H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18716H\"></sup>bore,And our sorrows He carried;Yet we ourselves esteemed Him stricken,Smitten of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18716I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18716I\"></sup>God, and afflicted.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But He was pierced through for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18717J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18717J\"></sup>our transgressions,He was crushed for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18717K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18717K\"></sup>our iniquities;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18717L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18717L\"></sup>chastening for our well-being <i>fell</i> upon Him,And by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18717M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18717M\"></sup>His scourging we are healed.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>All of us like sheep have gone astray,Each of us has turned to his own way;But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has caused the iniquity of us allTo fall on Him.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>He was oppressed and He was afflicted,Yet He did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18719N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18719N\"></sup>open His mouth;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18719O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18719O\"></sup>Like a lamb that is led to slaughter,And like a sheep that is silent before its shearers,So He did not open His mouth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>By oppression and judgment He was taken away;And as for His generation, who consideredThat He was cut off out of the land of the living<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18720P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18720P\"></sup>For the transgression of my people, to whom the stroke <i>was due</i>?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>His grave was assigned with wicked men,Yet He was with a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18721Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18721Q\"></sup>rich man in His death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18721R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18721R\"></sup>Because He had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18721S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18721S\"></sup>done no violence,Nor was there any deceit in His mouth.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> was pleasedTo <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18722T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18722T\"></sup>crush Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18722U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18722U\"></sup>putting <i>Him</i> to grief;If He would render Himself <i>as</i> a guilt <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18722V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18722V\"></sup>offering,He will see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18722W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18722W\"></sup><i>His</i> offspring,He will prolong <i>His</i> days,And the good <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18722X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18722X\"></sup>pleasure of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will prosper in His hand.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>As a result of the anguish of His soul,He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18723Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18723Y\"></sup>see <i>it and</i> be satisfied;By His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18723Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18723Z\"></sup>knowledge the Righteous One,My Servant, will justify the many,As He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18723AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18723AA\"></sup>bear their iniquities.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore, I will allot Him a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18724AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18724AB\"></sup>portion with the great,And He will divide the booty with the strong;Because He poured out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18724AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18724AC\"></sup>Himself to death,And was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18724AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18724AD\"></sup>numbered with the transgressors;Yet He Himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18724AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18724AE\"></sup>bore the sin of many,And interceded for the transgressors."
		},
		"54": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">54 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18725A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18725A\"></sup>Shout for joy, O barren one, you who have borne no <i>child</i>;Break forth into joyful shouting and cry aloud, you who have not travailed;For the sons of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18725B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18725B\"></sup>desolate one <i>will be</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18725C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18725C\"></sup>more numerousThan the sons of the married woman,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18726D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18726D\"></sup>Enlarge the place of your tent;Stretch out the curtains of your dwellings, spare not;Lengthen your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18726E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18726E\"></sup>cordsAnd strengthen your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18726F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18726F\"></sup>pegs.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“For you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18727G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18727G\"></sup>spread abroad to the right and to the left.And your descendants will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18727H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18727H\"></sup>possess nationsAnd will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18727I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18727I\"></sup>resettle the desolate cities.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Fear not, for you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18728J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18728J\"></sup>not be put to shame;And do not feel humiliated, for you will not be disgraced;But you will forget the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18728K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18728K\"></sup>shame of your youth,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18728L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18728L\"></sup>reproach of your widowhood you will remember no more.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“For your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18729M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18729M\"></sup>husband is your Maker,Whose name is the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> of hosts;And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18729N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18729N\"></sup>Redeemer is the Holy One of Israel,Who is called the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18729O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18729O\"></sup>God of all the earth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has called you,Like a wife <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18730P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18730P\"></sup>forsaken and grieved in spirit,Even like a wife of <i>one’s</i> youth when she is rejected,”Says your God.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“For a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18731Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18731Q\"></sup>brief moment I forsook you,But with great compassion I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18731R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18731R\"></sup>gather you.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“In an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18732S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18732S\"></sup>outburst of angerI hid My face from you for a moment,But with everlasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18732T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18732T\"></sup>lovingkindness I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18732U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18732U\"></sup>have compassion on you,”Says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18732V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18732V\"></sup>Redeemer.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“For this is like the days of Noah to Me,When I swore that the waters of NoahWould <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18733W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18733W\"></sup>not flood the earth again;So I have sworn that I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18733X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18733X\"></sup>not be angry with youNor will I rebuke you.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18734Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18734Y\"></sup>mountains may be removed and the hills may shake,But My lovingkindness will not be removed from you,And My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18734Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18734Z\"></sup>covenant of peace will not be shaken,”Says <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18734AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18734AA\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who has compassion on you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“O <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18735AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18735AB\"></sup>afflicted one, storm-tossed, <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18735AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18735AC\"></sup>not comforted,Behold, I will set your stones in antimony,And your foundations I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18735AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18735AD\"></sup>lay in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18735AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18735AE\"></sup>sapphires.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Moreover, I will make your battlements of rubies,And your gates of crystal,And your entire wall of precious stones.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18737AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18737AF\"></sup>All your sons will be taught of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;And the well-being of your sons will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18737AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18737AG\"></sup>great.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“In <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18738AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18738AH\"></sup>righteousness you will be established;You will be far from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18738AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18738AI\"></sup>oppression, for you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18738AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18738AJ\"></sup>not fear;And from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18738AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18738AK\"></sup>terror, for it will not come near you.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“If anyone fiercely assails <i>you</i> it will not be from Me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18739AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18739AL\"></sup>Whoever assails you will fall because of you.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Behold, I Myself have created the smith who blows the fire of coalsAnd brings out a weapon for its work;And I have created the destroyer to ruin.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18741AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18741AM\"></sup>No weapon that is formed against you will prosper;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18741AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18741AN\"></sup>every tongue that accuses you in judgment you will condemn.This is the heritage of the servants of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18741AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18741AO\"></sup>vindication is from Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"55": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">55 </span>“Ho! Every one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18742A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18742A\"></sup>thirsts, come to the waters;And you who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18742B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18742B\"></sup>no money come, buy and eat.Come, buy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18742C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18742C\"></sup>wine and milk<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18742D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18742D\"></sup>Without money and without cost.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Why do you spend money for what is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18743E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18743E\"></sup>not bread,And your wages for what does not satisfy?Listen carefully to Me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18743F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18743F\"></sup>eat what is good,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18743G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18743G\"></sup>delight yourself in abundance.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18744H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18744H\"></sup>Incline your ear and come to Me.Listen, that you may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18744I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18744I\"></sup>live;And I will make <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18744J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18744J\"></sup>an everlasting covenant with you,<i>According to</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18744K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18744K\"></sup>faithful mercies shown to David.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Behold, I have made <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18745L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18745L\"></sup>him a witness to the peoples,A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18745M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18745M\"></sup>leader and commander for the peoples.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Behold, you will call a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18746N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18746N\"></sup>nation you do not know,And a nation which knows you not will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18746O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18746O\"></sup>run to you,Because of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God, even the Holy One of Israel;For He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18746P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18746P\"></sup>glorified you.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18747Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18747Q\"></sup>Seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> while He may be found;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18747R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18747R\"></sup>Call upon Him while He is near.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18748S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18748S\"></sup>Let the wicked forsake his wayAnd the unrighteous man his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18748T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18748T\"></sup>thoughts;And let him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18748U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18748U\"></sup>return to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And He will have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18748V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18748V\"></sup>compassion on him,And to our God,For He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18748W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18748W\"></sup>abundantly pardon.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“For My thoughts are not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18749X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18749X\"></sup>your thoughts,Nor are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18749Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18749Y\"></sup>your ways My ways,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18750Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18750Z\"></sup><i>as</i> the heavens are higher than the earth,So are My ways higher than your waysAnd My thoughts than your thoughts.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“For as the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18751AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18751AA\"></sup>rain and the snow come down from heaven,And do not return there without watering the earthAnd making it bear and sprout,And furnishing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18751AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18751AB\"></sup>seed to the sower and bread to the eater;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So will My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18752AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18752AC\"></sup>word be which goes forth from My mouth;It will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18752AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18752AD\"></sup>not return to Me empty,Without <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18752AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18752AE\"></sup>accomplishing what I desire,And without succeeding <i>in the matter</i> for which I sent it.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“For you will go out with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18753AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18753AF\"></sup>joyAnd be led forth with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18753AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18753AG\"></sup>peace;The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18753AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18753AH\"></sup>mountains and the hills will break forth into shouts of joy before you,And all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18753AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18753AI\"></sup>trees of the field will clap <i>their</i> hands.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“Instead of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18754AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18754AJ\"></sup>thorn bush the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18754AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18754AK\"></sup>cypress will come up,And instead of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18754AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18754AL\"></sup>nettle the myrtle will come up,And it will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18754AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18754AM\"></sup>memorial to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,For an everlasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18754AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18754AN\"></sup>sign which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18754AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18754AO\"></sup>will not be cut off.”"
		},
		"56": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">56 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18755A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18755A\"></sup>Preserve justice and do righteousness,For My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18755B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18755B\"></sup>salvation is about to comeAnd My righteousness to be revealed.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“How <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18756C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18756C\"></sup>blessed is the man who does this,And the son of man who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18756D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18756D\"></sup>takes hold of it;Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18756E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18756E\"></sup>keeps from profaning the sabbath,And keeps his hand from doing any evil.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Let not the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18757F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18757F\"></sup>foreigner who has joined himself to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> say,“The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will surely separate me from His people.”Nor let the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18757G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18757G\"></sup>eunuch say, “Behold, I am a dry tree.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“To the eunuchs who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18758H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18758H\"></sup>keep My sabbaths,And choose what pleases Me,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18758I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18758I\"></sup>hold fast My covenant,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>To them I will give in My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18759J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18759J\"></sup>house and within My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18759K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18759K\"></sup>walls a memorial,And a name better than that of sons and daughters;I will give them an everlasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18759L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18759L\"></sup>name which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18759M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18759M\"></sup>will not be cut off.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Also the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18760N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18760N\"></sup>foreigners who join themselves to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,To minister to Him, and to love the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,To be His servants, every one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18760O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18760O\"></sup>keeps from profaning the sabbathAnd holds fast My covenant;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18761P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18761P\"></sup>those I will bring to My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18761Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18761Q\"></sup>holy mountainAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18761R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18761R\"></sup>make them joyful in My house of prayer.Their burnt offerings and their sacrifices will be acceptable on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18761S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18761S\"></sup>My altar;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18761T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18761T\"></sup>My house will be called a house of prayer for all the peoples.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18762U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18762U\"></sup>gathers the dispersed of Israel, declares,“Yet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18762V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18762V\"></sup><i>others</i> I will gather to them, to those <i>already</i> gathered.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>All you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18763W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18763W\"></sup>beasts of the field,All you beasts in the forest,Come to eat.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18764X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18764X\"></sup>watchmen are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18764Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18764Y\"></sup>blind,All of them know nothing.All of them are mute dogs unable to bark,Dreamers lying down, who love to slumber;",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the dogs are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18765Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18765Z\"></sup>greedy, they are not satisfied.And they are shepherds who have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18765AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18765AA\"></sup>no understanding;They have all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18765AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18765AB\"></sup>turned to their own way,Each one to his unjust gain, to the last one.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Come,” <i>they say</i>, “let us get <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18766AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18766AC\"></sup>wine, and let us drink heavily of strong drink;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18766AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18766AD\"></sup>tomorrow will be like today, only more so.”"
		},
		"57": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">57 </span>The righteous man perishes, and no man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18767A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18767A\"></sup>takes it to heart;And devout men are taken away, while no one understands.For the righteous man is taken away from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18767B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18767B\"></sup>evil,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He enters into peace;They rest in their beds,<i>Each one</i> who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18768C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18768C\"></sup>walked in his upright way.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“But come here, you sons of a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18769D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18769D\"></sup>sorceress,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18769E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18769E\"></sup>Offspring of an adulterer and a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18769F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18769F\"></sup>prostitute.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Against whom do you jest?Against whom do you open wide your mouthAnd stick out your tongue?Are you not children of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18770G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18770G\"></sup>rebellion,Offspring of deceit,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><i>Who</i> inflame yourselves among the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18771H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18771H\"></sup>oaks,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18771I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18771I\"></sup>Under every luxuriant tree,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18771J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18771J\"></sup>slaughter the children in the ravines,Under the clefts of the crags?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Among the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18772K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18772K\"></sup>smooth <i>stones</i> of the ravineIs your portion, they are your lot;Even to them you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18772L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18772L\"></sup>poured out a drink offering,You have made a grain offering.Shall I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18772M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18772M\"></sup>relent concerning these things?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Upon a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18773N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18773N\"></sup>high and lofty mountainYou have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18773O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18773O\"></sup>made your bed.You also went up there to offer sacrifice.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Behind the door and the doorpostYou have set up your sign;Indeed, far removed from Me, you have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18774P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18774P\"></sup>uncovered yourself,And have gone up and made your bed wide.And you have made an agreement for yourself with them,You have loved their bed,You have looked on <i>their</i> manhood.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“You have journeyed to the king with oilAnd increased your perfumes;You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18775Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18775Q\"></sup>sent your envoys a great distanceAnd made <i>them</i> go down to Sheol.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“You were tired out by the length of your road,<i>Yet</i> you did not say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18776R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18776R\"></sup>It is hopeless.’You found renewed strength,Therefore you did not faint.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18777S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18777S\"></sup>whom were you worried and fearfulWhen you lied, and did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18777T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18777T\"></sup>not remember MeNor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18777U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18777U\"></sup>give <i>Me</i> a thought?Was I not silent even for a long timeSo you do not fear Me?",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18778V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18778V\"></sup>declare your righteousness and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18778W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18778W\"></sup>deeds,But they will not profit you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“When you cry out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18779X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18779X\"></sup>let your collection <i>of idols</i> deliver you.But the wind will carry all of them up,<i>And</i> a breath will take <i>them away</i>.But he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18779Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18779Y\"></sup>takes refuge in Me will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18779Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18779Z\"></sup>inherit the landAnd will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18779AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18779AA\"></sup>possess My holy mountain.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And it will be said,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18780AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18780AB\"></sup>Build up, build up, prepare the way,Remove <i>every</i> obstacle out of the way of My people.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For thus says the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18781AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18781AC\"></sup>high and exalted OneWho <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18781AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18781AD\"></sup>lives forever, whose name is Holy,“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18781AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18781AE\"></sup>dwell <i>on</i> a high and holy place,And <i>also</i> with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18781AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18781AF\"></sup>contrite and lowly of spiritIn order to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18781AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18781AG\"></sup>revive the spirit of the lowlyAnd to revive the heart of the contrite.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“For I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18782AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18782AH\"></sup>not contend forever,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18782AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18782AI\"></sup>Nor will I always be angry;For the spirit would grow faint before Me,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18782AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18782AJ\"></sup>breath <i>of those whom</i> I have made.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Because of the iniquity of his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18783AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18783AK\"></sup>unjust gain I was angry and struck him;I hid <i>My face</i> and was angry,And he went on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18783AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18783AL\"></sup>turning away, in the way of his heart.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“I have seen his ways, but I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18784AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18784AM\"></sup>heal him;I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18784AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18784AN\"></sup>lead him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18784AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18784AO\"></sup>restore comfort to him and to his mourners,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Creating the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18785AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18785AP\"></sup>praise of the lips.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18785AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18785AQ\"></sup>Peace, peace to him who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18785AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18785AR\"></sup>far and to him who is near,”Says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “and I will heal him.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18786AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18786AS\"></sup>wicked are like the tossing sea,For it cannot be quiet,And its waters toss up refuse and mud.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18787AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18787AT\"></sup>There is no peace,” says <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18787AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18787AU\"></sup>my God, “for the wicked.”"
		},
		"58": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">58 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18788A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18788A\"></sup>Cry loudly, do not hold back;Raise your voice like a trumpet,And declare to My people their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18788B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18788B\"></sup>transgressionAnd to the house of Jacob their sins.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Yet they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18789C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18789C\"></sup>seek Me day by day and delight to know My ways,As a nation that has done <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18789D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18789D\"></sup>righteousnessAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18789E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18789E\"></sup>has not forsaken the ordinance of their God.They ask Me <i>for</i> just decisions,They delight <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18789F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18789F\"></sup>in the nearness of God.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>‘Why have we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18790G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18790G\"></sup>fasted and You do not see?<i>Why</i> have we humbled ourselves and You do not notice?’Behold, on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18790H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18790H\"></sup>day of your fast you find <i>your</i> desire,And drive hard all your workers.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Behold, you fast for contention and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18791I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18791I\"></sup>strife and to strike with a wicked fist.You do not fast like <i>you do</i> today to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18791J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18791J\"></sup>make your voice heard on high.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Is it a fast like this which I choose, a day for a man to humble himself?Is it for bowing one’s head like a reedAnd for spreading out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18792K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18792K\"></sup>sackcloth and ashes as a bed?Will you call this a fast, even an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18792L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18792L\"></sup>acceptable day to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Is this not the fast which I choose,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18793M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18793M\"></sup>loosen the bonds of wickedness,To undo the bands of the yoke,And to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18793N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18793N\"></sup>let the oppressed go freeAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18793O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18793O\"></sup>break every yoke?",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Is it not to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18794P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18794P\"></sup>divide your bread with the hungryAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18794Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18794Q\"></sup>bring the homeless poor into the house;When you see the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18794R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18794R\"></sup>naked, to cover him;And not to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18794S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18794S\"></sup>hide yourself from your own flesh?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Then your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18795T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18795T\"></sup>light will break out like the dawn,And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18795U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18795U\"></sup>recovery will speedily spring forth;And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18795V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18795V\"></sup>righteousness will go before you;The glory of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18795W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18795W\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be your rear guard.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18796X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18796X\"></sup>call, and the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will answer;You will cry, and He will say, ‘Here I am.’If you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18796Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18796Y\"></sup>remove the yoke from your midst,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18796Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18796Z\"></sup>pointing of the finger and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18796AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18796AA\"></sup>speaking wickedness,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And if you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18797AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18797AB\"></sup>give yourself to the hungryAnd satisfy the desire of the afflicted,Then your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18797AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18797AC\"></sup>light will rise in darknessAnd your gloom <i>will become</i> like midday.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18798AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18798AD\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will continually guide you,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18798AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18798AE\"></sup>satisfy your desire in scorched places,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18798AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18798AF\"></sup>give strength to your bones;And you will be like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18798AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18798AG\"></sup>watered garden,And like a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18798AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18798AH\"></sup>spring of water whose waters do not fail.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Those from among you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18799AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18799AI\"></sup>rebuild the ancient ruins;You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18799AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18799AJ\"></sup>raise up the age-old foundations;And you will be called the repairer of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18799AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18799AK\"></sup>breach,The restorer of the streets in which to dwell.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“If because of the sabbath, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18800AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18800AL\"></sup>turn your footFrom doing your <i>own</i> pleasure on My holy day,And call the sabbath a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18800AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18800AM\"></sup>delight, the holy <i>day</i> of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> honorable,And honor it, desisting from your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18800AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18800AN\"></sup><i>own</i> ways,From seeking your <i>own</i> pleasureAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18800AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18800AO\"></sup>speaking <i>your own</i> word,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then you will take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18801AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18801AP\"></sup>delight in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And I will make you ride <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18801AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18801AQ\"></sup>on the heights of the earth;And I will feed you <i>with</i> the heritage of Jacob your father,For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18801AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18801AR\"></sup>mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has spoken.”"
		},
		"59": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">59 </span>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18802A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18802A\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord’s</span> hand is not so shortThat it cannot save;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18802B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18802B\"></sup>Nor is His ear so dullThat it cannot hear.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18803C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18803C\"></sup>iniquities have made a separation between you and your God,And your sins have hidden <i>His</i> face from you so that He does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18803D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18803D\"></sup>not hear.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18804E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18804E\"></sup>hands are defiled with bloodAnd your fingers with iniquity;Your lips have spoken <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18804F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18804F\"></sup>falsehood,Your tongue mutters wickedness.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18805G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18805G\"></sup>No one sues righteously and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18805H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18805H\"></sup>no one pleads honestly.They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18805I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18805I\"></sup>trust in confusion and speak lies;They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18805J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18805J\"></sup>conceive mischief and bring forth iniquity.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They hatch adders’ eggs and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18806K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18806K\"></sup>weave the spider’s web;He who eats of their eggs dies,And <i>from</i> that which is crushed a snake breaks forth.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Their webs will not become clothing,Nor will they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18807L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18807L\"></sup>cover themselves with their works;Their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18807M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18807M\"></sup>works are works of iniquity,And an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18807N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18807N\"></sup>act of violence is in their hands.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18808O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18808O\"></sup>Their feet run to evil,And they hasten to shed innocent blood;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18808P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18808P\"></sup>Their thoughts are thoughts of iniquity,Devastation and destruction are in their highways.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They do not know the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18809Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18809Q\"></sup>way of peace,And there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18809R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18809R\"></sup>no justice in their tracks;They have made their paths crooked,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18809S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18809S\"></sup>Whoever treads on them does not know peace.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18810T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18810T\"></sup>justice is far from us,And righteousness does not overtake us;We <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18810U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18810U\"></sup>hope for light, but behold, darkness,For brightness, but we walk in gloom.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>We <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18811V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18811V\"></sup>grope along the wall like blind men,We grope like those who have no eyes;We <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18811W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18811W\"></sup>stumble at midday as in the twilight,Among those who are vigorous <i>we are</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18811X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18811X\"></sup>like dead men.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>All of us growl like bears,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18812Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18812Y\"></sup>moan sadly like doves;We hope for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18812Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18812Z\"></sup>justice, but there is none,For salvation, <i>but</i> it is far from us.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18813AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18813AA\"></sup>transgressions are multiplied before You,And our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18813AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18813AB\"></sup>sins testify against us;For our transgressions are with us,And we know our iniquities:",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Transgressing and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18814AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18814AC\"></sup>denying the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And turning away from our God,Speaking <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18814AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18814AD\"></sup>oppression and revolt,Conceiving <i>in</i> and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18814AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18814AE\"></sup>uttering from the heart lying words.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18815AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18815AF\"></sup>Justice is turned back,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18815AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18815AG\"></sup>righteousness stands far away;For truth has stumbled in the street,And uprightness cannot enter.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Yes, truth is lacking;And he who turns aside from evil <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18816AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18816AH\"></sup>makes himself a prey.Now the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> saw,And it was displeasing in His sight <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18816AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18816AI\"></sup>that there was no justice.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And He saw that there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18817AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18817AJ\"></sup>no man,And was astonished that there was no one to intercede;Then His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18817AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18817AK\"></sup>own arm brought salvation to Him,And His righteousness upheld Him.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He put on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18818AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18818AL\"></sup>righteousness like a breastplate,And a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18818AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18818AM\"></sup>helmet of salvation on His head;And He put on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18818AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18818AN\"></sup>garments of vengeance for clothingAnd wrapped Himself with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18818AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18818AO\"></sup>zeal as a mantle.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18819AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18819AP\"></sup>According to <i>their</i> deeds, so He will repay,Wrath to His adversaries, recompense to His enemies;To the coastlands He will make recompense.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So they will fear the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18820AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18820AQ\"></sup>westAnd His glory from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18820AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18820AR\"></sup>rising of the sun,For He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18820AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18820AS\"></sup>come like a rushing streamWhich the wind of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> drives.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“A <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18821AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18821AT\"></sup>Redeemer will come to Zion,And to those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18821AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18821AU\"></sup>turn from transgression in Jacob,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“As for Me, this is My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18822AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18822AV\"></sup>covenant with them,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>: “My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18822AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18822AW\"></sup>Spirit which is upon you, and My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18822AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18822AX\"></sup>words which I have put in your mouth shall not depart from your mouth, nor from the mouth of your offspring, nor from the mouth of your offspring’s offspring,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “from now and forever.”"
		},
		"60": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">60 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18823A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18823A\"></sup>Arise, shine; for your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18823B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18823B\"></sup>light has come,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18823C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18823C\"></sup>glory of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has risen upon you.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“For behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18824D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18824D\"></sup>darkness will cover the earthAnd deep darkness the peoples;But the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will rise upon youAnd His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18824E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18824E\"></sup>glory will appear upon you.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18825F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18825F\"></sup>Nations will come to your light,And kings to the brightness of your rising.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18826G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18826G\"></sup>Lift up your eyes round about and see;They all gather together, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18826H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18826H\"></sup>come to you.Your sons will come from afar,And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18826I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18826I\"></sup>daughters will be carried in the arms.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Then you will see and be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18827J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18827J\"></sup>radiant,And your heart will thrill and rejoice;Because the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18827K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18827K\"></sup>abundance of the sea will be turned to you,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18827L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18827L\"></sup>wealth of the nations will come to you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“A multitude of camels will cover you,The young camels of Midian and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18828M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18828M\"></sup>Ephah;All those from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18828N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18828N\"></sup>Sheba will come;They will bring <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18828O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18828O\"></sup>gold and frankincense,And will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18828P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18828P\"></sup>bear good news of the praises of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“All the flocks of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18829Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18829Q\"></sup>Kedar will be gathered together to you,The rams of Nebaioth will minister to you;They will go up with acceptance on My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18829R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18829R\"></sup>altar,And I shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18829S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18829S\"></sup>glorify My glorious house.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18830T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18830T\"></sup>Who are these who fly like a cloudAnd like the doves to their lattices?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Surely the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18831U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18831U\"></sup>coastlands will wait for Me;And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18831V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18831V\"></sup>ships of Tarshish <i>will come</i> first,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18831W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18831W\"></sup>bring your sons from afar,Their silver and their gold with them,For the name of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God,And for the Holy One of Israel because He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18831X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18831X\"></sup>glorified you.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18832Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18832Y\"></sup>Foreigners will build up your walls,And their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18832Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18832Z\"></sup>kings will minister to you;For in My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18832AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18832AA\"></sup>wrath I struck you,And in My favor I have had compassion on you.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18833AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18833AB\"></sup>gates will be open continually;They will not be closed day or night,So that <i>men</i> may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18833AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18833AC\"></sup>bring to you the wealth of the nations,With <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18833AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18833AD\"></sup>their kings led in procession.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18834AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18834AE\"></sup>nation and the kingdom which will not serve you will perish,And the nations will be utterly ruined.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18835AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18835AF\"></sup>glory of Lebanon will come to you,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18835AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18835AG\"></sup>juniper, the box tree and the cypress together,To beautify the place of My sanctuary;And I shall make the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18835AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18835AH\"></sup>place of My feet glorious.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18836AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18836AI\"></sup>sons of those who afflicted you will come bowing to you,And all those who despised you will bow themselves at the soles of your feet;And they will call you the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18836AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18836AJ\"></sup>city of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18836AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18836AK\"></sup>Zion of the Holy One of Israel.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Whereas you have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18837AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18837AL\"></sup>forsaken and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18837AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18837AM\"></sup>hatedWith no one passing through,I will make you an everlasting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18837AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18837AN\"></sup>pride,A joy from generation to generation.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“You will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18838AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18838AO\"></sup>suck the milk of nationsAnd suck the breast of kings;Then you will know that I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, am your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18838AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18838AP\"></sup>SaviorAnd your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18838AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18838AQ\"></sup>Redeemer, the Mighty One of Jacob.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Instead of bronze I will bring gold,And instead of iron I will bring silver,And instead of wood, bronze,And instead of stones, iron.And I will make peace your administratorsAnd righteousness your overseers.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18840AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18840AR\"></sup>Violence will not be heard again in your land,Nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18840AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18840AS\"></sup>devastation or destruction within your borders;But you will call your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18840AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18840AT\"></sup>walls salvation, and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18840AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18840AU\"></sup>gates praise.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“No longer will you have the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18841AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18841AV\"></sup>sun for light by day,Nor for brightness will the moon give you light;But you will have the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18841AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18841AW\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> for an everlasting light,And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18841AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18841AX\"></sup>God for your glory.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18842AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18842AY\"></sup>sun will no longer set,Nor will your moon wane;For you will have the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> for an everlasting light,And the days of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18842AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18842AZ\"></sup>mourning will be over.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Then all your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18843BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18843BA\"></sup>people <i>will be</i> righteous;They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18843BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18843BB\"></sup>possess the land forever,The branch of My planting,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18843BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18843BC\"></sup>work of My hands,That I may be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18843BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18843BD\"></sup>glorified.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18844BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18844BE\"></sup>smallest one will become a clan,And the least one a mighty nation.I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, will hasten it in its time.”"
		},
		"61": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">61 </span>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18845A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18845A\"></sup>Spirit of the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> is upon me,Because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has anointed meTo <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18845B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18845B\"></sup>bring good news to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18845C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18845C\"></sup>afflicted;He has sent me to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18845D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18845D\"></sup>bind up the brokenhearted,To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18845E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18845E\"></sup>proclaim liberty to captivesAnd freedom to prisoners;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18846F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18846F\"></sup>proclaim the favorable year of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18846G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18846G\"></sup>day of vengeance of our God;To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18846H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18846H\"></sup>comfort all who mourn,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18847I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18847I\"></sup>grant those who mourn <i>in</i> Zion,Giving them a garland instead of ashes,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18847J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18847J\"></sup>oil of gladness instead of mourning,The mantle of praise instead of a spirit of fainting.So they will be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18847K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18847K\"></sup>oaks of righteousness,The planting of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, that He may be glorified.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18848L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18848L\"></sup>rebuild the ancient ruins,They will raise up the former devastations;And they will repair the ruined cities,The desolations of many generations.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18849M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18849M\"></sup>Strangers will stand and pasture your flocks,And foreigners will be your farmers and your vinedressers.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But you will be called the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18850N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18850N\"></sup>priests of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;You will be spoken of <i>as</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18850O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18850O\"></sup>ministers of our God.You will eat the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18850P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18850P\"></sup>wealth of nations,And in their riches you will boast.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Instead of your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18851Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18851Q\"></sup>shame <i>you will have a</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18851R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18851R\"></sup>double <i>portion</i>,And <i>instead of</i> humiliation they will shout for joy over their portion.Therefore they will possess a double <i>portion</i> in their land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18851S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18851S\"></sup>Everlasting joy will be theirs.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18852T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18852T\"></sup>love justice,I hate robbery in the burnt offering;And I will faithfully give them their recompenseAnd make an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18852U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18852U\"></sup>everlasting covenant with them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then their offspring will be known among the nations,And their descendants in the midst of the peoples.All who see them will recognize themBecause they are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18853V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18853V\"></sup>offspring <i>whom</i> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has blessed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18854W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18854W\"></sup>rejoice greatly in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,My soul will exult in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18854X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18854X\"></sup>my God;For He has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18854Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18854Y\"></sup>clothed me with garments of salvation,He has wrapped me with a robe of righteousness,As a bridegroom decks himself with a garland,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18854Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18854Z\"></sup>as a bride adorns herself with her jewels.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For as the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18855AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18855AA\"></sup>earth brings forth its sprouts,And as a garden causes the things sown in it to spring up,So the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18855AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18855AB\"></sup>cause <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18855AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18855AC\"></sup>righteousness and praiseTo spring up before all the nations."
		},
		"62": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">62 </span>For Zion’s sake I will not keep silent,And for Jerusalem’s sake I will not keep quiet,Until her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18856A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18856A\"></sup>righteousness goes forth like brightness,And her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18856B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18856B\"></sup>salvation like a torch that is burning.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18857C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18857C\"></sup>nations will see your righteousness,And all kings your glory;And you will be called by a new <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18857D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18857D\"></sup>nameWhich the mouth of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will designate.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>You will also be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18858E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18858E\"></sup>crown of beauty in the hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And a royal diadem in the hand of your God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>It will no longer be said to you, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18859F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18859F\"></sup>Forsaken,”Nor to your land will it any longer be said, “Desolate”;But you will be called, “My delight is in her,”And your land, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18859G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18859G\"></sup>Married”;For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18859H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18859H\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> delights in you,And <i>to Him</i> your land will be married.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For <i>as</i> a young man marries a virgin,<i>So</i> your sons will marry you;And <i>as</i> the bridegroom rejoices over the bride,<i>So</i> your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18860I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18860I\"></sup>God will rejoice over you.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>On your walls, O Jerusalem, I have appointed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18861J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18861J\"></sup>watchmen;All day and all night they will never keep silent.You who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18861K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18861K\"></sup>remind the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, take no rest for yourselves;",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18862L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18862L\"></sup>give Him no rest until He establishesAnd makes <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18862M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18862M\"></sup>Jerusalem a praise in the earth.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18863N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18863N\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has sworn by His right hand and by His strong arm,“I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18863O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18863O\"></sup>never again give your grain <i>as</i> food for your enemies;Nor will foreigners drink your new wine for which you have labored.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18864P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18864P\"></sup>garner it will eat it and praise the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;And those who gather it will drink it in the courts of My sanctuary.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Go through, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18865Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18865Q\"></sup>go through the gates,Clear the way for the people;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18865R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18865R\"></sup>Build up, build up the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18865S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18865S\"></sup>highway,Remove the stones, lift up a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18865T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18865T\"></sup>standard over the peoples.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Behold, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has proclaimed to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18866U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18866U\"></sup>end of the earth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18866V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18866V\"></sup>Say to the daughter of Zion, “Lo, your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18866W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18866W\"></sup>salvation comes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18866X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18866X\"></sup>Behold His reward is with Him, and His recompense before Him.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And they will call them, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18867Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18867Y\"></sup>The holy people,The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18867Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18867Z\"></sup>redeemed of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>”;And you will be called, “Sought out, a city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18867AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18867AA\"></sup>not forsaken.”"
		},
		"63": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">63 </span>Who is this who comes from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18868A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18868A\"></sup>Edom,With <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18868B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18868B\"></sup>garments of glowing colors from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18868C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18868C\"></sup>Bozrah,This One who is majestic in His apparel,Marching in the greatness of His strength?“It is I who speak in righteousness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18868D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18868D\"></sup>mighty to save.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Why is Your apparel red,And Your garments like the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18869E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18869E\"></sup>treads in the wine press?",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18870F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18870F\"></sup>I have trodden the wine trough alone,And from the peoples there was no man with Me.I also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18870G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18870G\"></sup>trod them in My angerAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18870H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18870H\"></sup>trampled them in My wrath;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18870I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18870I\"></sup>their lifeblood is sprinkled on My garments,And I stained all My raiment.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18871J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18871J\"></sup>day of vengeance was in My heart,And My year of redemption has come.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“I looked, and there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18872K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18872K\"></sup>no one to help,And I was astonished and there was no one to uphold;So My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18872L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18872L\"></sup>own arm brought salvation to Me,And My wrath upheld Me.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18873M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18873M\"></sup>trod down the peoples in My angerAnd made them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18873N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18873N\"></sup>drunk in My wrath,And I poured out their lifeblood on the earth.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>I shall make mention of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18874O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18874O\"></sup>lovingkindnesses of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, the praises of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,According to all that the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has granted us,And the great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18874P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18874P\"></sup>goodness toward the house of Israel,Which He has granted them according to His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18874Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18874Q\"></sup>compassionAnd according to the abundance of His lovingkindnesses.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For He said, “Surely, they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18875R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18875R\"></sup>My people,Sons who will not deal falsely.”So He became their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18875S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18875S\"></sup>Savior.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>In all their affliction <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18876T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18876T\"></sup>He was afflicted,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18876U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18876U\"></sup>angel of His presence saved them;In His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18876V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18876V\"></sup>love and in His mercy He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18876W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18876W\"></sup>redeemed them,And He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18876X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18876X\"></sup>lifted them and carried them all the days of old.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18877Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18877Y\"></sup>rebelledAnd grieved His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18877Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18877Z\"></sup>Holy Spirit;Therefore He turned Himself to become their enemy,He fought against them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18878AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18878AA\"></sup>His people remembered the days of old, of Moses.Where is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18878AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18878AB\"></sup>He who brought them up out of the sea with the shepherds of His flock?Where is He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18878AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18878AC\"></sup>put His Holy Spirit in the midst of them,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Who caused His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18879AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18879AD\"></sup>glorious arm to go at the right hand of Moses,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18879AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18879AE\"></sup>divided the waters before them to make for Himself an everlasting name,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Who led them through the depths?Like the horse in the wilderness, they did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18880AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18880AF\"></sup>stumble;",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>As the cattle which go down into the valley,The Spirit of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18881AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18881AG\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> gave them rest.So You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18881AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18881AH\"></sup>led Your people,To make for Yourself a glorious name.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18882AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18882AI\"></sup>Look down from heaven and see from Your holy and glorious <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18882AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18882AJ\"></sup>habitation;Where are Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18882AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18882AK\"></sup>zeal and Your mighty deeds?The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18882AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18882AL\"></sup>stirrings of Your heart and Your compassion are restrained toward me.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For You are our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18883AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18883AM\"></sup>Father, though <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18883AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18883AN\"></sup>Abraham does not know usAnd Israel does not recognize us.You, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, are our Father,Our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18883AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18883AO\"></sup>Redeemer from of old is Your name.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Why, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, do You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18884AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18884AP\"></sup>cause us to stray from Your waysAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18884AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18884AQ\"></sup>harden our heart from fearing You?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18884AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18884AR\"></sup>Return for the sake of Your servants, the tribes of Your heritage.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Your holy people possessed Your sanctuary for a little while,Our adversaries have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18885AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18885AS\"></sup>trodden <i>it</i> down.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>We have become <i>like</i> those over whom You have never ruled,<i>Like</i> those who were not called by Your name."
		},
		"64": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">64 </span>Oh, that You would rend the heavens <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18887A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18887A\"></sup>come down,That the mountains might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18887B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18887B\"></sup>quake at Your presence—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>As fire kindles the brushwood, <i>as</i> fire causes water to boil—To make Your name known to Your adversaries,<i>That</i> the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18888C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18888C\"></sup>nations may tremble at Your presence!",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When You did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18889D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18889D\"></sup>awesome things which we did not expect,You came down, the mountains quaked at Your presence.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For from days of old <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18890E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18890E\"></sup>they have not heard or perceived by ear,Nor has the eye seen a God besides You,Who acts in behalf of the one who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18890F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18890F\"></sup>waits for Him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18891G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18891G\"></sup>meet him who rejoices in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18891H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18891H\"></sup>doing righteousness,Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18891I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18891I\"></sup>remembers You in Your ways.Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18891J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18891J\"></sup>You were angry, for we sinned,<i>We continued</i> in them a long time;And shall we be saved?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For all of us have become like one who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18892K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18892K\"></sup>unclean,And all our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18892L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18892L\"></sup>righteous deeds are like a filthy garment;And all of us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18892M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18892M\"></sup>wither like a leaf,And our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18892N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18892N\"></sup>iniquities, like the wind, take us away.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>There is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18893O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18893O\"></sup>no one who calls on Your name,Who arouses himself to take hold of You;For You have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18893P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18893P\"></sup>hidden Your face from usAnd have delivered us into the power of our iniquities.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But now, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18894Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18894Q\"></sup>You are our Father,We are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18894R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18894R\"></sup>clay, and You our potter;And all of us are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18894S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18894S\"></sup>work of Your hand.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Do not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18895T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18895T\"></sup>angry beyond measure, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18895U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18895U\"></sup>Nor remember iniquity forever;Behold, look now, all of us are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18895V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18895V\"></sup>Your people.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18896W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18896W\"></sup>holy cities have become a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18896X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18896X\"></sup>wilderness,Zion has become a wilderness,Jerusalem a desolation.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Our holy and beautiful <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18897Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18897Y\"></sup>house,Where our fathers praised You,Has been burned <i>by</i> fire;And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18897Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18897Z\"></sup>all our precious things have become a ruin.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Will You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18898AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18898AA\"></sup>restrain Yourself at these things, O <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?Will You keep silent and afflict us beyond measure?"
		},
		"65": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">65 </span>“I permitted Myself to be sought by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18899A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18899A\"></sup>those who did not ask <i>for Me</i>;I permitted Myself to be found by those who did not seek Me.I said, ‘Here am I, here am I,’To a nation which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18899B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18899B\"></sup>did not call on My name.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18900C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18900C\"></sup>I have spread out My hands all day long to a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18900D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18900D\"></sup>rebellious people,Who walk <i>in</i> the way which is not good, following their own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18900E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18900E\"></sup>thoughts,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>A people who continually <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18901F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18901F\"></sup>provoke Me to My face,Offering sacrifices in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18901G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18901G\"></sup>gardens and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18901H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18901H\"></sup>burning incense on bricks;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Who sit among graves and spend the night in secret places;Who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18902I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18902I\"></sup>eat swine’s flesh,And the broth of unclean meat is <i>in</i> their pots.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Who say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18903J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18903J\"></sup>Keep to yourself, do not come near me,For I am holier than you!’These are smoke in My nostrils,A fire that burns all the day.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Behold, it is written before Me,I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18904K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18904K\"></sup>not keep silent, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18904L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18904L\"></sup>I will repay;I will even repay into their bosom,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Both their own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18905M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18905M\"></sup>iniquities and the iniquities of their fathers together,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Because they have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18905N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18905N\"></sup>burned incense on the mountainsAnd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18905O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18905O\"></sup>scorned Me on the hills,Therefore I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18905P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18905P\"></sup>measure their former work into their bosom.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“As the new wine is found in the cluster,And one says, ‘Do not destroy it, for there is benefit in it,’So I will act on behalf of My servantsIn order <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18906Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18906Q\"></sup>not to destroy all of them.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“I will bring forth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18907R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18907R\"></sup>offspring from Jacob,And an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18907S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18907S\"></sup>heir of My mountains from Judah;Even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18907T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18907T\"></sup>My chosen ones shall inherit it,And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18907U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18907U\"></sup>My servants will dwell there.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18908V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18908V\"></sup>Sharon will be a pasture land for flocks,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18908W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18908W\"></sup>valley of Achor a resting place for herds,For My people who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18908X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18908X\"></sup>seek Me.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“But you who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18909Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18909Y\"></sup>forsake the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,Who forget My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18909Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18909Z\"></sup>holy mountain,Who set a table for Fortune,And who fill <i>cups</i> with mixed wine for Destiny,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will destine you for the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18910AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18910AA\"></sup>sword,And all of you will bow down to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18910AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18910AB\"></sup>slaughter.Because I called, but you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18910AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18910AC\"></sup>did not answer;I spoke, but you did not hear.And you did evil in My sightAnd chose that in which I did not delight.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore, thus says the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span>,“Behold, My servants will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18911AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18911AD\"></sup>eat, but you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18911AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18911AE\"></sup>hungry.Behold, My servants will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18911AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18911AF\"></sup>drink, but you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18911AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18911AG\"></sup>thirsty.Behold, My servants will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18911AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18911AH\"></sup>rejoice, but you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18911AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18911AI\"></sup>put to shame.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Behold, My servants will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18912AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18912AJ\"></sup>shout joyfully with a glad heart,But you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18912AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18912AK\"></sup>cry out with a heavy heart,And you will wail with a broken spirit.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“You will leave your name for a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18913AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18913AL\"></sup>curse to My chosen ones,And the Lord <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God</span> will slay you.But My servants will be called by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18913AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18913AM\"></sup>another name.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Because he who is blessed in the earthWill be blessed by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18914AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18914AN\"></sup>God of truth;And he who swears in the earthWill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18914AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18914AO\"></sup>swear by the God of truth;Because the former troubles are forgotten,And because they are hidden from My sight!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“For behold, I create <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18915AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18915AP\"></sup>new heavens and a new earth;And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18915AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18915AQ\"></sup>former things will not be remembered or come to mind.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“But be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18916AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18916AR\"></sup>glad and rejoice forever in what I create;For behold, I create Jerusalem <i>for</i> rejoicingAnd her people <i>for</i> gladness.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“I will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18917AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18917AS\"></sup>rejoice in Jerusalem and be glad in My people;And there will no longer be heard in herThe voice of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18917AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18917AT\"></sup>weeping and the sound of crying.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“No longer will there be in it an infant <i>who lives but a few</i> days,Or an old man who does <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18918AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18918AU\"></sup>not live out his days;For the youth will die at the age of one hundredAnd the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18918AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18918AV\"></sup>one who does not reach the age of one hundredWill be <i>thought</i> accursed.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18919AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18919AW\"></sup>build houses and inhabit <i>them</i>;They will also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18919AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18919AX\"></sup>plant vineyards and eat their fruit.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“They will not build and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18920AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18920AY\"></sup>another inhabit,They will not plant and another eat;For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18920AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18920AZ\"></sup>as the lifetime of a tree, <i>so will be</i> the days of My people,And My chosen ones will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18920BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18920BA\"></sup>wear out the work of their hands.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18921BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18921BB\"></sup>not labor in vain,Or bear <i>children</i> for calamity;For they are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18921BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18921BC\"></sup>offspring of those blessed by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,And their descendants with them.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>It will also come to pass that before they call, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18922BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18922BD\"></sup>answer; and while they are still speaking, I will hear.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18923BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18923BE\"></sup>wolf and the lamb will graze together, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18923BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18923BF\"></sup>lion will eat straw like the ox; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18923BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18923BG\"></sup>dust will be the serpent’s food. They will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18923BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18923BH\"></sup>do no evil or harm in all My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18923BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18923BI\"></sup>holy mountain,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>."
		},
		"66": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">66 </span>Thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18924A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18924A\"></sup>Heaven is My throne and the earth is My footstool.Where then is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18924B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18924B\"></sup>house you could build for Me?And where is a place that I may rest?",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18925C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18925C\"></sup>My hand made all these things,Thus all these things came into being,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“But to this one I will look,To him who is humble and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18925D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18925D\"></sup>contrite of spirit, and who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18925E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18925E\"></sup>trembles at My word.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<i>But</i> he who kills an ox is <i>like</i> one who slays a man;He who sacrifices a lamb is <i>like</i> the one who breaks a dog’s neck;He who offers a grain offering <i>is like one who offers</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18926F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18926F\"></sup>swine’s blood;He who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18926G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18926G\"></sup>burns incense is <i>like</i> the one who blesses an idol.As they have chosen their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18926H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18926H\"></sup><i>own</i> ways,And their soul delights in their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18926I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18926I\"></sup>abominations,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>So I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18927J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18927J\"></sup>choose their punishmentsAnd will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18927K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18927K\"></sup>bring on them what they dread.Because I called, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18927L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18927L\"></sup>no one answered;I spoke, but they did not listen.And they did <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18927M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18927M\"></sup>evil in My sightAnd chose that in which I did not delight.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18928N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18928N\"></sup>tremble at His word:“Your brothers who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18928O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18928O\"></sup>hate you, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18928P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18928P\"></sup>exclude you for My name’s sake,Have said, ‘Let the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> be glorified, that we may see your joy.’But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18928Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18928Q\"></sup>they will be put to shame.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“A voice of uproar from the city, a voice from the temple,The voice of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18929R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18929R\"></sup>rendering recompense to His enemies.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Before she travailed, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18930S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18930S\"></sup>she brought forth;Before her pain came, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18930T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18930T\"></sup>she gave birth to a boy.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18931U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18931U\"></sup>Who has heard such a thing? Who has seen such things?Can a land be born in one day?Can a nation be brought forth all at once?As soon as Zion travailed, she also brought forth her sons.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Shall I bring to the point of birth and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18932V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18932V\"></sup>not give delivery?” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.“Or shall I who gives delivery shut <i>the womb</i>?” says your God.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18933W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18933W\"></sup>joyful with Jerusalem and rejoice for her, all you who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18933X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18933X\"></sup>love her;Be exceedingly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18933Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18933Y\"></sup>glad with her, all you who mourn over her,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>That you may nurse and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18934Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18934Z\"></sup>be satisfied with her comforting breasts,That you may suck and be delighted with her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18934AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18934AA\"></sup>bountiful bosom.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For thus says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “Behold, I extend <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18935AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18935AB\"></sup>peace to her like a river,And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18935AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18935AC\"></sup>glory of the nations like an overflowing stream;And you will be nursed, you will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18935AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18935AD\"></sup>carried on the hip and fondled on the knees.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“As one whom his mother comforts, so I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18936AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18936AE\"></sup>comfort you;And you will be comforted in Jerusalem.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18937AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18937AF\"></sup>see <i>this</i>, and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18937AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18937AG\"></sup>heart will be glad,And your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18937AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18937AH\"></sup>bones will flourish like the new grass;And the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18937AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18937AI\"></sup>hand of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be made known to His servants,But He will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18937AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18937AJ\"></sup>indignant toward His enemies.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For behold, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will come in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18938AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18938AK\"></sup>fireAnd His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18938AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18938AL\"></sup>chariots like the whirlwind,To render His anger with fury,And His rebuke with flames of fire.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will execute judgment by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18939AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18939AM\"></sup>fireAnd by His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18939AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18939AN\"></sup>sword on all flesh,And those slain by the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will be many.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Those who sanctify and purify themselves <i>to go</i> to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18940AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18940AO\"></sup>gardens,Following one in the center,Who eat <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18940AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18940AP\"></sup>swine’s flesh, detestable things and mice,Will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18940AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18940AQ\"></sup>come to an end altogether,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“For I know their works and their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18941AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18941AR\"></sup>thoughts; the time is coming to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18941AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18941AS\"></sup>gather all nations and tongues. And they shall come and see My glory.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I will set a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18942AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18942AT\"></sup>sign among them and will send survivors from them to the nations: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18942AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18942AU\"></sup>Tarshish, Put, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18942AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18942AV\"></sup>Lud, Meshech, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18942AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18942AW\"></sup>Tubal and Javan, to the distant <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18942AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18942AX\"></sup>coastlands that have neither heard My fame nor seen My glory. And they will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18942AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18942AY\"></sup>declare My glory among the nations.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then they shall <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18943AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18943AZ\"></sup>bring all your brethren from all the nations as a grain offering to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, on horses, in chariots, in litters, on mules and on camels, to My <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18943BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18943BA\"></sup>holy mountain Jerusalem,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, “just as the sons of Israel bring their grain offering in a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18943BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18943BB\"></sup>clean vessel to the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I will also take some of them for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18944BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18944BC\"></sup>priests <i>and</i> for Levites,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“For just as the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18945BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18945BD\"></sup>new heavens and the new earthWhich I make will endure before Me,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“So your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18945BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18945BE\"></sup>offspring and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18945BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18945BF\"></sup>name will endure.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“And it shall be from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18946BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18946BG\"></sup>new moon to new moonAnd from sabbath to sabbath,All mankind will come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18946BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18946BH\"></sup>bow down before Me,” says the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Then they will go forth and lookOn the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18947BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18947BI\"></sup>corpses of the menWho have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18947BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18947BJ\"></sup>transgressed against Me.For their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18947BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18947BK\"></sup>worm will not die<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18947BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18947BL\"></sup>And their fire will not be quenched;And they will be an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-18947BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-18947BM\"></sup>abhorrence to all mankind.”"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;